{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1001", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Geoffrey Hinton is a pioneer in artificial intelligence, known for his work on neural networks and deep learning.", "citations": {"042ce256-aaa2-4944-8725-7deb68b8b43f_125182681": 1.0, "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684": 0.5, "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_779126512": 0.25, "79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_496813334": 0.125, "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079": 0.0625, "d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942": 0.03125, "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_839419513": 0.015625}}, {"text": "He is often called the \"godfather of artificial intelligence\".", "citations": {"042ce256-aaa2-4944-8725-7deb68b8b43f_125182681": 1.0, "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684": 0.5, "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_779126512": 0.25, "79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_496813334": 0.125, "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079": 0.0625, "d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942": 0.03125, "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_839419513": 0.015625}}, {"text": "Hinton's contributions have been instrumental in shaping the field of AI.", "citations": {"3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684": 1.0, "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_779126512": 0.5, "79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_496813334": 0.25, "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079": 0.125}}, {"text": "His warnings about AI's potential dangers have sparked significant attention and debate.", "citations": {"042ce256-aaa2-4944-8725-7deb68b8b43f_125182681": 1.0, "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684": 0.5, "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_779126512": 0.25, "792ba802-fc52-4ca2-bb1a-ee90ce0fe3de_704363760": 0.125, "79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_496813334": 0.0625, "892eb5ca-2b8c-4eeb-b71c-c9f8f83ccc6a_11672726": 0.03125, "a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134": 0.015625, "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079": 0.0078125, "d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942": 0.00390625, "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_839419513": 0.001953125, "eec5e074-3566-4b62-a2e7-65d0579c4f71_924627484": 0.0009765625}}, {"text": "Hinton believes AI could surpass human intelligence and threaten humanity if mismanaged.", "citations": {"3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684": 1.0, "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_779126512": 0.5, "792ba802-fc52-4ca2-bb1a-ee90ce0fe3de_704363760": 0.25, "79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_496813334": 0.125, "892eb5ca-2b8c-4eeb-b71c-c9f8f83ccc6a_11672726": 0.0625, "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079": 0.03125, "d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942": 0.015625, "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_839419513": 0.0078125}}, {"text": "He warns that AI poses a greater existential threat than climate change.", "citations": {"d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hinton's concerns about AI involve both the technology and its potential mismanagement.", "citations": {"3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684": 1.0, "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_779126512": 0.5, "792ba802-fc52-4ca2-bb1a-ee90ce0fe3de_704363760": 0.25, "79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_496813334": 0.125, "9f2305a4-5741-4eef-9e53-fd05af571cdf_241409653": 0.0625, "a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134": 0.03125, "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079": 0.015625, "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_76481654": 0.0078125, "d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942": 0.00390625, "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_304858450": 0.001953125, "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_839419513": 0.0009765625, "eec5e074-3566-4b62-a2e7-65d0579c4f71_924627484": 0.00048828125}}, {"text": "He has expressed concerns about AI being used for lethal autonomous weapons.", "citations": {"eec5e074-3566-4b62-a2e7-65d0579c4f71_924627484": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hinton does not think suspending AI research is the solution, but rather that politics should control AI development.", "citations": {"d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942": 1.0}}, {"text": "Elon Musk and other experts share Hinton's AI concerns and call for a development pause.", "citations": {"d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079": 1.0, "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_76481654": 0.5, "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_304858450": 0.25}}, {"text": "The European Parliament and thousands of signatories are calling for a halt to powerful AI system development.", "citations": {"d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942": 1.0}}, {"text": "The public should carefully consider AI's potential risks and benefits as it rapidly develops.", "citations": {"3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684": 1.0, "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_779126512": 0.5, "792ba802-fc52-4ca2-bb1a-ee90ce0fe3de_704363760": 0.25, "79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_496813334": 0.125, "9f2305a4-5741-4eef-9e53-fd05af571cdf_241409653": 0.0625, "a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134": 0.03125, "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079": 0.015625, "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_76481654": 0.0078125, "d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942": 0.00390625, "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_304858450": 0.001953125, "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_839419513": 0.0009765625, "eec5e074-3566-4b62-a2e7-65d0579c4f71_924627484": 0.00048828125}}, {"text": "Developing safe and controlled AI systems is a complex challenge requiring careful attention and regulation.", "citations": {"3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684": 1.0, "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_779126512": 0.5, "792ba802-fc52-4ca2-bb1a-ee90ce0fe3de_704363760": 0.25, "79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_496813334": 0.125, "9f2305a4-5741-4eef-9e53-fd05af571cdf_241409653": 0.0625, "a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134": 0.03125, "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079": 0.015625, "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_76481654": 0.0078125, "d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942": 0.00390625, "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_304858450": 0.001953125, "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_839419513": 0.0009765625, "eec5e074-3566-4b62-a2e7-65d0579c4f71_924627484": 0.00048828125}}, {"text": "Governments, industry leaders, and researchers must collaborate to ensure the responsible development of AI.", "citations": {"0a14ae6a-c873-450a-a681-13c26f1ddc99_956540449": 1.0}}, {"text": "The EU and US President Biden are taking steps to regulate AI for transparency, safety, security, and trust.", "citations": {"5f992d20-bd7f-443e-87b7-ec865d1ffdb8_291818721": 1.0}}, {"text": "The EU regulates AI to ensure ethical and safe use, respecting rights like privacy.", "citations": {"5fa19199-4cb9-4eb3-985d-a35e9a0e00f0_843949295": 1.0}}, {"text": "The EU requires human supervision and sets standards for AI risk assessment and testing.", "citations": {"5fa19199-4cb9-4eb3-985d-a35e9a0e00f0_843949295": 1.0}}, {"text": "Independent bodies are crucial for assessing the trustworthiness of AI systems and building public trust.", "citations": {"c4df1771-8297-4414-adac-d7cd6bb376e0_839018043": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US AI regulatory landscape is a patchwork of laws and guidelines issued by federal agencies.", "citations": {"d6cca264-c75e-4b92-a005-59318fba1d99_148847369": 1.0}}], "references": ["d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079", "9f2305a4-5741-4eef-9e53-fd05af571cdf_241409653", "d6cca264-c75e-4b92-a005-59318fba1d99_148847369", "5fa19199-4cb9-4eb3-985d-a35e9a0e00f0_843949295", "eec5e074-3566-4b62-a2e7-65d0579c4f71_924627484", "042ce256-aaa2-4944-8725-7deb68b8b43f_125182681", "d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942", "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_839419513", "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_304858450", "792ba802-fc52-4ca2-bb1a-ee90ce0fe3de_704363760", "c4df1771-8297-4414-adac-d7cd6bb376e0_839018043", "892eb5ca-2b8c-4eeb-b71c-c9f8f83ccc6a_11672726", "79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_496813334", "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_779126512", "5f992d20-bd7f-443e-87b7-ec865d1ffdb8_291818721", "0a14ae6a-c873-450a-a681-13c26f1ddc99_956540449", "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684", "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_76481654", "a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1002", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Geoffrey Hinton is a renowned cognitive psychologist and computer scientist who is known as the \"father of artificial intelligence\" or the \"godfather\" of artificial intelligence.", "citations": {"79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_496813334": 1.0}}, {"text": "He has made significant contributions to the development of artificial intelligence, particularly in the field of neural networks and deep learning.", "citations": {"79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_496813334": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hinton's work has enabled the creation of AI systems such as Google's Bard chatbot and ChatGPT.", "citations": {"79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_496813334": 1.0}}, {"text": "He was awarded the Turing Award in 2018 for his research breakthroughs in artificial intelligence.", "citations": {"792ba802-fc52-4ca2-bb1a-ee90ce0fe3de_704363760": 1.0, "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079": 0.5, "d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942": 0.25}}, {"text": "Hinton has expressed regrets over his life's work on AI development due to the potential dangers it poses.", "citations": {"3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_779126512": 1.0, "792ba802-fc52-4ca2-bb1a-ee90ce0fe3de_704363760": 0.5, "a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134": 0.25}}, {"text": "He believes that AI is becoming smarter than humans and may lead to mass unemployment.", "citations": {"3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684": 1.0, "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_779126512": 0.5, "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079": 0.25}}, {"text": "Hinton also warns that AI can create a world where reality is unclear and can be used to manipulate humans.", "citations": {"3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684": 1.0, "9f2305a4-5741-4eef-9e53-fd05af571cdf_241409653": 0.5}}, {"text": "He is concerned about the impact of AI on human life trajectory and the potential for AI to spread false information easily.", "citations": {"3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684": 1.0, "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_779126512": 0.5, "9f2305a4-5741-4eef-9e53-fd05af571cdf_241409653": 0.25}}, {"text": "Hinton's warnings about AI dangers and mismanagement have made headlines, with many experts agreeing that AI poses significant risks to society and humanity.", "citations": {"9f2305a4-5741-4eef-9e53-fd05af571cdf_241409653": 1.0, "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_76481654": 0.5, "d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942": 0.25, "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_839419513": 0.125}}, {"text": "He has called for governments to intervene in AI development and for scientists to control AI before scaling it up.", "citations": {"9f2305a4-5741-4eef-9e53-fd05af571cdf_241409653": 1.0, "d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942": 0.5}}, {"text": "Hinton has also suggested marking AI-generated content to identify fakes and has warned that the average person may not know what's true.", "citations": {"9f2305a4-5741-4eef-9e53-fd05af571cdf_241409653": 1.0, "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_839419513": 0.5}}, {"text": "Other experts, including Elon Musk, have led calls for a moratorium on AI development due to the potential risks it poses.", "citations": {"e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_304858450": 1.0}}, {"text": "The European Parliament has also called for a summit to control advanced AI development.", "citations": {"d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hinton's resignation from Google was motivated by his desire to speak freely about AI risks without employer involvement.", "citations": {"3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684": 1.0, "a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134": 0.5, "d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942": 0.25}}, {"text": "He has stated that he wants to raise awareness about AI risks and has warned that AI could potentially eliminate humans.", "citations": {"3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684": 1.0, "eec5e074-3566-4b62-a2e7-65d0579c4f71_924627484": 0.5}}, {"text": "Hinton's warnings have sparked a debate about the need for responsible AI development and the potential consequences of creating advanced AI systems.", "citations": {"d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_76481654": 1.0, "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_304858450": 0.5, "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_839419513": 0.25}}, {"text": "The public should understand that AI poses significant risks and that experts like Hinton are calling for caution and regulation in the development of AI systems.", "citations": {"9f2305a4-5741-4eef-9e53-fd05af571cdf_241409653": 1.0, "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_76481654": 0.5, "d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942": 0.25, "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_839419513": 0.125}}, {"text": "The development of safe and reliable AI systems is a complex challenge that requires a comprehensive approach, involving technical, social, and regulatory considerations.", "citations": {"c4df1771-8297-4414-adac-d7cd6bb376e0_839018043": 1.0}}, {"text": "Established methodologies from cybersecurity are necessary for AI accountability, and novel AI auditing techniques are needed for AI-specific accountability mechanisms.", "citations": {"c4df1771-8297-4414-adac-d7cd6bb376e0_839018043": 1.0}}, {"text": "The development of safe and reliable AI systems also requires a focus on cybersecurity, as AI systems are vulnerable to cyberattacks and can be used for misinformation and social engineering.", "citations": {"64e6fa77-3898-4a0b-8f42-fd5bc1ba669d_679352341": 1.0}}, {"text": "Global initiatives, such as the AI Safety Institutes announced by the US and UK, are working to address these challenges and develop guidelines for secure AI systems.", "citations": {"64e6fa77-3898-4a0b-8f42-fd5bc1ba669d_679352341": 1.0}}, {"text": "The use of techniques such as Lyapunov functions and \u03b1,\u03b2-CROWN verifier can help ensure the safety and stability of robots and autonomous vehicles powered by neural networks.", "citations": {"b70d22f5-40c4-44d2-9905-0eefdabb60b3_475184109": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Biden administration has created an AI Safety and Security Board with 22 initial members, including tech CEOs, to identify potential security threats from AI and develop recommendations for critical infrastructure stakeholders.", "citations": {"05485d42-eb1c-440d-89fc-fefbe908b608_608456199": 1.0}}, {"text": "The board aims to prevent AI-related disruptions to services and includes government officials, with the Department of Homeland Security establishing an advisory panel on AI threats.", "citations": {"05485d42-eb1c-440d-89fc-fefbe908b608_608456199": 1.0}}, {"text": "CoSAI, an open-source initiative hosted by OASIS, was formed by 14 major AI companies to provide guidance and tools for secure AI systems, focusing on mitigating AI risks like model theft and data poisoning.", "citations": {"4cdb4201-8924-4d41-aa8b-39d6a3e4e0be_555998384": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US and UK have partnered to safety test AI models, and have established AI Safety Institutes to develop a common approach to AI safety testing and share information on AI capabilities and risks.", "citations": {"7b060d6e-72c0-4bd5-a1c5-5755c75ac708_625462368": 1.0}}, {"text": "The EU's AI Act requires companies to disclose safety test results, and the US President's executive order requires safety testing, demonstrating the growing recognition of the need for rigorous testing and evaluation of AI systems.", "citations": {"7b060d6e-72c0-4bd5-a1c5-5755c75ac708_625462368": 1.0}}, {"text": "Experts believe that future AI systems may outmatch humans in cognitive skills, and that stronger democratic oversight is needed over AI development and deployment to prevent potential harms.", "citations": {"14190bf2-5114-4846-bdc2-bca381772686_999456816": 1.0}}, {"text": "Independent auditing can help reduce AI risks and surface previously overlooked harms, and rebalancing funding to prioritize AI safety and transparency is necessary to ensure that AI development is aligned with human values.", "citations": {"14190bf2-5114-4846-bdc2-bca381772686_999456816": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US and UK collaboration on AI safety is a key development, and the establishment of AI Safety Institutes in both countries marks a significant step towards ensuring the safe development and deployment of AI.", "citations": {"c2d673d5-2fcf-4a36-b3d8-82c13cfba1a8_54419265": 1.0}}, {"text": "The European Union enacted an AI Regulation on February 2, 2024, which aims to ensure AI systems are safe and respect rights.", "citations": {"2e2a3c56-85ef-4c9a-9a51-d4494940c73a_995080848": 1.0}}, {"text": "The AI Act applies to businesses operating within the EU, as well as companies outside the EU territory, and requires them to compile an inventory of their AI models.", "citations": {"2e2a3c56-85ef-4c9a-9a51-d4494940c73a_995080848": 1.0}}, {"text": "AI models are classified according to associated risks, and high-risk AI models must comply with strict requirements, including establishing governance and monitoring measures.", "citations": {"2e2a3c56-85ef-4c9a-9a51-d4494940c73a_995080848": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies that fail to comply with the AI Act may face penalties ranging from \u20ac10 million to \u20ac40 million, or up to 7% of the company's global annual turnover.", "citations": {"2e2a3c56-85ef-4c9a-9a51-d4494940c73a_995080848": 1.0}}, {"text": "In the United States, California has proposed AI regulation with safety standards, including pre-deployment safety testing and cybersecurity protections for large AI developers.", "citations": {"4e914587-fb2a-4471-9cb6-807c70917fa1_233249691": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US government plays a significant role in setting AI standards, and the Biden administration has made efforts to develop AI standards, including an executive order that establishes new standards for AI safety and security.", "citations": {"5185820f-8379-4a4a-9f20-919851060177_1070258821": 1.0}}, {"text": "President Joe Biden's Executive Order requires developers to share safety test results with the U.S. government and protects Americans' privacy and advances equity.", "citations": {"5185820f-8379-4a4a-9f20-919851060177_1070258821": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Order also aims to study AI's labor-market impacts and seeks to strengthen federal support for workers.", "citations": {"5185820f-8379-4a4a-9f20-919851060177_1070258821": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Biden Administration focuses on worker protections and responsible AI development, and the OFCCP will publish guidance on nondiscrimination in hiring involving AI technology.", "citations": {"6fba71a6-c24a-4e7c-ab41-321e987f2d08_642357599": 1.0}}, {"text": "The National Institute of Standards and Technology will draft guidelines for safe, secure, and trustworthy AI system development, and security testing and \"red teaming\" of AI will become more relevant for employers.", "citations": {"6fba71a6-c24a-4e7c-ab41-321e987f2d08_642357599": 1.0}}, {"text": "The European Union's Artificial Intelligence Act sets global standards for AI development and use, and promotes trustworthy AI development and use in the EU.", "citations": {"858d96d9-7588-4d8d-860c-bc8f8e9295a1_1027864270": 1.0}}, {"text": "The AI Act establishes a risk-based approach to AI governance and imposes strict prohibitions on certain AI applications, including manipulative persuasion and social scoring systems.", "citations": {"858d96d9-7588-4d8d-860c-bc8f8e9295a1_1027864270": 1.0}}, {"text": "The EU AI Act safeguards fundamental rights, including privacy and non-discrimination, and non-EU companies using EU customer data must comply with the AI Act.", "citations": {"858d96d9-7588-4d8d-860c-bc8f8e9295a1_1027864270": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US lacks comprehensive AI regulation, but the Biden administration has issued executive orders and guidelines to regulate AI development and safety.", "citations": {"97e63a47-7c14-4575-9872-a2a862306281_609743591": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US government oversees AI development for national security, and companies must disclose safety results to US agencies.", "citations": {"97e63a47-7c14-4575-9872-a2a862306281_609743591": 1.0}}, {"text": "The National Institute of Standards and Technology sets safety test standards, and the Department of Homeland Security applies standards to critical infrastructure.", "citations": {"97e63a47-7c14-4575-9872-a2a862306281_609743591": 1.0}}, {"text": "Experts are skeptical about the effectiveness of new regulations, and the AI industry lacks standard testing safety protocols.", "citations": {"a3deca51-5c90-4c87-bc89-ed5d356ceb39_369709195": 1.0}}, {"text": "The administration faces the challenge of creating reasonable standards that balance safety and innovation.", "citations": {"a3deca51-5c90-4c87-bc89-ed5d356ceb39_369709195": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US and EU are collaborating on a voluntary AI code of conduct, and 97% of businesses expect to use AI to improve efficiencies and cut costs.", "citations": {"d1932530-fbdc-442b-ad84-0a9f508aff57_710421970": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, the US lacks data privacy regulations, which hinders AI safety efforts, and China's AI development has prompted the US to avoid stiff regulation.", "citations": {"d1932530-fbdc-442b-ad84-0a9f508aff57_710421970": 1.0}}, {"text": "The term \"AI safety\" is vague and open to interpretation, and the National AI Commission Act proposes a 20-member commission to study AI regulation.", "citations": {"d1932530-fbdc-442b-ad84-0a9f508aff57_710421970": 1.0}}, {"text": "Geoffrey Hinton's warnings about the dangers of unmanaged AI have made headlines, but the current AI regulation standards and efforts to address AI safety concerns are ongoing and evolving.", "citations": {"4ab52a0d-9c44-4951-8fc4-9e354311b019_626405997": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UK has pledged 80 million pounds for AI projects globally, with a focus on supporting AI expertise in Africa, and establishing eight new AI research labs in African universities.", "citations": {"0137d42a-bd83-4fac-ab2b-15e7ecb73bce_589680454": 1.0}}, {"text": "The United Nations has adopted a resolution on safe artificial intelligence systems, which aims to promote sustainable development and human rights, and calls for governments to collaborate with the private sector on AI safety.", "citations": {"0919f2b3-8599-4ff4-8c83-1c7584e8db7c_520067563": 1.0}}, {"text": "Over 120 countries co-sponsored the UN resolution, which establishes clear international standards for AI and protects citizens' safety, privacy, and human rights.", "citations": {"0919f2b3-8599-4ff4-8c83-1c7584e8db7c_520067563": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Global AI Safety Summit aims to mitigate AI risks, and has been hosted by the UK, with tech companies and AI experts in attendance, including Elon Musk, who has called for a regulatory framework for AI.", "citations": {"0a928078-45cf-4a68-aa31-82ba3fa3c894_127629751": 1.0}}, {"text": "China, the US, and the EU have agreed to work together on AI safety, and have signed the \"Bletchley Declaration\" for AI oversight, which marks a significant step towards international cooperation on AI safety.", "citations": {"0a928078-45cf-4a68-aa31-82ba3fa3c894_127629751": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US has released an executive order on AI safety, which identifies areas of concern with AI use, including labor and cybersecurity, and requires federal agencies to develop principles to mitigate AI harms to workers.", "citations": {"7053b263-6272-4027-9320-d4533d950e59_231081723": 1.0}}, {"text": "The executive order also promotes a pro-union agenda across the government and seeks to support workers' collective bargaining rights, highlighting the need for careful consideration of the social implications of AI development.", "citations": {"7053b263-6272-4027-9320-d4533d950e59_231081723": 1.0}}], "references": ["d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942", "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_304858450", "97e63a47-7c14-4575-9872-a2a862306281_609743591", "64e6fa77-3898-4a0b-8f42-fd5bc1ba669d_679352341", "7b060d6e-72c0-4bd5-a1c5-5755c75ac708_625462368", "7053b263-6272-4027-9320-d4533d950e59_231081723", "4cdb4201-8924-4d41-aa8b-39d6a3e4e0be_555998384", "5185820f-8379-4a4a-9f20-919851060177_1070258821", "9f2305a4-5741-4eef-9e53-fd05af571cdf_241409653", "a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134", "14190bf2-5114-4846-bdc2-bca381772686_999456816", "858d96d9-7588-4d8d-860c-bc8f8e9295a1_1027864270", "0137d42a-bd83-4fac-ab2b-15e7ecb73bce_589680454", "79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_496813334", "a3deca51-5c90-4c87-bc89-ed5d356ceb39_369709195", "c2d673d5-2fcf-4a36-b3d8-82c13cfba1a8_54419265", "e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_839419513", "b70d22f5-40c4-44d2-9905-0eefdabb60b3_475184109", "d1932530-fbdc-442b-ad84-0a9f508aff57_710421970", "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_76481654", "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_779126512", "c4df1771-8297-4414-adac-d7cd6bb376e0_839018043", "2e2a3c56-85ef-4c9a-9a51-d4494940c73a_995080848", "4ab52a0d-9c44-4951-8fc4-9e354311b019_626405997", "4e914587-fb2a-4471-9cb6-807c70917fa1_233249691", "792ba802-fc52-4ca2-bb1a-ee90ce0fe3de_704363760", "d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079", "0919f2b3-8599-4ff4-8c83-1c7584e8db7c_520067563", "6fba71a6-c24a-4e7c-ab41-321e987f2d08_642357599", "0a928078-45cf-4a68-aa31-82ba3fa3c894_127629751", "05485d42-eb1c-440d-89fc-fefbe908b608_608456199", "eec5e074-3566-4b62-a2e7-65d0579c4f71_924627484", "3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1003", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle involves traveling while working remotely, with countries like Japan considering specialized visas to support it.", "citations": {"c99adb91-64a7-454a-a41a-1cd3415fae92_617034367": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads work in fields like software development, writing, and design, using laptops, smartphones, and cloud-based software to stay productive while traveling.", "citations": {"a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641": 1.0}}, {"text": "Thailand and Vietnam are popular destinations for digital nomads, with Thailand offering a 90-day visa-free entry for Russian citizens, extendable to 180 days.", "citations": {"0be60a3e-b6c5-4420-9ef2-c97b0bd0919f_600996491": 1.0, "1231defb-7f28-4479-9af5-28ec6229624e_69724798": 0.5}}, {"text": "Portugal and Spain also offer digital nomad visas, with Portugal's visa requiring a monthly income of around $2,750 and Spain's visa requiring 80% of income to come from outside Spain.", "citations": {"3c57c4fb-d12e-473a-a696-2f312f3dbe84_185731968": 1.0, "b3b0382a-c38c-4858-8b00-38e921fd7e35_817402441": 0.5}}, {"text": "Thailand's digital nomad visa costs 10,000 THB and requires applicants to have 500,000 THB in a bank account and proof of registered company employment.", "citations": {"68481cfe-cd12-4858-a950-e67fa9f2f958_920402130": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russian digital nomads face cybersecurity and data protection risks when working abroad, and may be subject to a 13-15% personal income tax rate.", "citations": {"aeed650d-3516-4a18-9fbc-de1dc7268774_402499413": 1.0, "213bf97f-947f-4930-b7a6-7d7ab14f2ac9_385431892": 0.5}}, {"text": "Digital nomads often rely on coworking and coliving spaces, and use tools like ClickUp, Miro, and Google's Jamboard for remote collaboration.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0, "07cf246f-1952-45a1-8031-4d4ba74b540a_121181923": 0.5}}, {"text": "Remote desktop software, video conferencing tools like Zoom, and project management software like Trello and Asana also facilitate remote work.", "citations": {"b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_37536649": 1.0, "2d71c373-b971-42ef-9f1c-b79d9c1d5088_610946698": 0.5, "7cdf442e-e413-4b8e-aef4-797e9f721f01_188185910": 0.25}}, {"text": "Russian digital nomads can manage their tax obligations through the \"Gosuslugi\" platform, and are taxed at a uniform rate of 13-15% regardless of tax residency.", "citations": {"213bf97f-947f-4930-b7a6-7d7ab14f2ac9_385431892": 1.0, "22007e11-e905-4961-a00b-afd858aa8348_945646981": 0.5}}, {"text": "The tax rate applies to Russian company employees working abroad, and foreign companies must register as tax agents for Russian employees or have them file and pay taxes independently.", "citations": {"2ec94e79-be7d-4bbd-bbda-d553fb44e0b0_711412342": 1.0, "8d4e0568-da7f-48a1-9538-f65d6b4a2bf8_679684297": 0.5}}], "references": ["b3b0382a-c38c-4858-8b00-38e921fd7e35_817402441", "a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641", "7cdf442e-e413-4b8e-aef4-797e9f721f01_188185910", "22007e11-e905-4961-a00b-afd858aa8348_945646981", "c99adb91-64a7-454a-a41a-1cd3415fae92_617034367", "3c57c4fb-d12e-473a-a696-2f312f3dbe84_185731968", "b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_37536649", "1231defb-7f28-4479-9af5-28ec6229624e_69724798", "213bf97f-947f-4930-b7a6-7d7ab14f2ac9_385431892", "aeed650d-3516-4a18-9fbc-de1dc7268774_402499413", "72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748", "8d4e0568-da7f-48a1-9538-f65d6b4a2bf8_679684297", "2ec94e79-be7d-4bbd-bbda-d553fb44e0b0_711412342", "68481cfe-cd12-4858-a950-e67fa9f2f958_920402130", "2d71c373-b971-42ef-9f1c-b79d9c1d5088_610946698", "07cf246f-1952-45a1-8031-4d4ba74b540a_121181923", "0be60a3e-b6c5-4420-9ef2-c97b0bd0919f_600996491"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1004", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle involves working remotely and traveling often, providing individuals with the freedom and flexibility to work from anywhere with a stable internet connection.", "citations": {"23980c8b-8970-4b9b-96ce-6f690a62ec45_787468909": 1.0}}, {"text": "This lifestyle requires a mobile office setup, including a lightweight laptop, WiFi hotspot, USB charging station, portable work desk, noise-cancelling headphones, and portable wireless mouse.", "citations": {"23980c8b-8970-4b9b-96ce-6f690a62ec45_787468909": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can work in various fields, such as software development, digital marketing, and writing, and can earn a significant income, with some earning up to $50,000 per month.", "citations": {"f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_256892267": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, digital nomads also face challenges, such as homesickness, exhaustion, and time management, which can be mitigated with the right tools and strategies.", "citations": {"4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Many countries offer special visas for digital nomads, such as Japan, Spain, and Portugal, which provide a convenient option for workers who wish to maintain their residence in a destination country.", "citations": {"fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379": 1.0}}, {"text": "These visas often have specific requirements, such as a minimum income or employment contract, and may offer tax concessions or exemptions.", "citations": {"088e0346-91bf-43fd-b68c-748ae1e1247f_998032520": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads must also consider tax implications in different countries, and may need to register as self-employed or obtain a tax agent to manage their tax obligations.", "citations": {"a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641": 1.0}}, {"text": "To maintain a consistent client base while traveling, digital nomads can use communication tools, such as Zoom, Slack, and Google Calendar, to schedule meetings and block time for work and personal life.", "citations": {"249b8018-b83e-458c-be07-418fce10c28b_986701262": 1.0}}, {"text": "Project management tools, such as Trello, Asana, and Basecamp, can help digital nomads organize tasks and collaborate with team members in real-time remotely.", "citations": {"24b6312b-e15a-4c0d-9e24-184ea04376b4_218045225": 1.0}}, {"text": "Invoicing tools, such as Billdu, can provide professional invoice makers, online booking, and online store creation tools, as well as live chat features for client communication.", "citations": {"ea127547-3f76-481b-8ea0-e7d7d8b7832e_116322958": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can also use automation software to save time by automating regular tasks, and customer management platforms, such as Genesys, to streamline customer interactions.", "citations": {"249b8018-b83e-458c-be07-418fce10c28b_986701262": 1.0}}, {"text": "Remote desktop software, such as Splashtop, can provide secure remote desktop solutions, enabling digital nomads to access their work computers from anywhere.", "citations": {"b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_37536649": 1.0}}, {"text": "To set up a secure remote work environment, digital nomads can install antivirus software, enable two-factor authentication, and use a Virtual Private Network (VPN) to encrypt data and protect it from unauthorized access.", "citations": {"16bff253-f821-4c36-ae1e-566843a4046b_322133742": 1.0}}, {"text": "Creating strong passwords, disabling remote access, and using secure cloud storage with multi-factor authentication can also help protect sensitive information.", "citations": {"16bff253-f821-4c36-ae1e-566843a4046b_322133742": 1.0}}, {"text": "Regularly updating antivirus software and virus definitions, and using unique credentials for each account, can help prevent cyber attacks.", "citations": {"16bff253-f821-4c36-ae1e-566843a4046b_322133742": 1.0}}, {"text": "The VPN market has grown significantly, with a worth of $35.4 Billion in 2020, and is expected to reach $107.6 Billion by 2027, indicating the increasing demand for secure remote work solutions.", "citations": {"1e3a8772-07f1-43e0-8e22-8968a02bec12_797696511": 1.0}}, {"text": "End-to-end encryption, two-factor authentication, and port filtering are essential security features for digital nomads, and device authentication can ensure secure remote collaboration.", "citations": {"2cd59861-ef91-41c1-a09b-2492f149c4ba_498963821": 1.0}}, {"text": "Cybercrime has increased by 600% in 2021 due to remote work, and 95% of cybersecurity breaches result from human error, emphasizing the need for proper training and security measures.", "citations": {"422cd2de-cbe5-4f2b-a201-d5a13b8447ab_536909040": 1.0}}, {"text": "Using a VPN, employing anti-malware software, and installing privacy extensions, such as uBlock Origin, can help protect devices from cyber attacks.", "citations": {"569e7af2-fa30-48de-b472-f064c6307db7_43064042": 1.0}}, {"text": "Cloud VPN provides a secure approach to remote work, encrypting all network communications and offering state-of-the-art user control.", "citations": {"5b5734d4-7823-40dc-af7c-5d514d5b8e87_903041797": 1.0}}, {"text": "Updating router and Wi-Fi with complex passwords, and regularly updating software with critical patches, can help reduce vulnerabilities.", "citations": {"832c6fe0-2321-4541-a285-f596085d29da_464005243": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can use time tracking software, such as TimeSite Pro, ClickUp, Toggl, Harvest, and Clockify, to track time efficiently and effortlessly.", "citations": {"2060cd19-2a64-4537-987d-dc20f718a8a9_575680989": 1.0}}, {"text": "Team Time extension and MeetMomentum can help digital nomads manage time zones and schedule meetings across different time zones.", "citations": {"5750ba90-82b8-4b5a-8c4c-36fa3f02c29b_808221478": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the digital nomad lifestyle requires careful planning, self-discipline, and the right tools to maintain a consistent client base and achieve success while traveling.", "citations": {"a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641": 1.0}}, {"text": "Russian IT specialists can face challenges in ensuring compliance with international tax laws and regulations while working abroad, and must pay tax on their income, with a tax rate of 13-15% applicable to their income.", "citations": {"213bf97f-947f-4930-b7a6-7d7ab14f2ac9_385431892": 1.0}}, {"text": "The tax rate depends on their annual income, exceeding 5 million rubles, and Russian residents must pay tax for services to foreign companies.", "citations": {"2ec94e79-be7d-4bbd-bbda-d553fb44e0b0_711412342": 1.0}}, {"text": "Foreign companies must register as tax agents for Russian employees, and tax rate depends on annual income, exceeding 5 million rubles.", "citations": {"2ec94e79-be7d-4bbd-bbda-d553fb44e0b0_711412342": 1.0}}, {"text": "New tax norms apply from 2024 for full-time employees, and from 2025 for freelancers, with the Russian tax rate being 13% or 15% for remote workers abroad.", "citations": {"2ec94e79-be7d-4bbd-bbda-d553fb44e0b0_711412342": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads must balance work and personal life, and setting boundaries, scheduling outgoing messages, and reducing notifications can help minimize distractions and avoid interruptions.", "citations": {"151f3688-882b-4c8a-8195-f7bb6ba13d3b_420890211": 1.0}}, {"text": "Using various tools, such as project management software, time tracking tools, and collaboration platforms, can help digital nomads increase productivity and collaboration.", "citations": {"151f3688-882b-4c8a-8195-f7bb6ba13d3b_420890211": 1.0}}, {"text": "Understanding visa requirements and legal necessities is vital for digital nomads, and they must research the countries that support the digital nomad lifestyle with visas.", "citations": {"4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Project management software, such as ClickUp, can help remote teams unite and work efficiently, and offers features such as Gantt Charts, time estimation, and planning.", "citations": {"4da88c2e-7272-4f4e-9fb0-62813b55fce7_122186681": 1.0}}, {"text": "Collaboration platforms, such as Slack, can facilitate team operations and provide separate chat rooms for small talk, helping to encourage team bonding.", "citations": {"579faf84-de39-4ffc-aa4a-a6b0d10cd305_506889674": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the digital nomad lifestyle presents both challenges and advantages, but with the right tools and strategies, it can be a productive and fulfilling experience.", "citations": {"4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390": 1.0}}], "references": ["213bf97f-947f-4930-b7a6-7d7ab14f2ac9_385431892", "a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641", "2ec94e79-be7d-4bbd-bbda-d553fb44e0b0_711412342", "16bff253-f821-4c36-ae1e-566843a4046b_322133742", "249b8018-b83e-458c-be07-418fce10c28b_986701262", "2cd59861-ef91-41c1-a09b-2492f149c4ba_498963821", "579faf84-de39-4ffc-aa4a-a6b0d10cd305_506889674", "fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379", "b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_37536649", "088e0346-91bf-43fd-b68c-748ae1e1247f_998032520", "4da88c2e-7272-4f4e-9fb0-62813b55fce7_122186681", "f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_256892267", "ea127547-3f76-481b-8ea0-e7d7d8b7832e_116322958", "24b6312b-e15a-4c0d-9e24-184ea04376b4_218045225", "151f3688-882b-4c8a-8195-f7bb6ba13d3b_420890211", "422cd2de-cbe5-4f2b-a201-d5a13b8447ab_536909040", "23980c8b-8970-4b9b-96ce-6f690a62ec45_787468909", "569e7af2-fa30-48de-b472-f064c6307db7_43064042", "4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390", "2060cd19-2a64-4537-987d-dc20f718a8a9_575680989", "5750ba90-82b8-4b5a-8c4c-36fa3f02c29b_808221478", "832c6fe0-2321-4541-a285-f596085d29da_464005243", "1e3a8772-07f1-43e0-8e22-8968a02bec12_797696511", "5b5734d4-7823-40dc-af7c-5d514d5b8e87_903041797"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1005", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle, involving remote work while traveling, is growing and being supported by specialized visas in many countries.", "citations": {"23980c8b-8970-4b9b-96ce-6f690a62ec45_787468909": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomadism is a lifestyle of remote work and travel, offering high income and global location freedom.", "citations": {"495a3813-6b54-48f9-a9d3-18b74a1a72df_561526741": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads work in fields like software development and content creation, driving innovation and experiencing multiculturalism.", "citations": {"495a3813-6b54-48f9-a9d3-18b74a1a72df_561526741": 1.0}}, {"text": "A digital nomad is someone who works remotely and travels, needing a work-life balance for productivity and well-being.", "citations": {"4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads face challenges like productivity, healthcare, and finances, requiring careful planning and research.", "citations": {"4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390": 1.0}}, {"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle offers freedom and flexibility to live and work from anywhere with a stable internet connection.", "citations": {"77fe7fbf-41e8-4067-9063-0458ea76d448_158447245": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads prioritize balance between work and life, seeking comfortable environments with strong work support.", "citations": {"77fe7fbf-41e8-4067-9063-0458ea76d448_158447245": 1.0}}, {"text": "About 45% of global digital nomads stay in one place for one to three months, requiring flexible leasing and public facilities.", "citations": {"90884408-0e81-4e82-b05c-6d5e3880f722_235045315": 1.0}}, {"text": "Countries like Germany, Estonia, Malta, Bahamas, Cyprus, and Thailand offer digital nomad visas with varying requirements.", "citations": {"088e0346-91bf-43fd-b68c-748ae1e1247f_998032520": 1.0}}, {"text": "Japan's digital nomad visa requires a six-month residency, $68,000 annual income, and private health insurance, targeting highly qualified IT specialists.", "citations": {"0be60a3e-b6c5-4420-9ef2-c97b0bd0919f_600996491": 1.0}}, {"text": "South Korea offers a two-year digital nomad visa requiring an annual income of $66,000.", "citations": {"0be60a3e-b6c5-4420-9ef2-c97b0bd0919f_600996491": 1.0}}, {"text": "Spain's digital nomad visa requires a \u20ac2,200 monthly income, higher education diploma, employment contract, and health insurance.", "citations": {"b5783503-8224-44ea-b6b6-b462a9b6e5c4_585544854": 1.0}}, {"text": "Portugal's digital nomad visa requires \u20ac700 monthly, whereas Iceland's requires \u20ac7,100, and Croatia's digital nomad visa lasts up to one year, requires a \u20ac2,300 monthly income.", "citations": {"c99adb91-64a7-454a-a41a-1cd3415fae92_617034367": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads use tools like Egenda, Google Tasks, Trello, Freedom, and Todoist to track tasks, prioritize assignments, and manage workflow.", "citations": {"0bca9ef1-893e-48ec-8303-4980711ba3e0_302121846": 1.0}}, {"text": "Trello integrates apps and sets timers, while Todoist provides task overviews.", "citations": {"0bca9ef1-893e-48ec-8303-4980711ba3e0_302121846": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can use devices like the Microsoft Surface 4 Pro laptop with GlocalMe U3 WiFi Hotspot for a stable internet connection.", "citations": {"23980c8b-8970-4b9b-96ce-6f690a62ec45_787468909": 1.0}}], "references": ["77fe7fbf-41e8-4067-9063-0458ea76d448_158447245", "0bca9ef1-893e-48ec-8303-4980711ba3e0_302121846", "c99adb91-64a7-454a-a41a-1cd3415fae92_617034367", "088e0346-91bf-43fd-b68c-748ae1e1247f_998032520", "495a3813-6b54-48f9-a9d3-18b74a1a72df_561526741", "23980c8b-8970-4b9b-96ce-6f690a62ec45_787468909", "90884408-0e81-4e82-b05c-6d5e3880f722_235045315", "4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390", "0be60a3e-b6c5-4420-9ef2-c97b0bd0919f_600996491", "b5783503-8224-44ea-b6b6-b462a9b6e5c4_585544854"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1006", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle involves traveling while working remotely from laptops, and many countries are now offering digital nomad visas to support this lifestyle.", "citations": {"088e0346-91bf-43fd-b68c-748ae1e1247f_998032520": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads enjoy more family time and travel opportunities, and the Covid-19 pandemic accelerated the adoption of the remote work lifestyle.", "citations": {"23980c8b-8970-4b9b-96ce-6f690a62ec45_787468909": 1.0}}, {"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle offers cultural exploration and professional growth, but working abroad has complex visa application processes.", "citations": {"255cffed-9128-4d3c-aeb9-60ac4940c381_592587899": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads have high income and freedom benefits, and they work remotely with flexibility, with 35 million people expected to join the digital nomad community by 2022.", "citations": {"495a3813-6b54-48f9-a9d3-18b74a1a72df_561526741": 1.0}}, {"text": "One of the challenges faced by digital nomads is balancing work and school commitments, and access to healthcare is essential for them.", "citations": {"4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads may experience homesickness, especially internationally, and time management is critical to avoid burnout as a digital nomad.", "citations": {"4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390": 1.0}}, {"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle can be tiring, exhausting, and uncertain, but it allows for personal growth and self-discovery.", "citations": {"66a58391-3a62-480f-be64-9b2280bbe834_951964714": 1.0}}, {"text": "There are nearly 11 million people who identified as digital nomads in 2020, and the lifestyle can lead to a loss of cultural and national identity.", "citations": {"66a58391-3a62-480f-be64-9b2280bbe834_951964714": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads work remotely, often as programmers, writers, or designers, and they prioritize freedom, minimalism, and experiences over material possessions.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0}}, {"text": "The most attractive locations for digital nomads include Chiang Mai, Bali, and Lisbon, and digital nomad visas allow individuals to stay in countries longer than tourists.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads often rely on coworking and coliving spaces for community and infrastructure, and governments are concerned about the economic impact of digital nomadism on domestic economies.", "citations": {"72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads face financial challenges due to unpredictability, and having a stable debit card is crucial for them.", "citations": {"a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641": 1.0}}, {"text": "Researching local prices is essential for digital nomads, and tax requirements vary by country for them.", "citations": {"a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomad visas can offer tax relief or exemption, and a \"slow digital nomad\" lifestyle can help with budgeting.", "citations": {"a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641": 1.0}}, {"text": "Building a \"base camp\" can provide stability for digital nomads, and remote desktop storage enables access to work computers from anywhere.", "citations": {"b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_37536649": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads face challenges like connectivity issues and productivity, but remote desktop software helps address these challenges and increase productivity.", "citations": {"b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_37536649": 1.0}}, {"text": "Flexibility and freedom are key benefits of the digital nomad lifestyle, and remote desktop tools provide secure access to files without syncing or transferring.", "citations": {"b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_37536649": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can infuse a financial boost into the host country, but they can also push housing costs higher locally.", "citations": {"c7b767c9-09fd-43c7-83f7-b07f61e38ae6_818229618": 1.0}}, {"text": "Local residents often resent the presence of digital nomads, but volunteering helps digital nomads integrate with locals.", "citations": {"c7b767c9-09fd-43c7-83f7-b07f61e38ae6_818229618": 1.0}}, {"text": "Several countries offer special visas for digital nomads, and digital nomads can benefit local businesses by spending.", "citations": {"c7b767c9-09fd-43c7-83f7-b07f61e38ae6_818229618": 1.0}}, {"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle boomed since COVID-19, and 50 countries offer specific visas for digital nomads.", "citations": {"ea90bb4e-0607-4636-afd5-5e325bcbfef8_77576442": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can exacerbate gentrification and housing crisis, and Mexico City's housing market became unaffordable for locals due to digital nomads.", "citations": {"ea90bb4e-0607-4636-afd5-5e325bcbfef8_77576442": 1.0}}, {"text": "High-speed internet and freelancing drive digital nomad growth, and digital nomads can stay in one place for weeks, months, or years.", "citations": {"ea90bb4e-0607-4636-afd5-5e325bcbfef8_77576442": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can work remotely with a laptop and stable network, and low costs in Southeast Asia make it a popular spot for digital nomads.", "citations": {"f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_256892267": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads can work in various fields like freelancing, online teaching, and design, and the Web3.0 industry allows for remote work with international companies.", "citations": {"f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_256892267": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads need self-discipline to maintain their lifestyle, and remote work can be done from anywhere with a computer and internet.", "citations": {"f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_256892267": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomadism grew since the Coronavirus pandemic, and young people often adopt the digital nomad lifestyle.", "citations": {"fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379": 1.0}}, {"text": "Governments offer temporary visas to attract digital nomads, and countries issue visas to compensate for tourism loss.", "citations": {"fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379": 1.0}}, {"text": "Some countries attract digital nomads for skilled labor, and Cape Town is Africa's digital nomadic capital.", "citations": {"fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379": 1.0}}, {"text": "High-speed internet is crucial for digital nomads, and Malta and Croatia offer visas for digital nomads.", "citations": {"fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379": 1.0}}, {"text": "Malaysia offers a digital nomad visa with a $24,000 income requirement, allowing for a 3-12 month stay.", "citations": {"088e0346-91bf-43fd-b68c-748ae1e1247f_998032520": 1.0}}, {"text": "Estonia, Malta, Bahamas, Cyprus, and Thailand also offer digital nomad visas, although the specific requirements for these countries are not detailed.", "citations": {"088e0346-91bf-43fd-b68c-748ae1e1247f_998032520": 1.0}}, {"text": "Japan has introduced a digital nomad visa program, aiming to create a convenient environment for digital workers, with an estimated 35 million digital nomads existing worldwide.", "citations": {"09cbaa0c-5e42-4814-a1a1-3e28d939b1c4_202321090": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Japanese digital nomad visa requires an annual income of $68,300 and allows for a 6-month stay, with eligibility limited to citizens of tax agreement countries.", "citations": {"0be60a3e-b6c5-4420-9ef2-c97b0bd0919f_600996491": 1.0}}, {"text": "US, Australian, and Singaporean citizens are eligible for Japan's digital nomad visa, while Russians are not.", "citations": {"0be60a3e-b6c5-4420-9ef2-c97b0bd0919f_600996491": 1.0}}, {"text": "South Korea also offers a digital nomad visa, introduced in January, with a $66,000 income requirement.", "citations": {"0be60a3e-b6c5-4420-9ef2-c97b0bd0919f_600996491": 1.0}}, {"text": "Applicants for Japan's digital nomad visa must have private health insurance and can bring spouses and children with private medical insurance.", "citations": {"15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219": 1.0}}, {"text": "The visa allows remote work for foreign companies or self-employment, and YouTube bloggers with overseas income are also eligible.", "citations": {"2859f8ca-8608-4fca-9f8c-a999cd159cc8_459273502": 1.0}}, {"text": "Japan's digital nomad visa can be extended after six months outside Japan, but applicants are not eligible for residence permits.", "citations": {"2859f8ca-8608-4fca-9f8c-a999cd159cc8_459273502": 1.0}}, {"text": "Spain offers a digital nomad visa with specific requirements, including a passport with entry stamp, certificate of no criminal record, and diploma of higher education.", "citations": {"b5783503-8224-44ea-b6b6-b462a9b6e5c4_585544854": 1.0}}, {"text": "Croatia offers digital nomad visas for up to one year, with a minimum monthly income required of \u20ac2,300.", "citations": {"c529ac8d-80af-410a-a327-3546b54a14c8_242137462": 1.0}}, {"text": "Iceland's digital nomad visa requires a minimum monthly income of over \u20ac6,000, while the Czech Republic's digital nomad visa can be extended for up to three years.", "citations": {"c529ac8d-80af-410a-a327-3546b54a14c8_242137462": 1.0}}, {"text": "Portugal requires a monthly income of \u20ac700 for its digital nomad visa, and Spain requires a monthly income of \u20ac2,000.", "citations": {"c99adb91-64a7-454a-a41a-1cd3415fae92_617034367": 1.0}}, {"text": "Around 10,000 digital nomads stay in Croatia every month, and digital nomads can apply for a new visa after six months outside Croatia.", "citations": {"c529ac8d-80af-410a-a327-3546b54a14c8_242137462": 1.0}}, {"text": "Japan requires private health insurance for digital nomads and targets IT professionals and highly skilled professionals with its digital nomad visa.", "citations": {"ec9e942a-2b47-4552-9825-4e206606823c_696735006": 1.0}}, {"text": "Thailand offers a 10-year resident permit for remote workers, requiring an $80,000 annual salary or $40,000 with a master's degree.", "citations": {"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_427630041": 1.0}}, {"text": "Malaysia offers temporary residence through its \"De Rantau Nomad\" program, requiring a $24,000 annual income for digital nomads.", "citations": {"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_427630041": 1.0}}, {"text": "South Korea offers a \"Workcation\" visa with a two-year validity, requiring a minimum income threshold of KRW 85,000,000.", "citations": {"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_427630041": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads work remotely and travel often, requiring a range of tools and technologies to stay productive and connected.", "citations": {"4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390": 1.0}}, {"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle involves working from anywhere, and mobile hotspots, such as GlocalMe U3 WiFi Hotspot, ensure a stable internet connection.", "citations": {"23980c8b-8970-4b9b-96ce-6f690a62ec45_787468909": 1.0}}, {"text": "Noise-canceling headphones, like Beats Studio Earbuds, aid productivity by providing balanced sound and minimizing distractions.", "citations": {"23980c8b-8970-4b9b-96ce-6f690a62ec45_787468909": 1.0}}, {"text": "A good laptop setup, such as the Microsoft Surface 4 Pro, is necessary for work and school, and portable workstations like Worky Home Office desk can help digital nomads stay focused.", "citations": {"23980c8b-8970-4b9b-96ce-6f690a62ec45_787468909": 1.0}}, {"text": "Designated workspaces and time management are crucial for balancing work and school, and routine builds consistency in daily activities.", "citations": {"4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Prioritizing tasks and eliminating distractions are essential for productivity, and remote work options include tutoring, content writing, and other digital careers.", "citations": {"4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390": 1.0}}, {"text": "Citizen Remote is a tool that guides visa applications and procedures for digital nomads, offering a one-stop-shop for remote work visas worldwide.", "citations": {"255cffed-9128-4d3c-aeb9-60ac4940c381_592587899": 1.0}}, {"text": "Citizen Remote also provides verified rental properties for long-term accommodation, global health insurance with adjustable coverage, and a social network feature for connecting users.", "citations": {"255cffed-9128-4d3c-aeb9-60ac4940c381_592587899": 1.0}}, {"text": "Splashtop is a remote access software that offers robust security features, advanced compression technology, and support for 4K streaming and 60fps.", "citations": {"2d71c373-b971-42ef-9f1c-b79d9c1d5088_610946698": 1.0}}, {"text": "Trello, Slack, and Zoom are essential tools for remote teams, enabling collaboration, communication, and project management.", "citations": {"2d71c373-b971-42ef-9f1c-b79d9c1d5088_610946698": 1.0}}, {"text": "Regular check-ins and communication are critical for remote employee engagement, and video communication is 34 times more efficient than email communication.", "citations": {"2d71c373-b971-42ef-9f1c-b79d9c1d5088_610946698": 1.0}}, {"text": "Establishing clear expectations and goals is essential for remote employees, and providing comprehensive technical support is critical for their success.", "citations": {"2d71c373-b971-42ef-9f1c-b79d9c1d5088_610946698": 1.0}}, {"text": "Encouraging social interaction is important for remote employee morale, and promoting health and well-being is critical for their productivity.", "citations": {"2d71c373-b971-42ef-9f1c-b79d9c1d5088_610946698": 1.0}}, {"text": "Indeed, ZipRecruiter, FlexJobs, and RemoteOK are platforms that can help digital nomads find remote work opportunities, and LinkedIn is a prime spot for companies to post open jobs and recruit employees.", "citations": {"70c08b22-6ff6-4779-8c32-2cae86f3c67d_869875129": 1.0}}, {"text": "Facebook Groups and Handshake can also be used to recruit remote employees, especially for part-time and freelance roles.", "citations": {"70c08b22-6ff6-4779-8c32-2cae86f3c67d_869875129": 1.0}}, {"text": "High-speed internet is non-negotiable for digital nomads, and functional spaces with dedicated office areas are preferred.", "citations": {"90884408-0e81-4e82-b05c-6d5e3880f722_235045315": 1.0}}, {"text": "Flexible leasing options, access to nature, and community and co-living options can provide networking opportunities and elevate the remote work experience.", "citations": {"90884408-0e81-4e82-b05c-6d5e3880f722_235045315": 1.0}}, {"text": "Remote work uses digital tools for collaboration and task management, and Zoom and Slack are common communication platforms for remote work.", "citations": {"a673244c-03e7-49e9-9aec-6e6c8bc5e44c_948910508": 1.0}}, {"text": "Trello and Asana are project management software for remote work, and Splashtop is a remote desktop solution for secure access.", "citations": {"a673244c-03e7-49e9-9aec-6e6c8bc5e44c_948910508": 1.0}}, {"text": "Remote desktop software enables remote access to workstations, and cross-platform compatibility is a key feature of remote desktop software.", "citations": {"a673244c-03e7-49e9-9aec-6e6c8bc5e44c_948910508": 1.0}}, {"text": "Robust security features protect sensitive data during remote work, and regular software updates prevent vulnerabilities in remote work.", "citations": {"a673244c-03e7-49e9-9aec-6e6c8bc5e44c_948910508": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital nomads use remote technology to work from anywhere, and remote desktop storage is crucial for accessing files and resources.", "citations": {"b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_37536649": 1.0}}, {"text": "Splashtop offers remote desktop solutions for digital nomads, providing secure file access without syncing and overcoming travel unpredictability.", "citations": {"b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_37536649": 1.0}}, {"text": "Choosing the right remote desktop tool is critical for benefits, and Spl", "citations": {}}], "references": ["70c08b22-6ff6-4779-8c32-2cae86f3c67d_869875129", "495a3813-6b54-48f9-a9d3-18b74a1a72df_561526741", "b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_37536649", "66a58391-3a62-480f-be64-9b2280bbe834_951964714", "4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390", "ec9e942a-2b47-4552-9825-4e206606823c_696735006", "a673244c-03e7-49e9-9aec-6e6c8bc5e44c_948910508", "2859f8ca-8608-4fca-9f8c-a999cd159cc8_459273502", "088e0346-91bf-43fd-b68c-748ae1e1247f_998032520", "c7b767c9-09fd-43c7-83f7-b07f61e38ae6_818229618", "72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748", "23980c8b-8970-4b9b-96ce-6f690a62ec45_787468909", "a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641", "ea90bb4e-0607-4636-afd5-5e325bcbfef8_77576442", "f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_256892267", "255cffed-9128-4d3c-aeb9-60ac4940c381_592587899", "2d71c373-b971-42ef-9f1c-b79d9c1d5088_610946698", "f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_427630041", "09cbaa0c-5e42-4814-a1a1-3e28d939b1c4_202321090", "c99adb91-64a7-454a-a41a-1cd3415fae92_617034367", "15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219", "b5783503-8224-44ea-b6b6-b462a9b6e5c4_585544854", "90884408-0e81-4e82-b05c-6d5e3880f722_235045315", "c529ac8d-80af-410a-a327-3546b54a14c8_242137462", "fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379", "0be60a3e-b6c5-4420-9ef2-c97b0bd0919f_600996491"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1007", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The J-10 fighter jet has been exported to countries including Pakistan, which bought 36 J-10CE fighters.", "citations": {"a834da70-5664-4631-bba7-dba8ef82cd52_942464069": 1.0}}, {"text": "Pakistan has received 12 J-10C fighter jets from China.", "citations": {"3ec181a2-af55-4af9-aeb3-8720edd1498e_711423819": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Pakistan Air Force has inducted the J-10C to boost its combat capabilities.", "citations": {"3ec181a2-af55-4af9-aeb3-8720edd1498e_711423819": 1.0}}, {"text": "Egypt and Turkey, along with Pakistan, have shown interest in purchasing the J-10C fighter jet.", "citations": {"613a83ef-3b15-4765-854b-5d60ed7cc56c_379388153": 1.0, "7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_1044319203": 0.5}}, {"text": "Sudan has become the second buyer of China's J-10C fighter jets, after Pakistan.", "citations": {"9e893a13-a5bb-4822-8f87-187cba831d3d_453477269": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has received positive feedback, with Pakistan's Air Force expecting it to be an elite fighter.", "citations": {"ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C outperforms the F-16 with its advanced avionics and lower operating cost.", "citations": {"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_115461755": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C is a multi-role fighter with a 2,500km range and 1.9-ton payload.", "citations": {"3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C can track 10 targets and engage 4 simultaneously using its phased array radar.", "citations": {"3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has undergone significant upgrades, including new avionics and network-centric warfare capabilities.", "citations": {"ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C features reduced radar cross section, low-visibility coating, and electronic warfare countermeasures to enhance its combat survivability.", "citations": {"ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has been praised for its high-altitude, high-speed performance and maneuverability.", "citations": {"855ab901-32d2-49c8-b179-311d41c4a12f_597420948": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10 has major design and capability flaws, including limited AESA radar power and poor maneuverability compared to the Rafale.", "citations": {"855ab901-32d2-49c8-b179-311d41c4a12f_597420948": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C is a 4.5-generation medium-sized fighter jet with improved combat capabilities.", "citations": {"cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Pakistan Air Force has used the J-10C in combat, including air raids on eastern Iran.", "citations": {"99024cc3-a59f-4943-8b5d-dfcabf47135e_778752357": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has been used in joint operations with the JF-17.", "citations": {"99024cc3-a59f-4943-8b5d-dfcabf47135e_778752357": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C is a highly capable fighter jet popular in the export market, particularly in Pakistan, due to its AESA radars and fourth-generation air-to-air missiles.", "citations": {"ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561": 1.0, "cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815": 0.5}}, {"text": "The J-10C's advanced avionics and electronic warfare capabilities make it a desirable option for countries upgrading their air forces.", "citations": {"ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561": 1.0}}], "references": ["9e893a13-a5bb-4822-8f87-187cba831d3d_453477269", "7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_1044319203", "a834da70-5664-4631-bba7-dba8ef82cd52_942464069", "613a83ef-3b15-4765-854b-5d60ed7cc56c_379388153", "ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561", "7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_115461755", "99024cc3-a59f-4943-8b5d-dfcabf47135e_778752357", "3ec181a2-af55-4af9-aeb3-8720edd1498e_711423819", "3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939", "cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815", "855ab901-32d2-49c8-b179-311d41c4a12f_597420948"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1008", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The J-10 fighter jet has been exported to several countries, including Pakistan, which has purchased 35-40 J-10Cs for $1.5 billion, with each J-10C costing around $390 million.", "citations": {"558e844a-b52a-4f3a-8553-1ab6b696cb94_230889465": 1.0}}, {"text": "Pakistan's purchase of the J-10C is aimed at countering India's Rafale fighter jets, and the J-10C is equipped with the PL-15 long-range air-to-air missile.", "citations": {"558e844a-b52a-4f3a-8553-1ab6b696cb94_230889465": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sudan is also planning to buy the J-10C fighter from China, with the export price estimated at 40 million US dollars, and the purchase is aimed at countering India's fighters.", "citations": {"9e893a13-a5bb-4822-8f87-187cba831d3d_453477269": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has active phased array radar, which enhances its capabilities, and Pakistan has procured 36 J-10CE fighters, which is the export model of the J-10C.", "citations": {"a834da70-5664-4631-bba7-dba8ef82cd52_942464069": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has lower operating costs than the F-16, requires less maintenance, and has a faster delivery time, making it an attractive option for countries looking to replace their F-16s.", "citations": {"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_115461755": 1.0}}, {"text": "Turkey is considering the J-10 as a replacement for its F-16s, and the J-10C is seen as a competitor to the US F-15 and F-16 fighters.", "citations": {"3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939": 1.0}}, {"text": "Egypt is in talks with China to purchase the J-10C multirole fighter, as the country seeks to diversify its weapons supplies from the US and Russia.", "citations": {"613a83ef-3b15-4765-854b-5d60ed7cc56c_379388153": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia is also discussing large arms sales with a Chinese state-run company, which may include the purchase of unmanned reconnaissance aircraft, air defense systems, and possibly the J-10 fighter jet.", "citations": {"613a83ef-3b15-4765-854b-5d60ed7cc56c_379388153": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has multiple features and performance advantages over the F-16, including a lower operating cost and improved fifth-generation avionics.", "citations": {"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_115461755": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C has a bigger AESA radar than the JF-17 Block 3 and can carry fourth-generation air-to-air missiles, making it a more powerful option than the JF-17 fighter jet.", "citations": {"cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815": 1.0}}, {"text": "China will deliver 25 J-10C fighter jets to Pakistan, which will improve the Pakistan Air Force's combat capabilities and strengthen the Pakistani military's combat capabilities.", "citations": {"cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815": 1.0}}, {"text": "The J-10C promotes China's aviation equipment exports and serves the regional security interests of China, increasing Pakistan's military capability to defend its airspace.", "citations": {"cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, there is limited feedback available from countries like Egypt, Turkey, and Saudi Arabia regarding their experience with the J-10 fighter jet, as they have not yet completed their purchases or have not made their evaluations public.", "citations": {"613a83ef-3b15-4765-854b-5d60ed7cc56c_379388153": 1.0, "a4923ccc-5436-43fb-bf81-5027a3063a3a_117203148": 0.5, "a834da70-5664-4631-bba7-dba8ef82cd52_942464069": 0.25}}, {"text": "The J-10A has been criticized for its poor reliability and export performance, but the J-10C is seen as an improved version with better radar and avionics.", "citations": {"a834da70-5664-4631-bba7-dba8ef82cd52_942464069": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Chinese J-10C has been compared favorably to the F-16, with a lower cost and improved performance, making it an attractive option for countries looking to upgrade their air forces.", "citations": {"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_115461755": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the J-10C is seen as a cost-effective and capable fighter jet, with several countries considering its purchase, and its operational costs and effectiveness have significant implications for countries looking to enhance their military capabilities.", "citations": {"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_115461755": 1.0}}], "references": ["3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939", "613a83ef-3b15-4765-854b-5d60ed7cc56c_379388153", "a4923ccc-5436-43fb-bf81-5027a3063a3a_117203148", "cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815", "9e893a13-a5bb-4822-8f87-187cba831d3d_453477269", "558e844a-b52a-4f3a-8553-1ab6b696cb94_230889465", "a834da70-5664-4631-bba7-dba8ef82cd52_942464069", "7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_115461755"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1009", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Saharan dust storms can limit tropical cyclone development over the Atlantic, affecting North American climate.", "citations": {"0578f2f7-286b-4a58-9591-27af4f4fabcd_10997942": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saharan Air Layer prevents tropical moisture from entering the Atlantic, inhibiting storm development.", "citations": {"270add43-f80a-4e9c-b485-5fe6a47a33f4_186258722": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust affects North American climate indirectly and has a variable impact on South American climates.", "citations": {"270add43-f80a-4e9c-b485-5fe6a47a33f4_186258722": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sahara dust storms carry harmful bacteria and fungi globally into North America.", "citations": {"958ae1ee-19d5-41c4-8e42-0583f3ed6841_957102541": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust fertilizes the Amazon rainforest and the Caribbean Sea, providing essential nutrients.", "citations": {"847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659": 1.0}}, {"text": "The dust can disrupt environments, affect public health, and harm corals.", "citations": {"958ae1ee-19d5-41c4-8e42-0583f3ed6841_957102541": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust storms can cause respiratory issues and have significant economic impacts on San Antonio, TX.", "citations": {"135649f4-82c4-4bc9-903a-9d935421ea27_1026921352": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust contains iron, silica, fungi, bacteria, and viruses, which can exacerbate respiratory illnesses like asthma in San Antonio.", "citations": {"135649f4-82c4-4bc9-903a-9d935421ea27_1026921352": 1.0}}, {"text": "To mitigate Saharan dust storms, people can avoid outdoor activity, close windows and doors, and use air purifiers.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "A warning system can help people, especially those with allergies or respiratory issues, prepare for and minimize exposure to Saharan dust.", "citations": {"54c42d43-5691-4a18-a63f-3c936ecb10cc_86116201": 1.0}}, {"text": "City planners in San Antonio, TX, can develop mitigation strategies with local businesses to minimize weather-related service disruptions.", "citations": {"f887d2c1-bc5e-4758-b3dc-38c4dd2d780a_530029982": 1.0}}, {"text": "The city's power grid and traffic infrastructure can be optimized to respond to Saharan dust storms by implementing efficient systems like those in the UAE.", "citations": {"3b88f522-d063-4cb8-80f7-6fade6bd8e6e_585914125": 1.0}}, {"text": "Dust storms can cause power outages, reduce visibility, and disrupt air and road transport.", "citations": {"1fd604e6-30ba-4b91-b53c-ecb5241f2624_55169144": 1.0}}, {"text": "The city's emergency management systems can be optimized to support citizens with respiratory issues by issuing air quality warnings and guidance on reducing dust exposure.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "San Antonio can mitigate Saharan dust storms by implementing early warning systems, reducing air pollution, and promoting land restoration planning.", "citations": {"356cb856-b58c-4369-bc75-dc38b8bf07b5_573345250": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust storms significantly impact weather, air, public health, ecosystems, and economies in the Americas.", "citations": {"958ae1ee-19d5-41c4-8e42-0583f3ed6841_957102541": 1.0}}], "references": ["135649f4-82c4-4bc9-903a-9d935421ea27_1026921352", "f887d2c1-bc5e-4758-b3dc-38c4dd2d780a_530029982", "356cb856-b58c-4369-bc75-dc38b8bf07b5_573345250", "0578f2f7-286b-4a58-9591-27af4f4fabcd_10997942", "958ae1ee-19d5-41c4-8e42-0583f3ed6841_957102541", "847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659", "1fd604e6-30ba-4b91-b53c-ecb5241f2624_55169144", "3b88f522-d063-4cb8-80f7-6fade6bd8e6e_585914125", "5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364", "270add43-f80a-4e9c-b485-5fe6a47a33f4_186258722", "54c42d43-5691-4a18-a63f-3c936ecb10cc_86116201"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1010", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Saharan dust storms have been known to impact weather and air conditions in the Americas, including San Antonio, Texas, with the dust typically arriving in late June through mid-August.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "The dust from these storms contains iron, silica, fungi, bacteria, and viruses, which can cause respiratory diseases and allergies, as well as affect coral reefs and various crops.", "citations": {"135649f4-82c4-4bc9-903a-9d935421ea27_1026921352": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust storms can decrease rainfall and increase heat, and also cause skin problems and other health issues, making it essential for the city of San Antonio to prepare for their arrival.", "citations": {"135649f4-82c4-4bc9-903a-9d935421ea27_1026921352": 1.0}}, {"text": "The city can expect the dust to cause hazy skies and breathing issues, and affect air quality levels, which can be mitigated through public education campaigns and alerts.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "Residents with respiratory illnesses, such as asthma and COPD, should stay indoors during dust storms, avoid outdoor activities, and keep windows and doors closed to minimize exposure.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "The city of San Antonio can effectively communicate with residents and visitors about the arrival and potential impacts of Saharan dust storms through local weather reports and public education campaigns.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saharan dust storms can also cause vibrant sunrises and sunsets, which can be a positive impact, but residents and visitors should still be aware of the potential health risks.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "To minimize the disruption of traffic and transportation in San Antonio during Saharan dust storms, drivers should turn on their lights for safety, avoid sudden stops, and maintain a sufficient distance between vehicles.", "citations": {"4aea4334-dd2b-49d0-bcd9-c49f2f6beaa9_837338705": 1.0}}, {"text": "The city can also use Doppler radar to track dust storms and provide updates to residents and visitors on the potential impacts and necessary precautions.", "citations": {"d791a512-e3fd-43f0-898e-9a3de6be630e_858476001": 1.0}}, {"text": "In terms of power grid resilience, the city of San Antonio can implement measures such as grid modernization, underground power lines, and energy storage systems to mitigate the impact of Saharan dust storms.", "citations": {"e5d96f1c-f3b7-42d7-a26a-4a23826aec16_500780036": 1.0}}, {"text": "The city can also promote the use of renewable energy sources, such as solar and wind power, to reduce reliance on traditional energy sources and improve grid resilience.", "citations": {"1629b01a-9350-447d-bc0f-da7d8573399b_650528848": 1.0}}, {"text": "To protect vulnerable populations, such as those with respiratory issues, during Saharan dust storms, health institutions can be prepared with emergency services and medical supplies, and residents can be advised to stay indoors and avoid exposure.", "citations": {"008c4763-6eab-431b-83b6-7a6fe6b4d0ce_182181117": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Minister of Health can alert health institutions to be prepared for suffocation cases during dust storms, and emergency services and medicines can be made readily available.", "citations": {"008c4763-6eab-431b-83b6-7a6fe6b4d0ce_182181117": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the city of San Antonio can take proactive measures to mitigate the impacts of Saharan dust storms on its power grid, traffic, and citizens' health, and ensure that residents and visitors are aware of the potential risks and necessary precautions.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "By implementing these measures, the city can reduce the negative impacts of Saharan dust storms and promote a safer and healthier environment for its residents and visitors.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "The city's emergency response plans and protocols can be designed to address the specific needs of vulnerable populations, such as those with respiratory issues, and ensure that they receive the necessary medical attention and care during dust storms.", "citations": {"008c4763-6eab-431b-83b6-7a6fe6b4d0ce_182181117": 1.0}}, {"text": "By working together, the city of San Antonio can minimize the disruption caused by Saharan dust storms and promote a resilient and sustainable community.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "The city can also learn from other cities and countries that have experienced similar dust storms and implement best practices to mitigate their impacts.", "citations": {"f52c74df-55f4-4425-93cc-499619ed942b_968981722": 1.0}}, {"text": "By taking a proactive and collaborative approach, the city of San Antonio can reduce the risks associated with Saharan dust storms and promote a healthier and more sustainable environment for its residents and visitors.", "citations": {"5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364": 1.0}}, {"text": "[2] [3] [10] [31] [39] [50] [56].", "citations": {"f52c74df-55f4-4425-93cc-499619ed942b_968981722": 1.0}}], "references": ["e5d96f1c-f3b7-42d7-a26a-4a23826aec16_500780036", "1629b01a-9350-447d-bc0f-da7d8573399b_650528848", "f52c74df-55f4-4425-93cc-499619ed942b_968981722", "d791a512-e3fd-43f0-898e-9a3de6be630e_858476001", "135649f4-82c4-4bc9-903a-9d935421ea27_1026921352", "4aea4334-dd2b-49d0-bcd9-c49f2f6beaa9_837338705", "5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364", "008c4763-6eab-431b-83b6-7a6fe6b4d0ce_182181117"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1011", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Mohammed bin Salman has introduced social and economic reforms in Saudi Arabia since 2017 to diversify the economy and reduce its dependence on oil.", "citations": {"17686725-e6b2-42b7-ad90-e1d73dd68a8b_845745419": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saudi economy grew 8.7% in 2022, making it the fastest-growing G20 economy.", "citations": {"11ad698b-5e86-461f-9f75-1f94496e7dd4_1019313503": 1.0}}, {"text": "The non-oil sector grew 4.9% in 2023 and 8.4% in 2022, its best in ten years.", "citations": {"11ad698b-5e86-461f-9f75-1f94496e7dd4_1019313503": 1.0, "3ba8171a-5025-4b71-b03e-3be6260dfef4_239396021": 0.5}}, {"text": "Mohammed bin Salman's Vision 2030 aims to diversify the economy and improve citizens' quality of life through economic reforms.", "citations": {"90eaba16-a74f-4ca0-bf0e-7ba9c5adc602_617175124": 1.0}}, {"text": "The reforms have led to an increase in foreign investment, with over 800 opportunities worth one trillion riyals identified.", "citations": {"90eaba16-a74f-4ca0-bf0e-7ba9c5adc602_617175124": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has restricted the powers of the Wahhabi establishment, including the Commission for Promotion of Virtue.", "citations": {"2e03709c-a0f2-49c3-a204-0c5ebe79580e_315280229": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Commission's powers were stripped in 2016, and it now focuses on awareness campaigns, and MBS has limited the religious police's role and plans to recruit women to the Commission.", "citations": {"2e03709c-a0f2-49c3-a204-0c5ebe79580e_315280229": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saudi Entertainment Authority, led by Turki Al-Sheikh, has opened Saudi Arabia to music and dancing under MBS.", "citations": {"339272fc-3a19-449c-9773-432deaa8ab3d_356121651": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS's reforms have shifted Saudi Arabia away from Wahhabi doctrine towards moderate Islam.", "citations": {"339272fc-3a19-449c-9773-432deaa8ab3d_356121651": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women's labor market participation has increased from 18% to 37% since 2017.", "citations": {"11ad698b-5e86-461f-9f75-1f94496e7dd4_1019313503": 1.0}}, {"text": "Unemployment rates have decreased, with the overall rate at 8% in 2022 and a 13.7% drop in female unemployment in 2023.", "citations": {"11ad698b-5e86-461f-9f75-1f94496e7dd4_1019313503": 1.0, "8bf4b324-0fa4-4953-b361-028af7597974_481978147": 0.5}}, {"text": "The government has implemented reforms, including abolishing the male guardianship system, and has allowed women to drive and work.", "citations": {"521ac676-eb0a-4808-8618-33cf0a1f7330_270127309": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, Saudi Arabia restricts non-Muslim worship and beliefs, treating freedom of religion as a state-granted privilege.", "citations": {"85f8e514-d127-49df-8b2e-76a051ef8d32_25925039": 1.0}}, {"text": "The international community has responded to MBS's reforms with a mix of praise and criticism, with some expressing concerns about human rights abuses.", "citations": {"25425784-5ea3-4507-b7ed-6574f2c80bff_984950487": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS's rule has led to the worst repression in Saudi history, with authorities using torture and detention to silence dissidents.", "citations": {"98212169-eb6b-4484-9329-2896742036b3_583754114": 1.0}}], "references": ["85f8e514-d127-49df-8b2e-76a051ef8d32_25925039", "98212169-eb6b-4484-9329-2896742036b3_583754114", "25425784-5ea3-4507-b7ed-6574f2c80bff_984950487", "11ad698b-5e86-461f-9f75-1f94496e7dd4_1019313503", "17686725-e6b2-42b7-ad90-e1d73dd68a8b_845745419", "2e03709c-a0f2-49c3-a204-0c5ebe79580e_315280229", "90eaba16-a74f-4ca0-bf0e-7ba9c5adc602_617175124", "339272fc-3a19-449c-9773-432deaa8ab3d_356121651", "8bf4b324-0fa4-4953-b361-028af7597974_481978147", "3ba8171a-5025-4b71-b03e-3be6260dfef4_239396021", "521ac676-eb0a-4808-8618-33cf0a1f7330_270127309"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1012", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Mohammed bin Salman, the Crown Prince of Saudi Arabia, has introduced a series of social and economic reforms as part of his 2030 vision for the country, aiming to reduce the influence of the Wahhabi establishment and promote a more moderate form of Islam.", "citations": {"1ec84a30-fdcd-4f1f-a0a0-4429222362aa_712309850": 1.0}}, {"text": "The reforms include curtailing the influence of the Wahhabi religious establishment by restricting the powers of the religious police and improving women's rights, such as allowing women to drive and participate in the workforce.", "citations": {"1ec84a30-fdcd-4f1f-a0a0-4429222362aa_712309850": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS's vision 2030 supports the expansion of the entertainment market, with the aim of reaching SR30 billion, and the creation of a more moderate form of Islam.", "citations": {"1ec84a30-fdcd-4f1f-a0a0-4429222362aa_712309850": 1.0}}, {"text": "The plan aims to maintain the Kingdom's advanced status and achieve a significant increase in non-oil revenues.", "citations": {"2bba158f-9658-4b31-80f0-b91171fba07a_356300910": 1.0}}, {"text": "The non-oil sector has shown impressive growth, with a growth rate of 8.4% in 2022, the highest in ten years.", "citations": {"3ba8171a-5025-4b71-b03e-3be6260dfef4_239396021": 1.0}}, {"text": "The private sector has grown by 11.1% in 2021, while the government sector has grown by 2.3%.", "citations": {"3ba8171a-5025-4b71-b03e-3be6260dfef4_239396021": 1.0}}, {"text": "Non-oil revenues have reached 457 billion riyals in 2023, a significant increase from 127 billion riyals in 2014.", "citations": {"3070d6a1-fc25-41bc-8539-08c048cf7606_862949452": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Public Investment Fund has grown to 1.8 trillion riyals by 2021, contributing 8% to the GDP.", "citations": {"3ba8171a-5025-4b71-b03e-3be6260dfef4_239396021": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Vision 2030 plan has created over 365,000 jobs through human capital development, and the unemployment rate among Saudis has decreased to 7.7%.", "citations": {"8bf4b324-0fa4-4953-b361-028af7597974_481978147": 1.0}}, {"text": "The female unemployment rate has also decreased by 13.7%, and women's workforce participation has doubled since 2016.", "citations": {"bd18bfb8-3df1-40fe-80d2-e6f7164cb150_463168187": 1.0}}, {"text": "The plan aims to increase the industrial domestic product to SR895 billion by 2030 and to develop and stabilize global supply chains.", "citations": {"de7bafe3-0613-4f8d-a925-cd3f5a571d98_897868556": 1.0}}, {"text": "The National Strategy for Industry has identified over 800 investment opportunities worth SR1 trillion, aiming to double the industrial domestic product by 2030.", "citations": {"3e6ce080-5be8-4139-9ebb-2465c6f80d4c_721618053": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Kingdom aims to achieve zero neutrality by 2060 and to promote innovation and trade integration.", "citations": {"51322918-8f3c-491c-ab0c-3fc9867ad790_540591571": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Vision 2030 plan has also focused on improving the quality of life, with a significant increase in tourism, reaching 64% growth in the first quarter of 2023.", "citations": {"2bba158f-9658-4b31-80f0-b91171fba07a_356300910": 1.0}}, {"text": "The plan has also aimed to strengthen the financial position of the Kingdom, with a budget surplus of 57.5 billion riyals in Q1 2022.", "citations": {"3ba8171a-5025-4b71-b03e-3be6260dfef4_239396021": 1.0}}, {"text": "The 2023 budget supports the Saudi Vision 2030 objectives, with a focus on economic stability, security, health, and human development.", "citations": {"90eaba16-a74f-4ca0-bf0e-7ba9c5adc602_617175124": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, Mohammed bin Salman's 2030 vision economic reforms have shown significant progress in diversifying the Saudi economy and improving the quality of life for its citizens.", "citations": {"bd18bfb8-3df1-40fe-80d2-e6f7164cb150_463168187": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia has undergone significant social reforms under the leadership of Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman (MBS) since 2017, with a focus on empowering women and promoting economic development.", "citations": {"03a65bda-15ab-45ee-8824-f2c9b4fcc7aa_430978275": 1.0}}, {"text": "The country has amended its women's rights laws and regulations, achieving equality in traffic regulations and ranking high in the Women, Business and the Law report.", "citations": {"03a65bda-15ab-45ee-8824-f2c9b4fcc7aa_430978275": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saudi women have been granted the right to drive, and over 175,000 women applied for driving licenses in a year and a half.", "citations": {"eac6eeef-f0fb-427b-b9b3-a05209fb6f82_892176758": 1.0}}, {"text": "The National Platform for Saudi Women Leaders was launched, and the economic participation rate of Saudi females increased by 94%.", "citations": {"03a65bda-15ab-45ee-8824-f2c9b4fcc7aa_430978275": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Women Empowerment Program was launched at the Ministry of Communications, and more than 30 companies joined an alliance to support women's access to the workforce.", "citations": {"03a65bda-15ab-45ee-8824-f2c9b4fcc7aa_430978275": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women now occupy senior positions in government institutions and universities, and participate in decision-making and elections.", "citations": {"03a65bda-15ab-45ee-8824-f2c9b4fcc7aa_430978275": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Vision 2030 plan, launched in 2016, aims to invest in human resources and natural wealth, and has led to improvements in health standards and happiness, as well as a decline in anxiety among Saudis.", "citations": {"04f4db17-88d0-411d-a6e8-62935194f976_538343315": 1.0}}, {"text": "The plan also includes the expansion of the entertainment market, with the aim of reaching SR30 billion, and the creation of a more moderate form of Islam.", "citations": {"1ec84a30-fdcd-4f1f-a0a0-4429222362aa_712309850": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Commission for Promotion of Virtue's role has been diminished since 2017, and its members no longer intervene in public behaviors.", "citations": {"2e03709c-a0f2-49c3-a204-0c5ebe79580e_315280229": 1.0}}, {"text": "The country has also witnessed an increase in personal freedoms, especially for women, with the ban on mixing between men and women ended, and concerts and festivals organized with artists and stars.", "citations": {"2e03709c-a0f2-49c3-a204-0c5ebe79580e_315280229": 1.0, "a25571d6-5682-40b1-be4c-7e2830967807_463834707": 0.5}}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia has implemented 82 historical reforms in human rights since 2017, and the Vision 2030 plan aims for social and economic transformation.", "citations": {"acc1951f-108d-4bb5-80ba-1e4918c8ba27_234242927": 1.0}}, {"text": "The reforms include modernizing the legal and judicial system, codifying the judicial system, and upholding justice and human rights principles.", "citations": {"acc1951f-108d-4bb5-80ba-1e4918c8ba27_234242927": 1.0}}, {"text": "The kingdom has also diversified its economy, with a growing fashion industry and a shift in societal roles and expectations for women.", "citations": {"acfb0cea-fea6-41de-8259-b55498d43f7d_493804949": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, LGBTQ individuals still face severe repression in Saudi Arabia, and opposition is largely repressed.", "citations": {"acfb0cea-fea6-41de-8259-b55498d43f7d_493804949": 1.0}}, {"text": "The authorities have also overlooked queer designers in the fashion industry, and religious leaders have been stripped of power.", "citations": {"acfb0cea-fea6-41de-8259-b55498d43f7d_493804949": 1.0}}, {"text": "Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman has championed women's progress and empowered women in the labor market, with women's right to drive, travel, and run businesses helping to hire more female workers.", "citations": {"e3a72078-1055-4a67-be09-6dda7e9aca0b_126689011": 1.0}}, {"text": "The female unemployment rate has fallen to its lowest level in 20 years, and women in middle management and senior positions have increased from 28.6% to 39% between 2017 and 2022.", "citations": {"e3a72078-1055-4a67-be09-6dda7e9aca0b_126689011": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia has also launched initiatives to support women's education and participation in economic and social life, with the aim of creating a working environment that supports equality and diversity.", "citations": {"e3a72078-1055-4a67-be09-6dda7e9aca0b_126689011": 1.0}}, {"text": "The country has tightened legislation to combat sexual harassment, and women can now apply for passports without male guardian consent.", "citations": {"eac6eeef-f0fb-427b-b9b3-a05209fb6f82_892176758": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, the male guardianship system still restricts women's rights, and women's rights activists are arbitrarily arrested and detained.", "citations": {"eac6eeef-f0fb-427b-b9b3-a05209fb6f82_892176758": 1.0}}, {"text": "Despite these challenges, Saudi Arabia has made significant progress in promoting women's rights and social reforms under the leadership of Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman.", "citations": {"03a65bda-15ab-45ee-8824-f2c9b4fcc7aa_430978275": 1.0, "04f4db17-88d0-411d-a6e8-62935194f976_538343315": 0.5, "0bec1163-8e49-4121-9c2d-4d47f28b812b_815296896": 0.25, "1ec84a30-fdcd-4f1f-a0a0-4429222362aa_712309850": 0.125, "2e03709c-a0f2-49c3-a204-0c5ebe79580e_315280229": 0.0625, "a25571d6-5682-40b1-be4c-7e2830967807_463834707": 0.03125, "acc1951f-108d-4bb5-80ba-1e4918c8ba27_234242927": 0.015625, "acfb0cea-fea6-41de-8259-b55498d43f7d_493804949": 0.0078125, "d11ea820-96a0-4484-8a36-89a601ffcd28_200468718": 0.00390625, "e3a72078-1055-4a67-be09-6dda7e9aca0b_126689011": 0.001953125, "eac6eeef-f0fb-427b-b9b3-a05209fb6f82_892176758": 0.0009765625, "f14b5c9e-084a-4291-8dc9-a631b84e6c4c_107673090": 0.00048828125}}, {"text": "Mohammed bin Salman, also known as MBS, has initiated a break from Wahhabi ideology, aiming to modernize Saudi Arabia with a moderate form of Islam.", "citations": {"1ec84a30-fdcd-4f1f-a0a0-4429222362aa_712309850": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS admitted that Saudi Wahhabism serves American interests, highlighting the complex historical relationship between the two countries.", "citations": {"1e8e09b8-4025-44b7-8ba7-bff81a96468c_790730076": 1.0}}, {"text": "Wahhabism was used as a tool in the Cold War between America and the Soviet Union, with the US planning \"Jihad in Afghanistan\" against the Soviet Union in 1979.", "citations": {"1e8e09b8-4025-44b7-8ba7-bff81a96468c_790730076": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has limited the role of the Commission for Virtue and Vice, also known as the religious police, restricting their powers and reducing their influence.", "citations": {"2e03709c-a0f2-49c3-a204-0c5ebe79580e_315280229": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Commission's role has been limited to awareness campaigns, and its members no longer intervene in people's behaviors.", "citations": {"2e03709c-a0f2-49c3-a204-0c5ebe79580e_315280229": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has introduced social reforms, including allowing women to drive, as part of his vision to develop Saudi Arabia beyond the energy sector.", "citations": {"1ec84a30-fdcd-4f1f-a0a0-4429222362aa_712309850": 1.0}}, {"text": "He has also reduced the Commission's role in enforcing Islamic law, giving more freedom to Saudi citizens.", "citations": {"2e03709c-a0f2-49c3-a204-0c5ebe79580e_315280229": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Muslim World League has transformed from promoting obscurantist ideology to promoting tolerance and reformation under MBS's guidance.", "citations": {"1ec84a30-fdcd-4f1f-a0a0-4429222362aa_712309850": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has convinced the clergy to follow his vision for a more moderate Islam, paving the way for a more inclusive and tolerant society.", "citations": {"1ec84a30-fdcd-4f1f-a0a0-4429222362aa_712309850": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia's Vision 2030 supports the expansion of the entertainment market, with mixed concerts and entertainment allowed in the country.", "citations": {"339272fc-3a19-449c-9773-432deaa8ab3d_356121651": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS's policies have aimed to win the youth to his side, with a focus on modernization and development.", "citations": {"339272fc-3a19-449c-9773-432deaa8ab3d_356121651": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Wahhabi doctrine was historically imposed on the Saudi people, but MBS's reforms have started to change this.", "citations": {"339272fc-3a19-449c-9773-432deaa8ab3d_356121651": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has arrested opposing religious scholars and reduced the religious establishment's role in Saudi society.", "citations": {"67d76069-bdf3-4994-8e19-7091df5f04f5_1016495452": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saudi Council has declared the Muslim Brotherhood a terrorist group, and MBS has abandoned Wahhabism and the Salafi school.", "citations": {"67d76069-bdf3-4994-8e19-7091df5f04f5_1016495452": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has prioritized a unique Saudi model, preserving Islamic identity while promoting development and modernization.", "citations": {"8597ca97-79d8-4426-85cb-4a9b6ed9ac9e_172625398": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saudi government has restricted non-Muslim worship and beliefs in public, with Wahhabism being the dominant form of Islam in the country.", "citations": {"85f8e514-d127-49df-8b2e-76a051ef8d32_25925039": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, MBS's reforms have started to address these issues, with a focus on improving women's rights and promoting sectarian pluralism.", "citations": {"2b866659-160d-4658-8b34-bab9758a798c_246988971": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia's Basic Law of Governance protects sectarian pluralism, and King Salman bin Abdulaziz has stressed equality between citizens.", "citations": {"2b866659-160d-4658-8b34-bab9758a798c_246988971": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has promoted sectarian pluralism in Saudi Arabia, recognizing the diversity of the Saudi population.", "citations": {"2b866659-160d-4658-8b34-bab9758a798c_246988971": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Islamic Affairs has promoted moderation in religious discourse, with over 3,800 women appointed to the ministry.", "citations": {"dd73de04-69f7-4e24-84f6-838862e7c192_721213270": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS's policies have aimed to eliminate extremism and promote moderation, with the Ministry of Islamic Affairs working with Al-Azhar to achieve this goal.", "citations": {"dd73de04-69f7-4e24-84f6-838862e7c192_721213270": 1.0}}, {"text": "Wahhabism was created by colonial powers to destroy the Ottoman Empire, and the British supported Muhammad bin Abdul Wahab and Ibn Saud to control Diriyah.", "citations": {"fc5ef41b-852e-4adb-a13b-f0c0f728fdf9_745675049": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saudi ruling family relies on Wahhabism to maintain power, but MBS's reforms have started to change this.", "citations": {"fc5ef41b-852e-4adb-a13b-f0c0f728fdf9_745675049": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has the power to change the doctrines of Takfir of Ibn Taymiyyah, which could lead to a more moderate and inclusive form of Islam.", "citations": {"fc5ef41b-852e-4adb-a13b-f0c0f728fdf9_745675049": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia aims to empower women without discrimination under the leadership of Mohammed bin Salman (MBS).", "citations": {"03a65bda-15ab-45ee-8824-f2c9b4fcc7aa_430978275": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia has reformed laws to ensure women's equal rights, with significant developments in women's affairs.", "citations": {"03a65bda-15ab-45ee-8824-f2c9b4fcc7aa_430978275": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women's rights have received the largest share of developments in the country, with a focus on promoting equality between men and women.", "citations": {"03a65bda-15ab-45ee-8824-f2c9b4fcc7aa_430978275": 1.0}}, {"text": "The economic participation rate of Saudi females has increased by 94% under MBS leadership, indicating a significant improvement in women's economic empowerment.", "citations": {"03a65bda-15ab-45ee-8824-f2c9b4fcc7aa_430978275": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has granted women rights previously denied to them, including the right to work and participate in the economy.", "citations": {"2b3920b8-8643-4db0-8193-eb85f79b7368_479346508": 1.0}}, {"text": "MBS has also", "citations": 