{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1017", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Disney's live-action remakes, such as Aladdin and The Lion King, have grossed over $1 billion worldwide.", "citations": {"affa62b6-3681-4651-bd81-70d2425e5fae_433916494": 1.0}}, {"text": "The remakes' success can be attributed to nostalgia, allowing people to share classic stories with the next generation.", "citations": {"4b7b2e66-ee70-426e-b6b1-ebfd29dca20b_59301776": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney produces live-action remakes of animated films due to their financial success and audience demand.", "citations": {"4f066135-2b16-40d4-b7e2-53d7b2c13378_369931830": 1.0}}, {"text": "The live-action remakes, like The Little Mermaid, promote diversity and inclusion in storytelling.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's casting choices reflect its commitment to diversity, despite racist backlash.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 1.0}}, {"text": "The production team behind the live-action remakes balances authenticity and relevance by consulting diverse communities and incorporating modern themes.", "citations": {"5e5c7575-0fff-41f7-833f-b9ff4b71230c_219533606": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's live-action remakes use nostalgia by recreating classic characters and stories with modern updates.", "citations": {"f2ef50c0-4817-4aae-bd18-4208e7c369cb_452895435": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Little Mermaid live-action remake updated Eric's character and allowed Ariel and Eric more time to get to know each other.", "citations": {"f2ef50c0-4817-4aae-bd18-4208e7c369cb_452895435": 1.0}}, {"text": "The remake aimed to resonate with a new generation while staying true to Ariel's original personality.", "citations": {"f2ef50c0-4817-4aae-bd18-4208e7c369cb_452895435": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes have sparked controversy over casting decisions and accusations of hypocrisy.", "citations": {"fff8c0a3-9878-48db-989f-82add6b6c560_882631475": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company has consulted with diverse communities to avoid stereotypes from the original films.", "citations": {"fff8c0a3-9878-48db-989f-82add6b6c560_882631475": 1.0}}, {"text": "The public reaction to the adaptations has been mixed, with some fans praising the updates and others criticizing the deviations from the originals.", "citations": {"8138d416-ceaa-43d3-a92d-7ad903317f2b_769285838": 1.0}}, {"text": "The success or failure of live-action remakes depends on production quality, faithfulness to the original, and adaptation to contemporary realities.", "citations": {"1d8d96bf-df07-4849-9c7b-b86862bd9de9_687585026": 1.0}}, {"text": "CGI and special effects in live-action remakes have enhanced the visual and storytelling experience, enabling the creation of impossible fantasy universes.", "citations": {"60009997-28f3-4001-891a-83762f2f8982_264364959": 1.0}}, {"text": "Nostalgia significantly drives Disney's live-action remakes, aiming to appeal to both old and new audiences.", "citations": {"440ee913-7016-4f8d-b2e0-3fce141e4dac_73458855": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes are driven by nostalgia, commercial considerations, and a desire to adapt beloved stories to contemporary realities.", "citations": {"04be02f4-bf63-4cf4-a520-2859d5be0752_801436266": 1.0}}], "references": ["8138d416-ceaa-43d3-a92d-7ad903317f2b_769285838", "fff8c0a3-9878-48db-989f-82add6b6c560_882631475", "affa62b6-3681-4651-bd81-70d2425e5fae_433916494", "4b7b2e66-ee70-426e-b6b1-ebfd29dca20b_59301776", "1d8d96bf-df07-4849-9c7b-b86862bd9de9_687585026", "5e5c7575-0fff-41f7-833f-b9ff4b71230c_219533606", "60009997-28f3-4001-891a-83762f2f8982_264364959", "440ee913-7016-4f8d-b2e0-3fce141e4dac_73458855", "84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498", "4f066135-2b16-40d4-b7e2-53d7b2c13378_369931830", "04be02f4-bf63-4cf4-a520-2859d5be0752_801436266", "f2ef50c0-4817-4aae-bd18-4208e7c369cb_452895435"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1018", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Disney has remade several classic animated films, including Cinderella, The Jungle Book, and The Lion King, in live-action.", "citations": {"2b7b6721-9b08-432c-b318-1f57bf8a8139_226946838": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's remakes are driven by nostalgia, aiming to capitalize on fond memories of older audiences and introduce the stories to a new generation.", "citations": {"5e5c7575-0fff-41f7-833f-b9ff4b71230c_219533606": 1.0}}, {"text": "Nostalgia drives Disney's live-action remakes, tapping into audiences' existing emotional connection to the original stories.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes aim to update stories and characters to modern standards, making them more relatable to contemporary audiences.", "citations": {"f2ef50c0-4817-4aae-bd18-4208e7c369cb_452895435": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company has made significant changes to the original stories and characters, making them more nuanced and complex.", "citations": {"f2ef50c0-4817-4aae-bd18-4208e7c369cb_452895435": 1.0}}, {"text": "The live-action remake of The Little Mermaid made Eric more restless and gave him and Ariel more time to bond, making their romance more satisfying.", "citations": {"f2ef50c0-4817-4aae-bd18-4208e7c369cb_452895435": 1.0}}, {"text": "The live-action remakes include more diverse casting and modern themes.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 1.0}}, {"text": "The remakes have been criticized for lacking the magic and charm of the originals.", "citations": {"9bf4d61e-80c6-417e-8c40-6d987236d4fb_1002818262": 1.0}}, {"text": "The public reaction to the adaptations has been mixed, with some praising the updates and others preferring the originals.", "citations": {"7807cece-c991-4f8b-9b52-1dcabc779f33_333067711": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes have been commercially successful, grossing hundreds of millions of dollars.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's films, like The Little Mermaid and Aladdin, feature diverse leads and supporting casts.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes have sparked debate about prioritizing nostalgia over representation and diversity.", "citations": {"7807cece-c991-4f8b-9b52-1dcabc779f33_333067711": 1.0}}, {"text": "Others argue that remakes allow Disney to reimagine stories in a more inclusive way.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes are driven by nostalgia, commercialism, and a desire to update stories for modern audiences.", "citations": {"5e5c7575-0fff-41f7-833f-b9ff4b71230c_219533606": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes, like The Little Mermaid and Aladdin, have grossed over $1 billion worldwide.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's live-action remakes prioritize inclusive stories with diverse representation and authenticity.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 1.0}}, {"text": "Visual effects in live-action remakes, like Avatar: The Way of Water, create realistic characters and environments by pushing motion capture technology boundaries.", "citations": {"a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_97576879": 1.0}}, {"text": "Collaboration between visual effects companies like Industrial Light & Magic and WETA Digital has been essential in creating realistic environments and characters in live-action remakes.", "citations": {"7e72fd16-b400-4c6f-a69d-b3f6a5b7febd_230387014": 1.0}}, {"text": "AI and machine learning algorithms have improved visual effects, enabling more subtle facial nuances and realistic character movements.", "citations": {"aed5a3eb-2dc5-456a-a450-a96f81362824_492622250": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action Little Mermaid remake has a $250 million budget.", "citations": {"08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_814052845": 1.0}}, {"text": "The film's marketing included interviews with Halle Bailey and a D23 Expo teaser, with production costs reportedly at $250 million.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney has remade several animated classics into live-action films in the past decade, including Cinderella, The Jungle Book, Beauty and the Beast, and others.", "citations": {"b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes are driven by nostalgia and a desire to update classic stories.", "citations": {"b2c206be-9a9c-4af5-814e-ef7dc03a58d5_1006080931": 1.0}}, {"text": "The changes made to the original stories and characters in remakes vary from faithful to significantly altered.", "citations": {"b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962": 1.0}}, {"text": "The public reaction to the adaptations has been mixed, with some receiving acclaim and others criticism.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 1.0}}, {"text": "Nostalgia plays a significant role in Disney's live-action remakes, tapping into older audiences while introducing stories to a new generation.", "citations": {"b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962": 1.0}}, {"text": "The financial performance of live-action remakes can be impacted by production costs, marketing, and public reaction, resulting in varying degrees of success.", "citations": {"3de8ff79-1db7-4668-9219-3878e4f56098_64540464": 1.0}}, {"text": "Indiana Jones and the Dial of Destiny cost $387.2 million to produce, but lost $134.2 million after earning $384 million at the box office.", "citations": {"ff180aae-02e1-45d7-b9e5-670aa1b6c769_83739031": 1.0}}, {"text": "The first three Indiana Jones films outperform Dial of Destiny when adjusted for inflation, sparking scrutiny of Disney's leadership.", "citations": {"ff180aae-02e1-45d7-b9e5-670aa1b6c769_83739031": 1.0}}, {"text": "Live-action remakes of Aladdin and Beauty and the Beast each grossed $1 billion globally.", "citations": {"c7e579e6-3738-495f-b411-43f31a0e8d23_584006662": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Little Mermaid live-action remake is expected to debut with $200 million globally, including $80 million overseas.", "citations": {"c7e579e6-3738-495f-b411-43f31a0e8d23_584006662": 1.0}}, {"text": "Marketing strategies for live-action remakes include showcasing diversity, adapting stories to contemporary times, and utilizing social media and digital platforms.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney measures success with box office numbers and streaming performance.", "citations": {"24961526-9c9a-4bc6-87f5-cd757c1305eb_413660801": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company uses a 30-45 day theatrical window before streaming.", "citations": {"24961526-9c9a-4bc6-87f5-cd757c1305eb_413660801": 1.0}}, {"text": "Box office numbers are key for Disney's live-action remakes, as seen in Shang-Chi and Free Guy.", "citations": {"24961526-9c9a-4bc6-87f5-cd757c1305eb_413660801": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's decision to release films in theaters follows successful releases that attract customers to theater chains.", "citations": {"24961526-9c9a-4bc6-87f5-cd757c1305eb_413660801": 1.0}}, {"text": "The live-action remake of The Little Mermaid debuted in 2023 under Disney's cinema-first release strategy.", "citations": {"24961526-9c9a-4bc6-87f5-cd757c1305eb_413660801": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney measures success by achieving profitability in its streaming business through four key growth opportunities.", "citations": {"29586042-926a-40b6-92cf-d94bb3c186df_747761640": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company assesses properties for long-term growth to increase film output and improve economics.", "citations": {"29586042-926a-40b6-92cf-d94bb3c186df_747761640": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney targets growth in its parks business based on future growth potential.", "citations": {"29586042-926a-40b6-92cf-d94bb3c186df_747761640": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company aims to build ESPN into a dominant digital sports platform amid its struggling stock.", "citations": {"29586042-926a-40b6-92cf-d94bb3c186df_747761640": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes measure success by box office performance.", "citations": {"458f78da-4fd3-48c7-8c6a-4d32ba5efffa_645465952": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Little Mermaid had a $250 million production budget and was expected to gross $120-130 million over a four-day weekend.", "citations": {"458f78da-4fd3-48c7-8c6a-4d32ba5efffa_645465952": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Little Mermaid has a 66% Rotten Tomatoes score and is also measured by global box office performance.", "citations": {"458f78da-4fd3-48c7-8c6a-4d32ba5efffa_645465952": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Little Mermaid remake grossed over $550 million globally.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 1.0}}, {"text": "The film surpassed the original's box office earnings.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's remakes, like The Little Mermaid, prioritize representation and diversity, particularly for young girls of color.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney evaluates success by cultural impact, standing firm against racist backlash.", "citations": {"84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company measures success by revenue and profit growth, with operating profit increasing by 50% year-on-year.", "citations": {"87229a1b-ac91-4609-b6ea-54cf4561ebe4_176609240": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's net profit rose 53% to $1.4 billion, beating analysts' expectations.", "citations": {"87229a1b-ac91-4609-b6ea-54cf4561ebe4_176609240": 1.0}}, {"text": "The theme park segment saw a 74% revenue increase, while Disney+ subscribers rose to 152.1 million, a gain of 14.4 million.", "citations": {"87229a1b-ac91-4609-b6ea-54cf4561ebe4_176609240": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney measures success by box office performance and streaming views.", "citations": {"9ce402fd-69ce-4eda-a393-7fcdf8ecc934_366945959": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Little Mermaid and Elemental broke Disney+ records, with the latter garnering 26.4 million views in five days.", "citations": {"9ce402fd-69ce-4eda-a393-7fcdf8ecc934_366945959": 1.0}}, {"text": "Haunted Mansion struggled at the box office due to competition from Disney+ releases.", "citations": {"9ce402fd-69ce-4eda-a393-7fcdf8ecc934_366945959": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's live-action remakes face backlash, but Pixar's Elemental was Disney+'s most viewed 2023 premiere.", "citations": {"9ce402fd-69ce-4eda-a393-7fcdf8ecc934_366945959": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney's streaming service boosts movie performance after cinema release, prompting the company to consider new distribution strategies.", "citations": {"9ce402fd-69ce-4eda-a393-7fcdf8ecc934_366945959": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney measures success through box office performance and audience reception.", "citations": {"b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company plans to turn most of its animated catalog into live-action movies.", "citations": {"b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sequels and spin-offs are in the works for some live-action remakes, to be streamed on Disney+.", "citations": {"b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962": 1.0}}, {"text": "Disney measures success through earnings results and cost-cutting measures.", "citations": {"b17d7702-fa05-431e-affe-57a5879b8e56_475045862": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's stock has a 25.19% upside potential to $135.", "citations": {}}], "references": ["2b7b6721-9b08-432c-b318-1f57bf8a8139_226946838", "a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_97576879", "29586042-926a-40b6-92cf-d94bb3c186df_747761640", "7e72fd16-b400-4c6f-a69d-b3f6a5b7febd_230387014", "b2c206be-9a9c-4af5-814e-ef7dc03a58d5_1006080931", "7807cece-c991-4f8b-9b52-1dcabc779f33_333067711", "9ce402fd-69ce-4eda-a393-7fcdf8ecc934_366945959", "9bf4d61e-80c6-417e-8c40-6d987236d4fb_1002818262", "458f78da-4fd3-48c7-8c6a-4d32ba5efffa_645465952", "b0cdad92-634f-4d6e-b764-f694603e164e_943700962", "24961526-9c9a-4bc6-87f5-cd757c1305eb_413660801", "87229a1b-ac91-4609-b6ea-54cf4561ebe4_176609240", "aed5a3eb-2dc5-456a-a450-a96f81362824_492622250", "ff180aae-02e1-45d7-b9e5-670aa1b6c769_83739031", "5e5c7575-0fff-41f7-833f-b9ff4b71230c_219533606", "c7e579e6-3738-495f-b411-43f31a0e8d23_584006662", "f2ef50c0-4817-4aae-bd18-4208e7c369cb_452895435", "3de8ff79-1db7-4668-9219-3878e4f56098_64540464", "b17d7702-fa05-431e-affe-57a5879b8e56_475045862", "08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_814052845", "84e42260-399c-4d7b-8ea7-6f4f8bd47c33_545966498"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1019", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Tai Chi, a traditional Chinese martial art, improves balance, reduces fall risk, and enhances physical stability in older adults.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is a low-impact exercise combining slow movements, deep breathing, and meditation, adaptable to individual fitness levels.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi reduces the risk of falls in older adults by improving balance, strength, and mobility, and alleviates symptoms of arthritis and COPD.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi benefits Parkinson's patients by improving balance and mobility and reducing fall risk.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi has physical and mental health benefits, reducing stress and anxiety while improving overall well-being.", "citations": {"b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414": 1.0}}, {"text": "Caregivers can support their aging parents in practicing Tai Chi by helping them find local or online classes.", "citations": {"07e86353-4df1-47dd-8ddd-a2c4d7b73d7d_327853608": 1.0}}, {"text": "Older adults are recommended to practice Tai Chi at least three times a week, starting gently and increasing intensity and duration over time.", "citations": {"693b6e6b-fdbf-422c-8eaf-6b786b9c3d7a_224422821": 1.0}}, {"text": "The World Health Organization recommends 150-300 minutes of moderate-intensity exercise, such as Tai Chi, per week for adults over 65 to improve balance and prevent falls.", "citations": {"4502ea6b-f423-4f08-b3e9-2c45e7a80185_337609787": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi reduces fall risk in older adults by improving balance and is suitable for those with mobility issues.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Exercise training, such as Tai Chi, improves muscle strength, balance, and bone density in older adults.", "citations": {"43b9a6ad-8db0-4be1-b27c-8de54e53d895_973279368": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi practice three times a week, for one hour per session, is sufficient for significant improvements in older adults.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Caregivers should consult a healthcare professional before starting their aging parents in a new exercise program, including Tai Chi.", "citations": {"43b9a6ad-8db0-4be1-b27c-8de54e53d895_973279368": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is an excellent option for older adults to improve balance, mobility, and health, with caregivers playing a vital supportive role.", "citations": {"b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi improves balance and reduces fall risk in older adults, with caregivers playing a crucial role in monitoring progress and ensuring safety.", "citations": {"184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782": 1.0, "2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 0.5, "6bb86295-c49b-4797-ab4b-5652344f2d4a_686292122": 0.25, "73578dea-46ff-4ea8-bef0-411024d49f39_18163632": 0.125, "885d7b96-d3cf-4d10-a3e7-5ac07edbd0bb_331812203": 0.0625, "9e869dee-8548-4a5b-b44d-a633f74e0073_299501002": 0.03125}}], "references": ["693b6e6b-fdbf-422c-8eaf-6b786b9c3d7a_224422821", "6bb86295-c49b-4797-ab4b-5652344f2d4a_686292122", "43b9a6ad-8db0-4be1-b27c-8de54e53d895_973279368", "07e86353-4df1-47dd-8ddd-a2c4d7b73d7d_327853608", "184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782", "885d7b96-d3cf-4d10-a3e7-5ac07edbd0bb_331812203", "9e869dee-8548-4a5b-b44d-a633f74e0073_299501002", "b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414", "4502ea6b-f423-4f08-b3e9-2c45e7a80185_337609787", "41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629", "73578dea-46ff-4ea8-bef0-411024d49f39_18163632", "2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1020", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Tai Chi is a form of exercise that combines physical training, self-defense, and meditation to improve balance and reduce the risk of falls in older adults.", "citations": {}}, {"text": "Tai Chi has been shown to improve strength and balance in elderly individuals, which can help prevent falls and related injuries.", "citations": {"0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653": 1.0}}, {"text": "The practice of Tai Chi involves gentle stretching and movement, which stimulates muscles and joints, and can be modified to accommodate individuals with various health conditions.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi has been found to reduce fall risk in older adults by improving balance, and it also alleviates degenerative arthritis symptoms like knee stiffness.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Regular practice of Tai Chi can lower blood pressure, improve lung function, and enhance cognitive functioning, all of which are important for reducing fall risk.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0, "f3f6c566-9c4f-4d07-a262-9f6ef4ef8f69_83051545": 0.5}}, {"text": "Balance training is a crucial component of Tai Chi, and it can be emphasized in a fall prevention program by incorporating exercises that challenge balance, such as single-leg and toe exercises.", "citations": {"245fa441-2e94-44fe-b953-9f09a184a0c7_915527216": 1.0, "460b5c39-c401-4e48-9f9d-49a3fd391e5d_154687180": 0.5}}, {"text": "The optimal frequency of Tai Chi exercise for fall prevention appears to be three times a week, with each session lasting about one hour.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Exercise programs that include Tai Chi have been shown to prevent falls in seniors living at home, and can be an effective way to reduce fall risk.", "citations": {"184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is a low-impact exercise that can be done anywhere without equipment, making it an accessible and convenient option for older adults.", "citations": {"f3f6c566-9c4f-4d07-a262-9f6ef4ef8f69_83051545": 1.0}}, {"text": "The key components of Tai Chi, including balance training, muscle strengthening, and flexibility exercises, can be emphasized in a fall prevention program to reduce fall risk and improve physical stability.", "citations": {"0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653": 1.0, "245fa441-2e94-44fe-b953-9f09a184a0c7_915527216": 0.5, "2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 0.25, "460b5c39-c401-4e48-9f9d-49a3fd391e5d_154687180": 0.125, "80c8da15-5fa3-4f38-8fa6-3c8ddc7d04f2_904596165": 0.0625}}, {"text": "Overall, the scientific evidence suggests that Tai Chi is an effective method for improving balance and reducing fall risk in older adults, and its components can be emphasized in a fall prevention program to maximize its benefits.", "citations": {"08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184": 1.0, "184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782": 0.5, "2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 0.25, "92fdcec5-a1b7-40fe-aa88-f3599690fa76_991201849": 0.125}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can be adapted for older adults with mobility issues, making it a suitable option for those with severe mobility limitations.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi classes can be tailored for specific health needs, and instructors can provide modifications for limitations, ensuring that older adults with complex health needs can safely participate.", "citations": {"5c1162ae-4b10-4556-b59e-5a30440f6c83_159992918": 1.0}}, {"text": "The effectiveness of a Tai Chi-based fall prevention program can be measured by evaluating its impact on fall risk, with prior falls predicting future fall risk.", "citations": {"a60aab1e-adb5-4379-8753-782847b58236_378435733": 1.0}}, {"text": "Collaboration between healthcare providers, patients, and family members is important for implementing effective fall prevention programs, including those incorporating Tai Chi.", "citations": {"aa6e94c3-5aa6-4e44-8979-b22807f64fa9_626282754": 1.0}}, {"text": "Resources, reimbursement, and patient motivation are also crucial factors in the success of Tai Chi-based fall prevention programs.", "citations": {"aa6e94c3-5aa6-4e44-8979-b22807f64fa9_626282754": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the scientific evidence suggests that Tai Chi is a valuable component of fall prevention programs, with significant benefits for physical stability, balance, and overall health outcomes in older adults.", "citations": {"0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653": 1.0, "184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782": 0.5, "2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 0.25, "41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 0.125, "a60aab1e-adb5-4379-8753-782847b58236_378435733": 0.0625, "b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414": 0.03125, "f3f6c566-9c4f-4d07-a262-9f6ef4ef8f69_83051545": 0.015625}}], "references": ["41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629", "80c8da15-5fa3-4f38-8fa6-3c8ddc7d04f2_904596165", "0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653", "08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184", "5c1162ae-4b10-4556-b59e-5a30440f6c83_159992918", "a60aab1e-adb5-4379-8753-782847b58236_378435733", "b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414", "245fa441-2e94-44fe-b953-9f09a184a0c7_915527216", "aa6e94c3-5aa6-4e44-8979-b22807f64fa9_626282754", "f3f6c566-9c4f-4d07-a262-9f6ef4ef8f69_83051545", "460b5c39-c401-4e48-9f9d-49a3fd391e5d_154687180", "2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624", "92fdcec5-a1b7-40fe-aa88-f3599690fa76_991201849", "184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1021", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Tai Chi can improve balance and reduce the risk of falls in older adults.", "citations": {"0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi involves slow and gentle movements that improve balance, strength, and flexibility, helping prevent falls.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi improves balance, reduces fall risk, and alleviates symptoms of degenerative arthritis and chronic obstructive pulmonary disease.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi has a relaxing and meditative effect that can help reduce stress and anxiety, contributing to fall prevention.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi practice is recommended at least three times a week for one hour per session to improve balance and reduce fall risk in older adults.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is suitable for older adults with health conditions like arthritis, Parkinson's, and high blood pressure.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is an effective exercise for fall prevention in older adults and can be modified to suit individual needs.", "citations": {"184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782": 1.0}}, {"text": "Evidence from various studies, including randomized controlled trials, supports Tai Chi's effectiveness in reducing fall risk in older adults.", "citations": {"184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi offers physical, psychological, and social benefits, including reduced stress, improved mood, and increased social connections.", "citations": {"b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can improve cognitive function and reduce the risk of falls.", "citations": {"b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is an accessible form of exercise that can be modified to accommodate individual needs and abilities for older adults.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can be practiced in a group for social interaction or individually for calm and relaxation.", "citations": {"34a5ef86-794c-4dd0-95a9-b1b3c3632633_326815735": 1.0}}, {"text": "Most Tai Chi classes last around 40-60 minutes.", "citations": {"8138d416-ceaa-43d3-a92d-7ad903317f2b_135477836": 1.0}}, {"text": "The key to successful Tai Chi practice is finding a routine that works for you and practicing regularly, ideally with an instructor or group.", "citations": {"34a5ef86-794c-4dd0-95a9-b1b3c3632633_326815735": 1.0}}, {"text": "Incorporating Tai Chi into their routine can help older adults reduce their risk of falls and improve overall health.", "citations": {"80c8da15-5fa3-4f38-8fa6-3c8ddc7d04f2_904596165": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can be combined with exercises like walking and swimming for a comprehensive program.", "citations": {"0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653": 1.0}}], "references": ["41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629", "8138d416-ceaa-43d3-a92d-7ad903317f2b_135477836", "0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653", "80c8da15-5fa3-4f38-8fa6-3c8ddc7d04f2_904596165", "b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414", "184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782", "34a5ef86-794c-4dd0-95a9-b1b3c3632633_326815735", "2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1022", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Tai Chi is a highly effective exercise for improving balance and managing health conditions like Parkinson's, arthritis, and chronic obstructive pulmonary disease in older adults.", "citations": {"0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653": 1.0, "2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 0.5}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can alleviate arthritis symptoms, improve lung function, and enhance balance and mobility in older adults, aiding in fall prevention.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi reduces fall risk in older adults by improving balance, making it suitable for those with mobility or cognitive limitations.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0, "41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 0.5}}, {"text": "The World Health Organization recommends at least 150 minutes of moderate-intensity aerobic exercise, such as Tai Chi, per week for adults over 65.", "citations": {"4502ea6b-f423-4f08-b3e9-2c45e7a80185_337609787": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi and exercise training can help elderly individuals enhance strength and balance, reducing fall risk.", "citations": {"43b9a6ad-8db0-4be1-b27c-8de54e53d895_973279368": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can be modified to suit individual needs, making it accessible for older adults.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Older adults should practice Tai Chi three times a week for about an hour per session.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi practice can improve balance and mobility in older adults.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is an effective exercise for fall prevention and improved mobility in older adults, comparable to yoga and Pilates.", "citations": {"08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184": 1.0, "0b91df07-9f16-4d7b-a315-06ee2639898f_906991366": 0.5, "bc9d8a85-ac6a-49d7-ad15-c535b79a0654_46520525": 0.25}}, {"text": "Tai Chi, yoga, and Pilates show similar promise in reducing fall risk and improving balance in older adults.", "citations": {"08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184": 1.0, "0b91df07-9f16-4d7b-a315-06ee2639898f_906991366": 0.5, "0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653": 0.25, "184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782": 0.125, "2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 0.0625, "41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 0.03125, "bc9d8a85-ac6a-49d7-ad15-c535b79a0654_46520525": 0.015625}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is a highly effective exercise for reducing falls and improving physical stability in older adults.", "citations": {"184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782": 1.0, "2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 0.5, "34a5ef86-794c-4dd0-95a9-b1b3c3632633_326815735": 0.25, "41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 0.125, "b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414": 0.0625, "f3f6c566-9c4f-4d07-a262-9f6ef4ef8f69_83051545": 0.03125}}, {"text": "The minimum frequency and duration needed to improve balance, mobility, and fall prevention in older adults are not specified.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0, "4502ea6b-f423-4f08-b3e9-2c45e7a80185_337609787": 0.5, "97b014c9-d996-4206-b240-6c9c6a4b3ac0_531746640": 0.25}}, {"text": "Older adults with certain health conditions should undergo a professional assessment before starting Tai Chi or any exercise program.", "citations": {"43b9a6ad-8db0-4be1-b27c-8de54e53d895_973279368": 1.0}}, {"text": "Seated Tai Chi can help older adults with mobility limitations enter a meditative state and improve their balance.", "citations": {"14b74b2e-eb4c-4316-a13f-2b94ab1cae1a_760925045": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi practice for older adults is influenced by physical, psychological, and environmental factors.", "citations": {"f85faa27-0854-4de1-8e22-00af06712fac_232578191": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can be modified to accommodate mobility limitations and arthritis, making it suitable for older adults with these conditions.", "citations": {"46aac298-47e3-40c4-b112-cf04be57240a_846751787": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can be done anytime and anywhere, making it accessible to older adults.", "citations": {"f3f6c566-9c4f-4d07-a262-9f6ef4ef8f69_83051545": 1.0}}, {"text": "Gentle movements and breathing can calm older adults with anxiety by activating the parasympathetic nervous system.", "citations": {"f3f6c566-9c4f-4d07-a262-9f6ef4ef8f69_83051545": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is a low-impact exercise suitable for older adults with mobility or cognitive limitations.", "citations": {"f3f6c566-9c4f-4d07-a262-9f6ef4ef8f69_83051545": 1.0}}, {"text": "Accessibility at home, outdoors, and to transport can enhance Tai Chi practice feasibility for older adults.", "citations": {"f85faa27-0854-4de1-8e22-00af06712fac_232578191": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi improves cardiovascular health, reduces stress, and enhances overall well-being, benefiting older adults.", "citations": {"b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can help older adults by lowering blood pressure, improving balance and flexibility, and reducing the risk of falls.", "citations": {"b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi practice involves slow movements, improves blood pressure, and is an accessible exercise that activates the parasympathetic nervous system.", "citations": {"b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414": 1.0, "f3f6c566-9c4f-4d07-a262-9f6ef4ef8f69_83051545": 0.5}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is a calming exercise that can be done anytime and anywhere, benefiting older adults with mobility limitations and those with elevated blood pressure.", "citations": {"f3f6c566-9c4f-4d07-a262-9f6ef4ef8f69_83051545": 1.0}}, {"text": "Pilates improves balance and range of movement in older adults and aids in rehabilitation, including for inflammatory joint diseases and arthritis.", "citations": {"0b91df07-9f16-4d7b-a315-06ee2639898f_906991366": 1.0}}, {"text": "Well-designed exercise programs for seniors living at home can prevent falls, fractures, and injuries.", "citations": {"184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782": 1.0}}, {"text": "Accidental falls are the leading cause of fatal injuries for people over 65, resulting in long-term pain, disability, and over $50 billion in annual medical costs.", "citations": {"184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782": 1.0, "e9fff66d-bee2-41b1-bdea-13cc907fcb0e_387083581": 0.5}}, {"text": "Removing trip hazards, ensuring proper lighting, and managing health through hydration, nutrition, and prescription review are key to fall prevention and healthy aging.", "citations": {"e9fff66d-bee2-41b1-bdea-13cc907fcb0e_387083581": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi reduces fall risk and alleviates arthritis symptoms in older adults by improving balance and relieving knee stiffness and pain.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi enhances balance, mobility, and cognitive function, benefiting patients with Parkinson's and dementia.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi's gentle movements stimulate muscles, tendons, joints, and bones, relieving spinal pressure and benefiting the nervous system.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi improves mobility and reduces stress in older adults with mobility limitations.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi improves balance, strength, and mobility in older adults, enabling daily activities.", "citations": {"34a5ef86-794c-4dd0-95a9-b1b3c3632633_326815735": 1.0}}, {"text": "Yoga enhances proprioception, balancing capacity, and reduces fear of falling in older adults.", "citations": {"bc9d8a85-ac6a-49d7-ad15-c535b79a0654_46520525": 1.0}}, {"text": "Yoga therapy is given in addition to standard therapy to study its effects on older adults using randomized controlled trials.", "citations": {"bc9d8a85-ac6a-49d7-ad15-c535b79a0654_46520525": 1.0}}, {"text": "Pilates is useful for people with reduced bone strength, aids in post-surgery rehabilitation, and promotes flexibility in older individuals.", "citations": {"0b91df07-9f16-4d7b-a315-06ee2639898f_906991366": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi lowers blood pressure, reduces sympathetic excitability, and improves balance and coordination.", "citations": {"b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi enhances flexibility, cardiovascular health, and mental clarity, benefiting seniors with mobility issues.", "citations": {"b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is an effective exercise for fall prevention and improved mobility in older adults with mobility or cognitive limitations, comparable to yoga and Pilates.", "citations": {"08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184": 1.0, "0b91df07-9f16-4d7b-a315-06ee2639898f_906991366": 0.5, "184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782": 0.25, "2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 0.125, "b387b7e2-f045-452b-8758-c89e0f69c760_775838414": 0.0625}}, {"text": "Tai Chi improves balance, reducing fall risk in older adults.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Older adults should practice Tai Chi three times a week.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi practice sessions should last one hour.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi practice can improve balance and mobility in older adults.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi helps improve balance, mobility, and fall prevention in older adults.", "citations": {"08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can reduce the risk of falls and related injuries in older adults.", "citations": {"184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782": 1.0}}, {"text": "The World Health Organization recommends at least 150 minutes of moderate-intensity aerobic exercise per week for adults over 65, including Tai Chi.", "citations": {"4502ea6b-f423-4f08-b3e9-2c45e7a80185_337609787": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi and exercise training can help elderly individuals enhance strength and balance, reducing fall risk.", "citations": {"43b9a6ad-8db0-4be1-b27c-8de54e53d895_973279368": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi practice improves balance, strength, and endurance, all essential for fall prevention.", "citations": {"80c8da15-5fa3-4f38-8fa6-3c8ddc7d04f2_904596165": 1.0}}, {"text": "A study found that 40 minutes of weekly Tai Chi can benefit older adults.", "citations": {"8138d416-ceaa-43d3-a92d-7ad903317f2b_135477836": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi practice with balance training can reduce injuries from trips in older adults.", "citations": {"9aef89be-a1de-42e1-8c46-7b3ceadee58f_797019169": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi practice can be adjusted based on individual physical response and needs.", "citations": {"43b9a6ad-8db0-4be1-b27c-8de54e53d895_973279368": 1.0}}, {"text": "Older adults should undergo a professional assessment before starting Tai Chi or any exercise program.", "citations": {"43b9a6ad-8db0-4be1-b27c-8de54e53d895_973279368": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can be modified to suit individual needs, making it accessible for older adults.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi practice, done regularly at least three times a week, can reduce falls and improve physical stability in older adults.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi exercises improve strength and balance, helping prevent falls in the elderly.", "citations": {"0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653": 1.0}}, {"text": "Exercise, including Tai Chi, can prevent falls in the healthy elderly and benefit those with certain health conditions.", "citations": {"0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi improves coordination in the elderly, reducing the risk of falls.", "citations": {"0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653": 1.0}}, {"text": "Physicians recommend Tai Chi to the elderly for its health benefits, including improved balance and strength.", "citations": {"0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653": 1.0}}, {"text": "The documents lack specific information on Tai Chi routines for Parkinson's or osteoporosis.", "citations": {"0f5cd105-7572-4a55-9c42-607d1c65be3d_663764653": 1.0}}, {"text": "Exercising, including Tai Chi, slows down Parkinson's symptoms and improves balance and coordination.", "citations": {"136a1867-6d40-43ba-88ad-89134162d014_22790693": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Parkinson's Foundation recommends 2.5 hours of weekly exercise, such as Tai Chi, to help manage the disease.", "citations": {"136a1867-6d40-43ba-88ad-89134162d014_22790693": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can help improve lung function and reduce fall risk in COPD patients.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi improves balance and mobility in Parkinson's patients, reducing the risk of falls.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi reduces fall risk in older adults by improving balance.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can help with balance, although its specific benefits for osteoporosis are unknown.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi benefits the nervous system and can be beneficial for older adults with certain health conditions.", "citations": {"2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437053624": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is a suitable exercise option for chronic obstructive pulmonary disease patients.", "citations": {"2a6f17f8-5f36-4821-977d-86f241134f43_16168056": 1.0}}, {"text": "Pulmonary rehabilitation programs include safe exercise guidance, such as Tai Chi, for COPD patients.", "citations": {"2a6f17f8-5f36-4821-977d-86f241134f43_16168056": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi breathing exercises can strengthen lungs and manage shortness of breath.", "citations": {"2a6f17f8-5f36-4821-977d-86f241134f43_16168056": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi reduces waist circumference in elderly with central obesity, lowering fall risk.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is a suitable exercise for elderly with mobility issues and certain health conditions.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi can increase high-density cholesterol levels and reduce cardiovascular disease risk.", "citations": {"41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi is a recommended exercise for slowing down Parkinson's disease symptoms.", "citations": {"50f66e61-1706-4088-b019-f2bc5776b96f_887026344": 1.0}}, {"text": "Combining exercise, like Tai Chi, with medication can slow Parkinson's disease deterioration.", "citations": {"50f66e61-1706-4088-b019-f2bc5776b96f_887026344": 1.0}}, {"text": "At least 30 minutes of exercise, like Tai Chi, per session is recommended to help manage Parkinson's disease.", "citations": {"50f66e61-1706-4088-b019-f2bc5776b96f_887026344": 1.0}}, {"text": "The American Parkinson Foundation recommends a personalized exercise plan that may include Tai Chi.", "citations": {"50f66e61-1706-4088-b019-f2bc5776b96f_887026344": 1.0}}, {"text": "Parkinson's disease patients can improve walking ability with Tai Chi therapy.", "citations": {"59c0eb4e-e325-4297-a518-cd3e0286d830_727827473": 1.0}}, {"text": 