ng and treating diseases like Parkinson's.", "citations": {"db491037-7f64-4325-86de-077f5d2102f9_693279383": 1.0}}, {"text": "One in four seniors over 65 will fall annually, with about one in five falls resulting in serious injuries like broken bones.", "citations": {"08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184": 1.0}}, {"text": "A previous history of falls is the main risk factor, and physical balance is influenced by various systems, including sensory and muscular factors.", "citations": {"08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tai Chi and yoga can improve balance and prevent falls.", "citations": {"08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184": 1.0}}, {"text": "Pilates improves flexibility, strengthens core muscles, and reduces fall risk in older adults.", "citations": {"0b91df07-9f16-4d7b-a315-06ee2639898f_906991366": 1.0}}, {"text": "Pilates is beneficial for older adults with mobility limitations, including those with arthritis, osteoporosis, and musculoskeletal issues.", "citations": {"0b91df07-9f16-4d7b-a315-06ee2639898f_906991366": 1.0}}], "references": ["43b9a6ad-8db0-4be1-b27c-8de54e53d895_973279368", "97b014c9-d996-4206-b240-6c9c6a4b3ac0_531746640", "41541b00-f7b4-4a15-8ec7-2d7431c26695_263273629", "0b91df07-9f16-4d7b-a315-06ee2639898f_906991366", "08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184", "2a6f17f8-5f36-4821-977d-86f241134f43_16168056", "184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782", "59c0eb4e-e325-4297-a518-cd3e0286d830_727827473", "46aac298-47e3-40c4-b112-cf04be57240a_846751787", "80c8da15-5fa3-4f38-8fa6-3c8ddc7d04f2_904596165", "bc9d8a85-ac6a-49d7-ad15-c535b79a0654_46520525", "14b74b2e-eb4c-4316-a13f-2b94ab1cae1a_760925045", "db491037-7f64-4325-86de-077f5d2102f9_693279383", "4502ea6b-f423-4f08-b3e9-2c45e7a80185_337609787", "136a1867-6d40-43ba-88ad-89134162d014_22790693", "a9f634b0-048e-43c0-86b2-621504a62ac9_579770369", "accc8f73-5428-4f0e-a86d-27bf7abd2563_463771486", "2e864b6f-2e85-4876-845a-6831478b1237_437