 {"48d9908d-d5d6-4741-8c6b-db00de53769c_586913968": 1.0}}, {"text": "40% of the company's mid-level management positions are held by women.", "citations": {"48d9908d-d5d6-4741-8c6b-db00de53769c_586913968": 1.0}}, {"text": "Fleet Alliance has 33% female representation on its board and executive level.", "citations": {"48d9908d-d5d6-4741-8c6b-db00de53769c_586913968": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company prioritizes fairness, trust, engagement, and respect to support employee growth and development.", "citations": {"48d9908d-d5d6-4741-8c6b-db00de53769c_586913968": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ryder's Women Leadership Forum supports female career growth by developing skills and advancing careers.", "citations": {"63293454-a4ca-48c4-8a16-eba4dfe87ee5_38683585": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company exceeds industry averages in promoting women in the workplace.", "citations": {"63293454-a4ca-48c4-8a16-eba4dfe87ee5_38683585": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ryder offers competitive compensation and benefits for women.", "citations": {"63293454-a4ca-48c4-8a16-eba4dfe87ee5_38683585": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company provides career advancement opportunities to help women reach their full potential.", "citations": {"63293454-a4ca-48c4-8a16-eba4dfe87ee5_38683585": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ryder supports women's personal and professional needs to achieve family and work balance.", "citations": {"63293454-a4ca-48c4-8a16-eba4dfe87ee5_38683585": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women occupy traditionally male positions at Meest Group, including entire teams in warehouses and sorting centers.", "citations": {"65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178": 1.0}}, {"text": "Meest has formed all-women teams in male-dominated warehouses and sorting centers.", "citations": {"65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women demonstrate their capabilities and value as Meest employees through effective work and consistency.", "citations": {"65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178": 1.0}}, {"text": "ATB has over 56 thousand employees, with women making up 67% of the workforce.", "citations": {"65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women in ATB work in traditionally male positions, including security guards.", "citations": {"65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ferrexpo signed the Women's Empowerment Principles to promote gender equality and create a fair work environment.", "citations": {"65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company has increased women in leadership by 60% since 2020, promoting gender diversity.", "citations": {"65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ferrexpo aims for 25% female leadership by 2030 to promote gender equality.", "citations": {"65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178": 1.0}}, {"text": "The available documents do not mention KPIs for female crane operators, making performance assessment difficult.", "citations": {"b4382681-f199-43dc-a190-ef39b5bf9a5d_476864776": 1.0}}, {"text": "Amelia Walker-Ross is a service manager at Penske Canada, supervising 10 mechanics.", "citations": {"b4382681-f199-43dc-a190-ef39b5bf9a5d_476864776": 1.0}}, {"text": "Walker-Ross persevered through unwelcome feedback from male coworkers, achieving success through resilience and determination.", "citations": {"b4382681-f199-43dc-a190-ef39b5bf9a5d_476864776": 1.0}}, {"text": "Four women at Tata Steel Meramandali operate Stacker-cum Reclaimers, breaking the gender barrier in a male-dominated role.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company promotes diversity among vendor partners to create a more inclusive work environment.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tata Steel aims for a diverse and inclusive workplace.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}, {"text": "The number of female train drivers rose from 54 in 2022 to 76 in 2023.", "citations": {"f3130371-ec9f-4dee-a06c-18c9f5abdefd_177458598": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female representation among drivers reached 9.3% in 2023.", "citations": {"f3130371-ec9f-4dee-a06c-18c9f5abdefd_177458598": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women hold 42.9% of new apprenticeships in 2023.", "citations": {"f3130371-ec9f-4dee-a06c-18c9f5abdefd_177458598": 1.0}}, {"text": "The gender pay gap for TfW Rail and Group was reduced to 16.2% and 14.1%, respectively.", "citations": {"f3130371-ec9f-4dee-a06c-18c9f5abdefd_177458598": 1.0}}, {"text": "TfW plans to publish KPIs to measure and promote female recruitment and gender diversity.", "citations": {"f3130371-ec9f-4dee-a06c-18c9f5abdefd_177458598": 1.0}}, {"text": "TfW has invested in leadership training for women to develop their skills and advance their careers.", "citations": {"f3130371-ec9f-4dee-a06c-18c9f5abdefd_177458598": 1.0}}, {"text": "TfW aims to reduce unconscious bias to create a fair and inclusive work environment.", "citations": {"f3130371-ec9f-4dee-a06c-18c9f5abdefd_177458598": 1.0}}, {"text": "TfW will offer women more secondment opportunities to gain experience and develop their skills.", "citations": {"f3130371-ec9f-4dee-a06c-18c9f5abdefd_177458598": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women are achieving greater pay equality in higher-salaried roles.", "citations": {"f3130371-ec9f-4dee-a06c-18c9f5abdefd_177458598": 1.0}}, {"text": "KPIs will measure the success of female recruitment to track progress in promoting gender diversity.", "citations": {"f3130371-ec9f-4dee-a06c-18c9f5abdefd_177458598": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women are taking on roles in male-dominated fields like driving, construction, and maritime, including as crane operators.", "citations": {"14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies promoting gender equality are more competitive and profitable, a key factor in underrepresented industries like construction and maritime.", "citations": {"37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371": 1.0}}, {"text": "The United Nations Environment Programme considers promoting gender diversity crucial in male-dominated fields like construction and maritime.", "citations": {"37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371": 1.0}}, {"text": "Rewriting job descriptions and partnering with vocational schools can make hiring more inclusive and encourage underrepresented individuals, including women, to pursue certain careers.", "citations": {"37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371": 1.0}}, {"text": "A diverse workforce is essential for the construction and maritime industries, addressing labor shortages and bringing diverse perspectives.", "citations": {"37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ryder, a transportation company, has a Women Leadership Forum to promote female career growth.", "citations": {"63293454-a4ca-48c4-8a16-eba4dfe87ee5_38683585": 1.0}}, {"text": "XPO Logistics launched a female driver academy, a strategy that could also recruit female crane operators.", "citations": {"86cbd746-91e5-4583-a65d-05c1f8904f44_169456569": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women comprise 16% of the construction workforce and hold only 4% of site manager positions.", "citations": {"810dbd83-66fd-46d5-b733-7fd200ef200c_901656784": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Women into Home Building Employment Programme offers funded training and childcare support to encourage women to pursue construction careers.", "citations": {"810dbd83-66fd-46d5-b733-7fd200ef200c_901656784": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tata Steel hired four female Stacker-cum Reclaimer operators, promoting diversity and breaking traditional gender barriers.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}, {"text": "MDOT's on-the-job construction training program for women and minorities has more than doubled in enrollment from 2017 to 2021.", "citations": {"e54d5d6e-0c6a-47f4-9834-81419f13a22e_14234603": 1.0}}, {"text": "On-the-job training helps recruit women to construction crews.", "citations": {"e54d5d6e-0c6a-47f4-9834-81419f13a22e_14234603": 1.0}}, {"text": "Transport for Wales reduced its gender pay gap by recruiting female train drivers and investing in women's leadership training, strategies that can also promote diversity in construction and maritime.", "citations": {"f3130371-ec9f-4dee-a06c-18c9f5abdefd_177458598": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female truck drivers have increased by 80% in 20 years, with fewer fines and accidents, showing potential for women to excel in male-dominated roles like crane operation.", "citations": {"f8c8c06e-76b0-48f9-a66b-758fd08d0ac4_246084211": 1.0}}, {"text": "Confidence is key for women to succeed in male-dominated industries like construction and maritime.", "citations": {"f8c8c06e-76b0-48f9-a66b-758fd08d0ac4_246084211": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hiring female crane operators can bring diversity and improve safety and reduce costs in male-dominated industries.", "citations": {"f8c8c06e-76b0-48f9-a66b-758fd08d0ac4_246084211": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female crane operators face challenges balancing careers and family due to industry bias and guilt over not being at home with their children.", "citations": {"14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women in male-dominated industries face unfair treatment, bias, and intimidation from male colleagues.", "citations": {"14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women make up only 4% of skilled trades in the male-dominated construction industry.", "citations": {"3650242a-8a87-4c79-93c6-8a4315587753_706272734": 1.0}}, {"text": "Historical barriers have limited women's opportunities in construction, but investments aim to increase inclusion.", "citations": {"3650242a-8a87-4c79-93c6-8a4315587753_706272734": 1.0}}, {"text": "Unity LLP has 25 women in 152 positions, actively working to increase women's inclusion.", "citations": {"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female crane operators need to be calm and attentive.", "citations": {"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women in construction and maritime often face safety risks due to ill-fitting personal protective equipment (PPE).", "citations": {"8209db46-acf4-4c44-b5a9-32e037edd529_253256452": 1.0}}, {"text": "In the offshore industry, many female workers have ill-fitting PPE, including 68% with coveralls, 19% with safety shoes, and 43% with gloves.", "citations": {"8209db46-acf4-4c44-b5a9-32e037edd529_253256452": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women represent only 1.2% of the global seafarer workforce.", "citations": {"8488df16-98af-409c-aa7b-5ea6bc01fe53_306144329": 1.0}}, {"text": "There has been a 45.8% increase in women seafarers since 2015, with initiatives like scholarships and training programs supporting their growth in the maritime industry.", "citations": {"8488df16-98af-409c-aa7b-5ea6bc01fe53_306144329": 1.0}}, {"text": "The International Maritime Organisation and companies like Tata Steel are promoting diversity and inclusion.", "citations": {"905ea931-32d5-4971-b223-a102ade17176_665195989": 1.0, "c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 0.5}}, {"text": "Virtual reality training programs can help women succeed in male-dominated industries.", "citations": {"bcda4cee-ba76-4966-8dc6-1bfea85b5870_708941358": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diversity and inclusion initiatives can help promote gender equality in construction and maritime.", "citations": {"c40b5c1c-6e7a-45f6-a314-adcf276acb8c_663217418": 1.0}}, {"text": "Creating women's networks and implementing diversity initiatives can address challenges faced by female crane operators.", "citations": {"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554": 1.0}}, {"text": "Government initiatives, like the Flexible Working Act, support women in construction and maritime.", "citations": {"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women are increasingly breaking down traditional gender barriers in the construction and maritime industries, marking a shift towards greater gender equality.", "citations": {"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female crane operators need specialized training in areas like mobile crane operation and heavy equipment use to succeed.", "citations": {"271671f0-6c94-4942-a190-b98ef346ac8e_636011655": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female crane operators can benefit from TVET vocational training programs.", "citations": {"580f2642-46bb-44aa-9d11-f21b3ba03ac5_631417095": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saudi Technical Institute offers a diploma program for female crane operators covering crane operation, lifting, loading, and health and safety.", "citations": {"7ffabb8f-2da3-4672-864f-cb8ade82fa00_62847236": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female crane operators need technical skills, calmness, and attentiveness to excel in their roles.", "citations": {"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 1.0}}, {"text": "The maritime industry requires female crane operators to have STCW certification and digital skills.", "citations": {"575a1243-3c37-4fc9-9332-a8f5fdaf66ee_682674291": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women can benefit from leadership training programs like the Maritime SheEO Leadership Accelerator Programme, which helps break down traditional gender barriers.", "citations": {"575a1243-3c37-4fc9-9332-a8f5fdaf66ee_682674291": 1.0}}, {"text": "To become certified, women crane operators must undergo training and obtain certifications like the NCCCO.", "citations": {"ab8df9e5-b36b-4dd7-8673-9fa067add4c1_1053223185": 1.0}}, {"text": "Training programs for female crane operators can cost $3000 to $4000, but financial assistance like scholarships and grants may be available.", "citations": {"ab8df9e5-b36b-4dd7-8673-9fa067add4c1_1053223185": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Vocational Training Council offers apprenticeships with training allowances to help women gain skills and experience.", "citations": {"b6f168d0-6854-477d-bfd8-2241bf3d1593_244699964": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female crane operators may require certifications like the 06102 or 06201.", "citations": {"b6fb4342-3bba-47b7-852a-325e7aa4f3f6_1007863897": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female crane operators must have a mechanical engineering diploma and safety induction training.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female crane operators require on-the-job training and safety induction programs to gain necessary experience and skills.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tata Steel provides onboarding training for female operators and promotes diversity among vendor partners.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}, {"text": "LANA Academy offers training programs for women in technical fields like supply chain management, health and safety, and business administration.", "citations": {"dc901cf7-47c1-45fc-97fd-58475f2fc539_286143531": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diverse teams drive innovation, crucial for construction and maritime companies to stay competitive.", "citations": {"0b678d1c-9c60-438e-9aa0-f96469772485_682435552": 1.0}}, {"text": "Inclusion and diversity can increase earnings by 25% or more, particularly in recruiting and retaining female crane operators.", "citations": {"0b678d1c-9c60-438e-9aa0-f96469772485_682435552": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diverse teams achieve better business strategies through gender parity and inclusion.", "citations": {"0b678d1c-9c60-438e-9aa0-f96469772485_682435552": 1.0}}, {"text": "Training executives on inclusion and diversity helps create a culture of equality and empowerment.", "citations": {"0b678d1c-9c60-438e-9aa0-f96469772485_682435552": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diversity and Inclusion Councils develop strategies to promote diversity and inclusion in industries like construction and maritime.", "citations": {"0b678d1c-9c60-438e-9aa0-f96469772485_682435552": 1.0}}, {"text": "Celebrating employee differences promotes respect and inclusion through initiatives like awards and recognition programs.", "citations": {"0b678d1c-9c60-438e-9aa0-f96469772485_682435552": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Queensland government has launched the Women in Manufacturing Apprentice Awards to attract and promote women in the industry.", "citations": {"11b347c7-8980-4909-afb4-befebd9b3365_709054618": 1.0}}, {"text": "BlueScope Steel has achieved a 30% female manufacturing workforce through its diversity policies, serving as a model for other companies.", "citations": {"11b347c7-8980-4909-afb4-befebd9b3365_709054618": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diversity is essential for the construction and maritime industries to remain competitive.", "citations": {"11b347c7-8980-4909-afb4-befebd9b3365_709054618": 1.0}}, {"text": "The manufacturing sector needs more women and can achieve this through diversity and inclusion initiatives.", "citations": {"11b347c7-8980-4909-afb4-befebd9b3365_709054618": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women can excel in male-dominated areas like truck driving and crane operating with the right training and support.", "citations": {"14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female drivers and crane operators can balance work and motherhood with the right support systems.", "citations": {"14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women can succeed in male-dominated fields with determination, hard work, and professionalism.", "citations": {"14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281": 1.0}}, {"text": "Family and employer support is essential for female drivers and crane operators, and can be provided through initiatives like flexible work arrangements and mentorship programs.", "citations": {"14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women make up 24% of the US waste management workforce, but gender equality promotes competitiveness and attracts more women.", "citations": {"37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371": 1.0}}, {"text": "Inclusive hiring practices benefit waste management companies through initiatives like rewriting job descriptions and promoting diversity.", "citations": {"37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371": 1.0}}, {"text": "Partnerships with schools can promote diverse careers, including those in construction and maritime industries.", "citations": {"37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371": 1.0}}, {"text": "Meralco introduced female linecrew trainees in 2013, providing equal training to both males and females.", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 1.0}}, {"text": "Meralco promotes fairness and equality among all employees, regardless of gender.", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 1.0}}, {"text": "Building inclusion throughout organization levels is crucial and can be achieved by creating support systems and promoting diversity.", "citations": {"59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women should make up 30% of decision-making forums, which can be achieved by promoting them to leadership positions.", "citations": {"59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573": 1.0}}, {"text": "Support systems, such as training and mentorship programs, enable gender parity in technical positions.", "citations": {"59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ryder is a top company for women in transportation with above-average female career growth.", "citations": {"63293454-a4ca-48c4-8a16-eba4dfe87ee5_38683585": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ryder supports women's professional development and provides competitive compensation and benefits.", "citations": {"63293454-a4ca-48c4-8a16-eba4dfe87ee5_38683585": 1.0}}, {"text": "TransPennine Express has nearly a quarter of its engineering team as women, exceeding the UK rail industry's national average for female representation.", "citations": {"81a9ef56-c341-4ec4-9c48-dccc8e0a0888_1071056663": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women make up 16.5% of the UK rail industry workforce, but companies like TransPennine Express aim to increase this.", "citations": {"81a9ef56-c341-4ec4-9c48-dccc8e0a0888_1071056663": 1.0}}, {"text": "XPO Logistics launched a female driver academy with 12-16 week training.", "citations": {"86cbd746-91e5-4583-a65d-05c1f8904f44_169456569": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tata Steel hired four female operators as part of its goal to build a diverse and inclusive workplace.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}, {"text": "MDOT's on-the-job construction training program for women and minorities has more than doubled in enrollment from 2017 to 2021.", "citations": {"e54d5d6e-0c6a-47f4-9834-81419f13a22e_14234603": 1.0}}, {"text": "On-the-job training helps recruit women to construction crews.", "citations": {"e54d5d6e-0c6a-47f4-9834-81419f13a22e_14234603": 1.0}}, {"text": "Meralco's introduction of female linecrew trainees in 2013 helped break traditional gender barriers in the industry.", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 1.0}}, {"text": "Meralco provides equal training to male and female linecrew aspirants.", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's six-month Linecrew Training Program provides a path for female trainees to become third-class linecrew.", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 1.0}}, {"text": "Meralco promotes gender equality and career growth, as seen in women's progression to higher positions like Quality Inspector.", "citations": {"42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_682318363": 1.0}}, {"text": "Fleet Alliance's workforce is 53% female, exceeding the national average.", "citations": {"48d9908d-d5d6-4741-8c6b-db00de53769c_586913968": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company has 40% female representation in mid-level management, exceeding the required percentage.", "citations": {"48d9908d-d5d6-4741-8c6b-db00de53769c_586913968": 1.0}}, {"text": "Fleet Alliance was ranked the Best Workplace for Women in 2022, based 85% on women's workplace experience reports.", "citations": {"48d9908d-d5d6-4741-8c6b-db00de53769c_586913968": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies like Meest have formed all-women teams in traditionally male-dominated roles, proving their effectiveness.", "citations": {"65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ferrexpo has increased female leadership by 60% since 2020, targeting 25% by 2030.", "citations": {"65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178": 1.0}}, {"text": "At Tata Steel Meramandali, four women work as Stacker-cum Reclaimer operators and one as a Hyva operator, a company first.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}, {"text": "The performance and safety of female crane operators are not compared to their male counterparts, and no success metrics are provided.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}, {"text": "Transport for Wales reduced its gender pay gap, recruiting 22 female train drivers in 2022/23, bringing the total to 76 as of April 2023.", "citations": {"f3130371-ec9f-4dee-a06c-18c9f5abdefd_177458598": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company has increased female apprenticeships to 42.9% and will introduce key performance indicators for female recruitment.", "citations": {"f3130371-ec9f-4dee-a06c-18c9f5abdefd_177458598": 1.0}}, {"text": "There is a lack of data on how female crane operators compare to males in performance, safety, and career advancement.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}], "references": ["a734b9d4-037d-4ae4-9f0a-93ec5bf066f3_184464090", "bcda4cee-ba76-4966-8dc6-1bfea85b5870_708941358", "c40b5c1c-6e7a-45f6-a314-adcf276acb8c_663217418", "18936b99-e516-4cca-b846-d29e85b6c832_522368479", "14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281", "7eb81049-0a87-41be-95e3-2dfd47b4aeca_72244829", "8488df16-98af-409c-aa7b-5ea6bc01fe53_306144329", "85e27e71-b078-41a0-ab97-3a66be5b0bbf_218435243", "59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777", "ab8df9e5-b36b-4dd7-8673-9fa067add4c1_1053223185", "575a1243-3c3