{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1026", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The construction and maritime industries, traditionally male-dominated, are seeing more women excel in roles like crane operators.", "citations": {"3a8cbfea-9ef3-4a87-b89f-73c826c436b8_140000997": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women hold 4% of national construction trade jobs and 5% of Illinois apprenticeships.", "citations": {"3650242a-8a87-4c79-93c6-8a4315587753_706272734": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women are making significant strides in breaking down traditional gender barriers in construction and maritime.", "citations": {"14088fa6-23b4-4d55-b96b-803f49740287_341799643": 1.0}}, {"text": "The construction industry, including companies like Leighton, promotes diversity and inclusion, aiming for equal gender representation.", "citations": {"59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777": 1.0}}, {"text": "Leighton offers paid maternity and paternity leave beyond statutory requirements, with women making up 20% of its Hong Kong workforce.", "citations": {"59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777": 1.0}}, {"text": "US construction jobs held by women reached 14.1 percent, totaling 440,000 in April, the highest since 2001.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female construction workers earn 99 cents for every dollar earned by males.", "citations": {"b2e71ca1-f74f-41be-98bf-90b27f0ff99c_930292724": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women are increasingly entering the construction industry, with female apprentices nearly doubling from 2016 to 2019.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}, {"text": "Farkhana Safargaleeva, a 59-year-old crane operator, returned to work after retirement with 15 years of experience.", "citations": {"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female crane operators at Unity LLP are supported by relatives and colleagues, and require calmness and attentiveness.", "citations": {"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tata Steel has hired female operators and promotes workplace diversity and inclusion.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women comprise only 10.9 percent of the construction industry's workforce.", "citations": {"b2e71ca1-f74f-41be-98bf-90b27f0ff99c_930292724": 1.0}}, {"text": "Programs like the Women into Home Building Employment Programme aim to promote industry careers to young women.", "citations": {"b2e71ca1-f74f-41be-98bf-90b27f0ff99c_930292724": 1.0}}, {"text": "Suffolk Construction's Career Start program aims to recruit women for traditionally male-dominated jobs.", "citations": {"c6691d00-dfb0-4b34-8d9d-a1453a0429a1_717856038": 1.0}}, {"text": "Recruiting women in construction signals a changing mindset and provides role models for young girls.", "citations": {"c6691d00-dfb0-4b34-8d9d-a1453a0429a1_717856038": 1.0}}, {"text": "The construction industry is shifting towards greater gender equality, with women excelling in male-dominated roles.", "citations": {"b2e71ca1-f74f-41be-98bf-90b27f0ff99c_930292724": 1.0}}, {"text": "The International Maritime Organisation (IMO) aims to achieve global gender equality in the maritime sector by promoting women's participation.", "citations": {"02734096-17ba-4798-88b0-4e734752dc20_582620589": 1.0}}, {"text": "AASTMT and AWIMA signed an MoU to promote gender equality in the maritime sector.", "citations": {"02734096-17ba-4798-88b0-4e734752dc20_582620589": 1.0}}, {"text": "Mentorship programs can support women's career advancement in male-dominated fields by connecting them with top professionals.", "citations": {"235c8d54-6713-4ceb-808e-ba1232c65272_508111555": 1.0}}, {"text": "These programs can be tailored to specific industries, such as crane operation, to support women's careers.", "citations": {"235c8d54-6713-4ceb-808e-ba1232c65272_508111555": 1.0}}, {"text": "Networking opportunities, provided through industry events and conferences, are essential for career growth and development.", "citations": {"235c8d54-6713-4ceb-808e-ba1232c65272_508111555": 1.0}}, {"text": "Past beneficiaries can serve as role models, inspiring other women to pursue careers in these industries.", "citations": {"235c8d54-6713-4ceb-808e-ba1232c65272_508111555": 1.0}}, {"text": "Mentorship and coaching can help women develop skills and confidence to take on leadership roles.", "citations": {"23787d87-48cd-4f56-a076-c0a0c72cc698_163171819": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies with more women in leadership are 25% more likely to exceed profitability, making mentorship and networking essential for female crane operators.", "citations": {"23787d87-48cd-4f56-a076-c0a0c72cc698_163171819": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Women in Food & Agriculture Mentorship Program matches applicants with mentors based on preferences like gender and industry sector.", "citations": {"4be0a8db-bf89-4f0b-9686-abfc64a2cc95_333840456": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Sisters in Mining program offers women 7-day pre-employment and 12-month training, on-job coaching, and vocational education to succeed in mining.", "citations": {"9b95a346-03b3-49ba-86e4-adf7e644b438_910039464": 1.0}}, {"text": "Mentorship programs can support female crane operators' careers by providing necessary skills and guidance.", "citations": {"98290703-62ef-4d7a-866f-e52dbc55c3d8_172969558": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female crane operators need professional skills training.", "citations": {"061641d6-49c2-4b0c-ac1e-001c86b80a9e_89871675": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Global Wind Organisation provides essential basic safety training certificates for female crane operators.", "citations": {"061641d6-49c2-4b0c-ac1e-001c86b80a9e_89871675": 1.0}}, {"text": "The NCDMB offers a 12-month training program in Mobile Crane Operation for young university graduates.", "citations": {"271671f0-6c94-4942-a190-b98ef346ac8e_636011655": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hands-on training is held in Port Harcourt and Warri, providing practical experience for female crane operators.", "citations": {"271671f0-6c94-4942-a190-b98ef346ac8e_636011655": 1.0}}, {"text": "Farkhana Safargaleeva, a female crane operator with 15 years of experience, breaks stereotypes in a male-dominated field.", "citations": {"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women comprise 25 of 152 employees at Unity LLP and are praised by the chief engineer as excellent professionals.", "citations": {"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500": 1.0}}, {"text": "The government supports TVET institutions, providing practical training for artisans, including female crane operators.", "citations": {"580f2642-46bb-44aa-9d11-f21b3ba03ac5_631417095": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Saudi Technical Institute offers a two-year diploma program in Crane Operation, covering Lifting and Loading techniques.", "citations": {"7ffabb8f-2da3-4672-864f-cb8ade82fa00_62847236": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tata Steel provides training for female Stacker-cum Reclaimer operators.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}, {"text": "Crane operators need diverse technical skills and constant learning to excel.", "citations": {"ecab6dcb-e837-480d-93de-bd45c3ca82e0_161225094": 1.0}}, {"text": "Professional skill competitions help crane operators work safely and efficiently.", "citations": {"ecab6dcb-e837-480d-93de-bd45c3ca82e0_161225094": 1.0}}, {"text": "The construction and maritime industries are traditionally male-dominated, but initiatives like the UAE's \"Leaders in Difference\" are promoting diversity and empowering women.", "citations": {"446499ae-3270-4c22-a54c-07c275d9bfe4_1027392030": 1.0}}, {"text": "The International Maritime Organization (IMO) aims to achieve gender equality in the maritime sector through its Gender Diversity Programme.", "citations": {"02734096-17ba-4798-88b0-4e734752dc20_582620589": 1.0}}, {"text": "DP World prioritizes women in leadership and celebrates UAE Women's Day to promote diversity.", "citations": {"15b25587-4623-4f56-abd9-a945d1453dc4_255848621": 1.0}}, {"text": "JLL has launched the Women in Construction Initiative to promote diversity and raise awareness about the construction profession.", "citations": {"5911a757-3ab7-4098-ab50-709932704fef_878097771": 1.0}}, {"text": "Leighton promotes diversity with inclusive policies, including paid maternity and paternity leave.", "citations": {"59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777": 1.0}}, {"text": "EGA employs over 470 women in the UAE, aiming for 25% in supervisory positions by 2025.", "citations": {"8c446e64-679e-483f-9024-2afc82d0494a_180680552": 1.0}}, {"text": "Vistry Western has a 50% female director ratio and 34% female employees, exceeding the industry average.", "citations": {"980697fc-65d2-4a9e-b57c-9fc46559ec33_512741972": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Maritime Employee Survey tracks industry diversity, inclusion, and global employment trends.", "citations": {"07631742-4202-4035-a1b6-b234f8adbed3_328786045": 1.0}}, {"text": "The construction industry is promoting diversity and inclusion through initiatives like Construction Inclusion Week.", "citations": {"e311f92c-ac1a-4dfb-a548-ed2580d4d889_106933672": 1.0}}, {"text": "The IMO has launched the International Day for Women in Maritime to support industry diversity and inclusivity.", "citations": {"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women can assume roles in male-dominated areas, challenging traditional gender barriers.", "citations": {"14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281": 1.0}}, {"text": "Family and employer support is crucial for female crane operators' career success.", "citations": {"14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281": 1.0}}, {"text": "WANTT helps women enter the construction industry through pre-apprenticeships and training.", "citations": {"1c945363-358c-4398-9ccb-11aac43f6ef2_118306949": 1.0}}, {"text": "West Virginia Women Work offers tuition-free training in nontraditional occupations like construction and crane operation.", "citations": {"5bceb5cf-8197-45d5-949b-f90b2c9e792c_540770565": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Step Up for Women Construction Program teaches women skills like carpentry, electrical, plumbing, and welding for entry-level construction positions and apprenticeships.", "citations": {"5bceb5cf-8197-45d5-949b-f90b2c9e792c_540770565": 1.0}}, {"text": "Thiess' Sisters in Mining program supports women in mining with 12-month training and coaching to increase female participation.", "citations": {"9b95a346-03b3-49ba-86e4-adf7e644b438_910039464": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tata Steel provides on-the-job training to female operators to promote gender balance in the workforce.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}, {"text": "MDOT offers on-the-job training for women and minorities to increase female participation in construction.", "citations": {"e54d5d6e-0c6a-47f4-9834-81419f13a22e_14234603": 1.0}}], "references": ["3a8cbfea-9ef3-4a87-b89f-73c826c436b8_140000997", "ecab6dcb-e837-480d-93de-bd45c3ca82e0_161225094", "14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281", "8c446e64-679e-483f-9024-2afc82d0494a_180680552", "c6691d00-dfb0-4b34-8d9d-a1453a0429a1_717856038", "f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554", "580f2642-46bb-44aa-9d11-f21b3ba03ac5_631417095", "59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777", "14088fa6-23b4-4d55-b96b-803f49740287_341799643", "b2e71ca1-f74f-41be-98bf-90b27f0ff99c_930292724", "e54d5d6e-0c6a-47f4-9834-81419f13a22e_14234603", "485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500", "98290703-62ef-4d7a-866f-e52dbc55c3d8_172969558", "4be0a8db-bf89-4f0b-9686-abfc64a2cc95_333840456", "061641d6-49c2-4b0c-ac1e-001c86b80a9e_89871675", "446499ae-3270-4c22-a54c-07c275d9bfe4_1027392030", "c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220", "9b95a346-03b3-49ba-86e4-adf7e644b438_910039464", "3650242a-8a87-4c79-93c6-8a4315587753_706272734", "02734096-17ba-4798-88b0-4e7