{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1027", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The construction industry is traditionally male-dominated, but women made up 10.9 percent of employees in 2020.", "citations": {"b2e71ca1-f74f-41be-98bf-90b27f0ff99c_930292724": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women are becoming crane operators, with companies like Tata Steel hiring and training them, challenging traditional gender barriers.", "citations": {"c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220": 1.0}}, {"text": "Technology has increased the accessibility and appeal of crane operation to women, providing a safer environment.", "citations": {"ea2803e9-2428-4e1b-8a0a-9173914415c5_864708180": 1.0}}, {"text": "Construction companies have implemented diversity and inclusion initiatives, including paid leave and flexible work policies, to recruit and retain female employees.", "citations": {"59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Biden administration has tied $6B in climate funding to DEI requirements, promoting diversity and inclusion in the construction industry.", "citations": {"34bd4e92-86da-4bbd-9e68-489fd37f0abc_260688023": 1.0}}, {"text": "Construction companies can provide training and support for women to increase female participation in crane operation roles.", "citations": {"c6691d00-dfb0-4b34-8d9d-a1453a0429a1_717856038": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diversity and inclusion initiatives have increased female participation in the construction industry, challenging traditional gender barriers.", "citations": {"18936b99-e516-4cca-b846-d29e85b6c832_522368479": 1.0}}, {"text": "Investing in education and training, along with inclusive policies, can empower women in construction and promote gender equality.", "citations": {"c40b5c1c-6e7a-45f6-a314-adcf276acb8c_663217418": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies can attract and retain female employees by prioritizing safety and family-first culture.", "citations": {"14088fa6-23b4-4d55-b96b-803f49740287_341799643": 1.0}}, {"text": "Mentorship programs can help women in construction by providing guidance and support.", "citations": {"14088fa6-23b4-4d55-b96b-803f49740287_341799643": 1.0}}, {"text": "Language and behaviours are crucial for building an inclusive culture and improving industry performance.", "citations": {"b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_803111217": 1.0}}, {"text": "Leadership behaviours like openness, curiosity, and humility drive inclusion, requiring psychological safety.", "citations": {"b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_803111217": 1.0}}, {"text": "The construction industry can benefit from initiatives like Women into Construction, which offers funded training and childcare support.", "citations": {"810dbd83-66fd-46d5-b733-7fd200ef200c_901656784": 1.0}}, {"text": "On-the-job training programs, like MDOT's, can recruit women to construction and have seen significant growth in female enrollment.", "citations": {"e54d5d6e-0c6a-47f4-9834-81419f13a22e_14234603": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women can succeed in construction leadership with perseverance and attention to detail.", "citations": {"e54d5d6e-0c6a-47f4-9834-81419f13a22e_14234603": 1.0}}, {"text": "Only 10 percent of construction workers are female, but role models and early math and science education can encourage more girls to join the field.", "citations": {"c6691d00-dfb0-4b34-8d9d-a1453a0429a1_717856038": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diversifying the workforce brings a wealth of knowledge and experiences, signaling a shift towards greater gender equality.", "citations": {"c6691d00-dfb0-4b34-8d9d-a1453a0429a1_717856038": 1.0}}, {"text": "In the US, women comprise 14.1% of construction workers, with one quarter facing sexual harassment.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female construction workers often face unequal treatment, yet they earn higher salaries, with electricians averaging $59,000.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}, {"text": "Construction managers earn $98,500 per year, and female apprentices nearly doubled from 2016 to 2019.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sustainability and family-friendly culture can attract female workers to construction trades, promoting gender equality and diversity.", "citations": {"f73c1329-0b74-4166-9635-b300ed83ff84_963588351": 1.0}}, {"text": "The WANTT program offers pre-apprenticeship training for women in construction, including tool usage, blueprint reading, and OSHA and CPR certifications, along with job fairs.", "citations": {"1c945363-358c-4398-9ccb-11aac43f6ef2_118306949": 1.0}}, {"text": "Labor shortages drive women into traditional male jobs, where they prove to be valuable assets due to their strong work ethic.", "citations": {"4c0ee3ad-3947-4c32-9bdc-e1ea45fa3dd9_966556193": 1.0}}], "references": ["b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_803111217", "f73c1329-0b74-4166-9635-b300ed83ff84_963588351", "589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743", "34bd4e92-86da-4bbd-9e68-489fd37f0abc_260688023", "b2e71ca1-f74f-41be-98bf-90b27f0ff99c_930292724", "1c945363-358c-4398-9ccb-11aac43f6ef2_118306949", "c40b5c1c-6e7a-45f6-a314-adcf276acb8c_663217418", "c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220", "14088fa6-23b4-4d55-b96b-803f49740287_341799643", "18936b99-e516-4cca-b846-d29e85b6c832_522368479", "c6691d00-dfb0-4b34-8d9d-a1453a0429a1_717856038", "e54d5d6e-0c6a-47f4-9834-81419f13a22e_14234603", "4c0ee3ad-3947-4c32-9bdc-e1ea45fa3dd9_966556193", "59a811e7-464f-49b1-91a4-205335ed2127_1064480777", "810dbd83-66fd-46d5-b733-7fd200ef200c_901656784", "ea2803e9-2428-4e1b-8a0a-9173914415c5_864708180"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1028", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The construction industry has traditionally been male-dominated, but there is a growing trend towards greater gender equality and diversity, with women increasingly taking on roles such as crane operators.", "citations": {"c40b5c1c-6e7a-45f6-a314-adcf276acb8c_663217418": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women make up 10.9 percent of construction industry employees, with their participation increasing from 8% in 2016.", "citations": {"b2e71ca1-f74f-41be-98bf-90b27f0ff99c_930292724": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UAE has launched initiatives such as \"Leaders in Difference\" to empower women in the maritime sector, prioritizing the recruitment of female talent.", "citations": {"446499ae-3270-4c22-a54c-07c275d9bfe4_1027392030": 1.0}}, {"text": "The International Maritime Organization (IMO) has launched the International Day for Women in Maritime to promote diversity and inclusivity in the industry.", "citations": {"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women can excel in construction, with average salaries for electricians and construction managers being $59,000 and $98,500 respectively in 2021.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0}}, {"text": "Governments and organizations are taking steps to support women in construction and maritime, such as providing scholarships, training programs, and mentorship opportunities.", "citations": {"3650242a-8a87-4c79-93c6-8a4315587753_706272734": 1.0, "8488df16-98af-409c-aa7b-5ea6bc01fe53_306144329": 0.5, "f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554": 0.25}}, {"text": "The construction industry lacks female role models, making it challenging for women to break into the field.", "citations": {"18936b99-e516-4cca-b846-d29e85b6c832_522368479": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women in construction can bring valuable skills like attention to detail, and companies are starting to recognize the benefits of a diverse workforce.", "citations": {"c6691d00-dfb0-4b34-8d9d-a1453a0429a1_717856038": 1.0}}, {"text": "The number of women in construction has remained stagnant since the 90s, but initiatives like MDOT's on-the-job training program aim to recruit more women to the industry.", "citations": {"e54d5d6e-0c6a-47f4-9834-81419f13a22e_14234603": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tradeswomen's organizations are leading efforts to increase inclusion and promote gender equality in the construction industry.", "citations": {"3650242a-8a87-4c79-93c6-8a4315587753_706272734": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UAE is a founder of the IMO Gender Equality Network and has contributed to IMO resolutions on women's empowerment, demonstrating its commitment to promoting gender equality in the maritime sector.", "citations": {"446499ae-3270-4c22-a54c-07c275d9bfe4_1027392030": 1.0}}, {"text": "Women's participation in the construction industry can be lucrative, with salaries higher than many non-degree jobs, and industry certifications can be completed in 16-week training programs.", "citations": {"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743": 1.0, "b2e71ca1-f74f-41be-98bf-90b27f0ff99c_930292724": 0.5}}, {"text": "Regular feedback mechanisms and peer support play a pivotal role in fostering an inclusive workplace in the maritime industry.", "citations": {"59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573": 1.0}}, {"text": "Embedding inclusion efforts at all levels ensures gender parity throughout an organization, and leadership support is crucial for successful diversity, equality, and inclusion practices.", "citations": {"59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Federal Bipartisan Infrastructure Bill supports women in construction, and Illinois is leading the way in creating pathways for women in infrastructure.", "citations": {"3650242a-8a87-4c79-93c6-8a4315587753_706272734": 1.0}}, {"text": "To attract and retain more women in the construction industry, companies can offer flexible work arrangements, provide comprehensive employee benefits, and create inclusive work environments.", "citations": {"07421f09-9a4b-4314-8467-583b9def15b8_772024418": 1.0}}, {"text": "Mentorship initiatives can also support women in technical positions, such as those in the construction and maritime industries.", "citations": {"59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573": 1.0}}, {"text": "The use of virtual reality simulators can provide safe and cost-efficient training for women in crane operation and other heavy machinery roles, enhancing their efficiency and productivity in the workplace.", "citations": {"024b7fd4-4ccc-4bbd-a8bc-0c9e1528e417_454160512": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the shift towards greater gender equality and diversity in the construction and maritime industries requires a multifaceted approach, including the implementation of flexible work arrangements, comprehensive employee benefits, and inclusive work environments.", "citations": {"07421f09-9a4b-4314-8467-583b9def15b8_772024418": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies can promote gender equality by providing training and development opportunities, such as those offered by the Women's International Shipping and Trading Association (WISTA).", "citations": {"575a1243-3c37-4fc9-9332-a8f5fdaf66ee_682674291": 1.0}}, {"text": "Governments and organizations can implement initiatives to support women in construction and maritime, such as scholarships, mentorship opportunities, and inclusive policies, to promote gender equality and empower women in these male-dominated industries.", "citations": {"3650242a-8a87-4c79-93c6-8a4315587753_706272734": 1.0}}, {"text": "The International Day for Women in Maritime, launched by the IMO, aims to promote gender equality and diversity in the maritime industry, and companies are increasingly including gender diversity targets in loan agreements.", "citations": {"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554": 1.0}}, {"text": "Technology, such as virtual reality simulators, can play a significant role in breaking down traditional gender barriers in the construction and maritime industries by providing women with the necessary skills and training to excel in these roles.", "citations": {"a373ec6e-26d7-4b1d-80f8-8c5162b1d109_678303594": 1.0}}], "references": ["024b7fd4-4ccc-4bbd-a8bc-0c9e1528e417_454160512", "c40b5c1c-6e7a-45f6-a314-adcf276acb8c_663217418", "c6691d00-dfb0-4b34-8d9d-a1453a0429a1_717856038", "3650242a-8a87-4c79-93c6-8a4315587753_706272734", "f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554", "59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573", "a373ec6e-26d7-4b1d-80f8-8c5162b1d109_678303594", "446499ae-3270-4c22-a54c-07c275d9bfe4_1027392030", "b2e71ca1-f74f-41be-98bf-90b27f0ff99c_930292724", "8488df16-98af-409c-aa7b-5ea6bc01fe53_306144329", "589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743", "575a1243-3c37-4fc9-9332-a8f5fdaf66ee_682674291", "07421f09-9a4b-4314-8467-583b9def15b8_772024418", "e54d5d6e-0c6a-47f4-9834-81419f13a22e_14234603", "18936b99-e516-4cca-b846-d29e85b6c832_522368479"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1029", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The science fiction genre has evolved over time, reflecting technological, social, and cultural changes.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0}}, {"text": "The genre has been influenced by historical events like World War I and the Great Depression.", "citations": {"3797de52-ec0d-46e9-9e4c-6ad6767e4843_700816127": 1.0}}, {"text": "Liu Cixin's bestselling novel \"Three Bodies\" won the Hugo Award for Best Novel in 2015.", "citations": {"1f7cf673-5fc9-4e0a-a5e9-5e2e25960e13_103800701": 1.0}}, {"text": "Liu Cixin's work has brought Chinese science fiction to a global audience, with \"Three Bodies\" selling nearly 9 million copies worldwide.", "citations": {"1f7cf673-5fc9-4e0a-a5e9-5e2e25960e13_103800701": 1.0}}, {"text": "Digital platforms and social media have significantly impacted the science fiction genre, facilitating the discovery of new authors and creation of online communities.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "The internet has helped increase the number of women writing science fiction by removing barriers for non-male writers.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "The science fiction genre has become more diverse, with significant contributions from women and people of color.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "Octavia Butler and N.K. Jemisin have made significant contributions to the genre, exploring power, identity, and social justice.", "citations": {"37022fcf-1259-41ed-b209-7b8279a72f28_45304574": 1.0, "e0d0eaca-aa98-46fb-ab70-0f03363ebcea_816797857": 0.5}}, {"text": "The genre has evolved to include sub-genres like steampunk and solarpunk, and elements from fantasy and horror.", "citations": {"c716d913-ebbc-4399-9c94-8573f1c137ec_526932315": 1.0}}, {"text": "Speculative fiction has evolved into a universal mode of entertainment and a tool for social change and creating hope.", "citations": {"dc3c3b72-0d32-4b24-827d-e46b2f82f7cd_304953587": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diverse authors have enriched the science fiction genre with new perspectives and ideas.", "citations": {"b7e8f115-5e3f-4039-9e41-a3e57db6d05b_473763089": 1.0}}, {"text": "Chinese female writers are thriving in science fiction, with authors like Regina Kanyu Wang and others being recognized through Hugo nominations and published anthologies.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "Authors like Liu Cixin, Wang Jinkang, and R.F. Kuang are gaining international recognition with their works translated into multiple languages.", "citations": {"1f7cf673-5fc9-4e0a-a5e9-5e2e25960e13_103800701": 1.0, "ac3a1030-35ca-4592-9ac0-7de59165a212_979870341": 0.5, "baf82211-c881-4a74-842d-5e4115ccc0ee_322785834": 0.25}}, {"text": "Science fiction is evolving to include a more diverse range of voices, themes, and perspectives from authors of different demographics.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0, "ac3a1030-35ca-4592-9ac0-7de59165a212_979870341": 0.5, "c716d913-ebbc-4399-9c94-8573f1c137ec_526932315": 0.25}}], "references": ["37022fcf-1259-41ed-b209-7b8279a72f28_45304574", "c716d913-ebbc-4399-9c94-8573f1c137ec_526932315", "dc3c3b72-0d32-4b24-827d-e46b2f82f7cd_304953587", "ac3a1030-35ca-4592-9ac0-7de59165a212_979870341", "01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677", "40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979", "baf82211-c881-4a74-842d-5e4115ccc0ee_322785834", "e0d0eaca-aa98-46fb-ab70-0f03363ebcea_816797857", "3797de52-ec0d-46e9-9e4c-6ad6767e4843_700816127", "1f7cf673-5fc9-4e0a-a5e9-5e2e25960e13_103800701", "b7e8f115-5e3f-4039-9e41-a3e57db6d05b_473763089"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1030", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The science fiction genre has undergone significant changes and evolution over time.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0}}, {"text": "The genre has traditionally reflected societal issues like capitalism, communism, and racism, as well as threats including nuclear power and ecological crises.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0}}, {"text": "The genre has seen a surge in diversity and representation from women and authors of color in recent years.", "citations": {"783590cb-da21-40c7-8f9e-9f1bfd9f68f8_413609546": 1.0}}, {"text": "The internet has enabled women and queer writers to develop their skills, significantly increasing their presence in science fiction.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "Chinese science fiction has gained international recognition, led by authors like Liu Cixin and Wang Jinkang.", "citations": {"ac3a1030-35ca-4592-9ac0-7de59165a212_979870341": 1.0, "bd18bfb8-3df1-40fe-80d2-e6f7164cb150_587592202": 0.5}}, {"text": "The genre now explores modern themes like transhumanism, artificial intelligence, and environmental crises.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diverse voices have enriched the science fiction genre, offering new insights and ideas.", "citations": {"b189e16e-b1b0-4531-898b-22bc44ca457e_717111571": 1.0}}, {"text": "Incorporating diverse geographical and linguistic perspectives is crucial for a science fiction book club.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0}}, {"text": "The club can explore science fiction to identify problematic tools and highlight ideas that can inform political theory.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0}}, {"text": "Science fiction can reflect and comment on societal flaws by embracing diversity and inclusive storytelling.", "citations": {"8b4f4c1e-487c-4250-846e-31739ce65460_1048251213": 1.0}}, {"text": "The future of speculative fiction will be increasingly interdisciplinary, incorporating diverse perspectives to explore the human condition.", "citations": {"dc3c3b72-0d32-4b24-827d-e46b2f82f7cd_304953587": 1.0}}, {"text": "Fiction can be a tool for social change, providing hope and insight into reality's problems.", "citations": {"dc3c3b72-0d32-4b24-827d-e46b2f82f7cd_304953587": 1.0}}, {"text": "The science fiction genre has become more inclusive, with marginalized authors like women and people of color making an impact through publications like Solarpunk Magazine.", "citations": {"f9f01c81-b641-4eed-964a-eae67a9c4e15_783638320": 1.0}}, {"text": "Solarpunk depicts cooperative and sustainable communities, dismantling white supremacy and patriarchy.", "citations": {"f9f01c81-b641-4eed-964a-eae67a9c4e15_783638320": 1.0}}, {"text": "The development of science fiction in Africa has been marked by milestones exploring African identity, colonialism, and postcolonialism.", "citations": {"8af9ba95-6574-4065-ada4-641670dbe883_384792123": 1.0}}, {"text": "African science fiction trends include using digital technology for literary production, with events like the Lom\u00e9 International Book Fair supporting local writers.", "citations": {"66b4ac58-0205-4d47-94dd-c6a7af743d0b_962627276": 1.0}}, {"text": "African writers like Alexander Nderitu have turned to self-publishing to control their work.", "citations": {"1af10747-ef12-4039-ad52-ccd6a6df9876_995399609": 1.0}}, {"text": "African science fiction explores local issues, including human rights in east Africa, as in Chemutai Glasheen's work.", "citations": {"34d2d309-248b-4e94-9519-ced5dc29863b_317934455": 1.0}}, {"text": "African authors, like Nozuko Siyotula, are using science fiction to reclaim their power and push for nuance.", "citations": {"1fa05b58-9d99-404a-aed5-a106397f9169_162079505": 1.0}}, {"text": "The global science fiction community can better support African authors through initiatives like Netflix and UNESCO's \"African Folktales, Reimagined\" competition.", "citations": {"1af86f52-5ab8-4239-8202-f264c8702abf_961643466": 1.0}}, {"text": "The competition promotes original African stories, supporting young filmmakers with $25,000 and a $75,000 production grant for six winners.", "citations": {"1af86f52-5ab8-4239-8202-f264c8702abf_961643466": 1.0}}, {"text": "The science fiction genre has evolved over time, influenced by diverse perspectives from non-Western and marginalized communities.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0}}, {"text": "A science fiction book club can include works from non-Western authors and marginalized communities for more realistic representation.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diversity of perspectives is essential in science fiction, which can be analyzed through postcolonial and feminist studies.", "citations": {"01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677": 1.0}}, {"text": "The publishing industry, traditionally dominated by Western authors, is seeing a growing presence of women and people of color making an impact.", "citations": {"07b5e06c-3043-47d9-989e-9d635f58df04_74453374": 1.0}}, {"text": "Less than 2 percent of children's books feature Indigenous characters, but initiatives like HarperCollins' Heartdrum imprint aim to increase representation.", "citations": {"07b5e06c-3043-47d9-989e-9d635f58df04_74453374": 1.0}}, {"text": "The presence of Asian American women in science fiction is growing, with venues like Yu and Me Books centering their experiences and voices.", "citations": {"223254fc-e82d-4bf9-8353-4d81b3f306cb_685750108": 1.0}}, {"text": "Chinese women are thriving in science fiction and can be supported through book clubs.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "Female science fiction writers address women's issues, with four anthologies of Chinese fantasy novels by women published.", "citations": {"40905120-1cf6-49fc-a73d-e415e5ce057f_387896979": 1.0}}, {"text": "Book clubs can promote diversity and inclusion across all age groups, with local bookstores often providing a meeting space.", "citations": {"bb4200f9-e351-4a8d-b4e8-09ecab0eccbd_814792293": 1.0}}, {"text": "Book clubs promote diversity by reading books from Black and marginalized authors.", "citations": {"cd5dad01-bf79-45af-84bc-2410ee4ee409_777393523": 1.0}}, {"text": "The StoryGraph tracks diverse reading, and Black authors write various genres like sci-fi and fantasy.", "citations": {"cd5dad01-bf79-45af-84bc-2410ee4ee409_777393523": 1.0}}, {"text": "Book clubs can promote diversity by highlighting marginalized authors and diversifying children's books to reflect various racial backgrounds and cultures.", "citations": {"d2bcd8e9-da6c-448d-8690-40fc4e59cc5c_312782391": 1.0}}, {"text": "Book clubs can amplify marginalized voices and foster cultural understanding by reading diverse books.", "citations": {"d2bcd8e9-da6c-448d-8690-40fc4e59cc5c_312782391": 1.0}}, {"text": "Diverse perspectives are necessary for creating a hopeful vision of humanity's future.", "citations": {"dc3c3b72-0d32-4b24-827d-e46b2f82f7cd_304953587": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Speculative Fiction Project aims to represent diverse authors, including international ones, in future funded projects.", "citations": {"dc3c3b72-0d32-4b24-827d-e46b2f82f7cd_304953587": 1.0}}, {"text": "Book clubs can be radical, promote diverse discussions, and vary in composition and environment.", "citations": {"e18badeb-b5ca-441f-9ed9-631922a71714_123655344": 1.0}}, {"text": "University book clubs can have clear learning goals and be department-organized.", "citations": {"e18badeb-b5ca-441f-9ed9-631922a71714_123655344": 1.0}}, {"text": "Book clubs can discuss marginalized authors like Manuel Mu\u00f1oz, whose work is also