{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1032", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Africa has the highest return on investment in the world, with African countries having unprecedented competitive opportunities and huge investment opportunities for investors.", "citations": {"49df26a7-82a0-4dc1-bb11-c6e257cf429b_167847908": 1.0}}, {"text": "The continent has seen significant growth in foreign investment, with China's investment in Africa growing by 9.5% in 2020, reaching $2.96 billion.", "citations": {"04066339-a2c7-4229-9fce-5f8ea28c547a_1033323970": 1.0}}, {"text": "Non-financial direct investment from China was $2.66 billion in 2020, with investment in Africa's service sector increasing sharply in 2020.", "citations": {"04066339-a2c7-4229-9fce-5f8ea28c547a_1033323970": 1.0}}, {"text": "Investment in scientific research and technology more than doubled, and investment in transport and warehousing more than doubled in 2020, with Chinese investment in Africa expanding despite global economic decline.", "citations": {"04066339-a2c7-4229-9fce-5f8ea28c547a_1033323970": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Africa Investment Forum coordinated $32.8 billion investments, with the largest deal being $15.6 billion for the Lagos-Abidjan highway.", "citations": {"5bfeb426-e80d-45e0-9fc1-d9c7182c9abb_187276660": 1.0}}, {"text": "Projects addressed agriculture, education, energy, and healthcare, with a new medical city to be created in the Senegalese capital and a fund for health services for low-income populations in South Africa.", "citations": {"5bfeb426-e80d-45e0-9fc1-d9c7182c9abb_187276660": 1.0}}, {"text": "Two pharmaceutical manufacturing platforms were established in West Africa and Kenya, with investment flows helping to accelerate the African Continental Free Trade Area.", "citations": {"5bfeb426-e80d-45e0-9fc1-d9c7182c9abb_187276660": 1.0}}, {"text": "Egypt ranked first in North Africa in attracting foreign direct investment in 2020, with Egypt acquiring 15% of total investments in Africa in 2021.", "citations": {"77626304-23cc-441b-b824-e3da7700ee4a_182209447": 1.0}}, {"text": "Foreign direct investment in Egypt is expected to reach $16.5 billion in 2024-2025, with Egypt being the most important investment destination in Africa and the Arab world.", "citations": {"77626304-23cc-441b-b824-e3da7700ee4a_182209447": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sub-Saharan Africa needs $425 billion financing by 2030, with the Africa Investment Forum hosting 2021 Market Days in Abidjan to focus on agriculture and agro-processing investments.", "citations": {"811ebf51-2133-41e0-bba2-3fdae8ae6a70_757674700": 1.0}}, {"text": "Energy and climate investments are also prioritized, with health sector investments being highlighted at the forum and ICT and telecommunication investments being discussed.", "citations": {"811ebf51-2133-41e0-bba2-3fdae8ae6a70_757674700": 1.0}}, {"text": "Global FDI reached $1.65 trillion in 2021, surpassing pre-pandemic levels, with FDI increasing 77% in 2021 from the previous year.", "citations": {"8feb9eb1-7481-432d-a445-526ef149fd2e_365508457": 1.0}}, {"text": "FDI in the US jumped 114% from the previous year, and FDI in Europe increased by over 80% in 2021, with FDI inflows to developing countries increasing by 30% in 2021.", "citations": {"8feb9eb1-7481-432d-a445-526ef149fd2e_365508457": 1.0}}, {"text": "Africa received more foreign capital in 2021 than in the previous year, with infrastructure sector financing increasing by 53% in 2021.", "citations": {"8feb9eb1-7481-432d-a445-526ef149fd2e_365508457": 1.0}}, {"text": "China is Africa's largest trading partner for 15 years, with China-Africa trade reaching $282.1 billion in 2023 and China's direct investment in Africa exceeding $40 billion by 2022.", "citations": {"acdcfd54-0846-4776-960b-5245dbdb0a77_140675468": 1.0}}, {"text": "China imported African agricultural products increased by 130% in 2023, and new energy vehicle exports to Africa increased by 291% in 2023, with China-Africa investment cooperation growing steadily.", "citations": {"acdcfd54-0846-4776-960b-5245dbdb0a77_140675468": 1.0}}, {"text": "Egypt received $5.1 billion investments in 2021, and South Africa received $40.9 billion investments in 2021, with Mozambique receiving $5.1 billion investments in 2021.", "citations": {"ae292450-64e9-4526-be1f-0c7555974775_845790495": 1.0}}, {"text": "Nigeria accounted for 5.8% of FDI inflows to Africa in 2021, and Ethiopia accounted for 5.1% of FDI inflows to Africa in 2021, with Mauritius and South Africa recording the largest outflows in 2021.", "citations": {"ae292450-64e9-4526-be1f-0c7555974775_845790495": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UK and France led African investments with $65 and $60 billion, respectively, with Europeans being the largest investors in Africa.", "citations": {"da89937a-32d7-40db-beb3-46050cdb3c6d_927341125": 1.0}}, {"text": "FDI to North Africa was down 5% in 2021 to $9.3 billion, and Africa's FDI reached $83 billion in 2021, double the amount in 2020.", "citations": {"da89937a-32d7-40db-beb3-46050cdb3c6d_927341125": 1.0}}, {"text": "BII plans to invest $60 billion in Africa over five years, focusing on renewable power and digital infrastructure, with support for women-owned businesses in Africa.", "citations": {"e3d3bec1-19f0-4d60-a67f-c8cb4d639ade_764369635": 1.0}}, {"text": "The investment focus is on the private sector in Ethiopia, Kenya, Nigeria, and Egypt, with a $76 million contribution to the African Infrastructure Investment fund.", "citations": {"e3d3bec1-19f0-4d60-a67f-c8cb4d639ade_764369635": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Africa Investment Forum attracted $180 billion since its 2018 launch, with $3 billion committed to the Alliance for Special Agro-Industrial Processing Zones.", "citations": {"f1c02df9-944b-46b0-a272-00c962b5e792_788630913": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Islamic Development Bank committed $300 million to agro-industrial growth, and there were deals in agri-business, renewable energy, and healthcare sectors.", "citations": {"f1c02df9-944b-46b0-a272-00c962b5e792_788630913": 1.0}}, {"text": "Africa is considered a dynamic and promising market globally, with the Africa Investment Forum having over 60 country representatives attending and focusing on South-South partnerships and infrastructure financing.", "citations": {"f1c02df9-944b-46b0-a272-00c962b5e792_788630913": 1.0}}, {"text": "Major foreign companies such as Eni, Apache, and BP have invested significantly in Egypt, with a total investment of $12.6 billion.", "citations": {"144428a7-e284-44de-9df0-7d707b3a138d_463674264": 1.0}}, {"text": "Eni has invested $7.7 billion in Egypt, while Apache has invested $1.4 billion and BP has invested $3.5 billion.", "citations": {"144428a7-e284-44de-9df0-7d707b3a138d_463674264": 1.0}}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia has also made significant investments in Africa, with a planned investment of $41 billion until 2030, targeting 54 African countries.", "citations": {"1766a2f6-4c2b-4b44-a664-7f421a3c154c_896677360": 1.0}}, {"text": "The investments by Saudi Arabia are focused on development and humanitarian purposes, with $25 billion allocated to various African sectors.", "citations": {"1766a2f6-4c2b-4b44-a664-7f421a3c154c_896677360": 1.0}}, {"text": "China has also been a major investor in Africa, with $182.4 million invested in Rwanda in 2022, and a total of $357.7 million invested in Rwanda in 2021.", "citations": {"4c5a2c67-ac50-4aa2-ba34-6e4dc570c606_851181790": 1.0}}, {"text": "Chinese companies have built $155 billion worth of projects in sub-Saharan Africa, with a focus on infrastructure development.", "citations": {"4fab73d8-1228-4ec6-bb1c-034b79b4898d_1067303941": 1.0}}, {"text": "The China-Africa TEDA investment company has invested $5 billion in 8 projects in Egypt's Suez Canal zone, creating 7,000 job opportunities.", "citations": {"597ce22a-3355-4a23-a097-e5d2cf203c83_621803186": 1.0}}, {"text": "US companies such as Marriott International and General Electric are also investing in Africa, with a planned investment of $33 billion, focusing on construction, banking, and IT.", "citations": {"84ceb796-4153-4342-8ec2-f1ccf962ca23_314148496": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US \"Power Africa\" plan aims to double electricity coverage in sub-Saharan Africa, with $26 billion available for investment.", "citations": {"84ceb796-4153-4342-8ec2-f1ccf962ca23_314148496": 1.0}}, {"text": "The European Union has also announced plans to invest $150 billion in Africa's infrastructure, as part of its Global Gateway initiative.", "citations": {"940b83f7-af87-4242-9615-8597f9087952_786010691": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UK has been a significant investor in Africa, with British International Investment investing $60 billion in the continent, focusing on renewable power and digital infrastructure.", "citations": {"e3d3bec1-19f0-4d60-a67f-c8cb4d639ade_764369635": 1.0}}, {"text": "Other major investors in Africa include France and the Netherlands, with $54 billion invested in the continent.", "citations": {"b40e3169-b0e3-4e79-9135-979f85ff557e_660205898": 1.0}}, {"text": "African entities such as the Egyptian government and the Rwandan government have formed partnerships with foreign companies, such as Eni and China-Africa TEDA, to attract investments and promote economic development.", "citations": {"144428a7-e284-44de-9df0-7d707b3a138d_463674264": 1.0, "4c5a2c67-ac50-4aa2-ba34-6e4dc570c606_851181790": 0.5, "597ce22a-3355-4a23-a097-e5d2cf203c83_621803186": 0.25}}, {"text": "The energy and gas supply sector has been a major recipient of foreign investment, with projects worth $120 billion.", "citations": {"b40e3169-b0e3-4e79-9135-979f85ff557e_660205898": 1.0}}, {"text": "The investment trends in Africa are shifting towards renewable energy, with companies such as bp and Shell investing in LNG projects and solar energy.", "citations": {"ebe2c34c-5dcb-4421-a702-9bc0dd4f4ad9_741016251": 1.0}}, {"text": "Perenco has invested $50 million in a Batanga LPG plant in Gabon and is developing a $1 billion Cap Lopez LNG terminal in Gabon.", "citations": {"ebe2c34c-5dcb-4421-a702-9bc0dd4f4ad9_741016251": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tullow Oil anticipates commercial oil production in Kenya in 2028, while Chariot oil and gas has signed a gas commercialization agreement in Morocco.", "citations": {"ebe2c34c-5dcb-4421-a702-9bc0dd4f4ad9_741016251": 1.0}}, {"text": "CDC Group has invested $440 million in Egypt across 39 companies and plans to invest $700 million in Africa with DB World.", "citations": {"fe9b8031-91b0-459e-8952-4766250ddd0c_618966819": 1.0}}, {"text": "DP World and CDC have invested $1.7 billion in African logistics services, with investment locations including Sokhna in Egypt, Dakar in Senegal, and Berbera in Somalia.", "citations": {"fe9b8031-91b0-459e-8952-4766250ddd0c_618966819": 1.0}}, {"text": "Egypt is Africa's top investment destination, with the country acquiring 15% of Africa's total FDI in 2021.", "citations": {"77626304-23cc-441b-b824-e3da7700ee4a_182209447": 1.0}}, {"text": "Egypt had $5.122 billion FDI inflows in 2022, with clean energy and infrastructure being prominent sectors for FDI inflows.", "citations": {"a5d99f5d-5340-4171-8450-24720fdfb69e_898064754": 1.0}}, {"text": "The country aims to increase FDI to $11.7 billion in 2023, with Gulf countries investing heavily in Egypt's market.", "citations": {"a5d99f5d-5340-4171-8450-24720fdfb69e_898064754": 1.0}}, {"text": "South Africa received $40.889 billion FDI inflows in 2022, making it one of the top recipients of FDI in Africa.", "citations": {"a5d99f5d-5340-4171-8450-24720fdfb69e_898064754": 1.0}}, {"text": "Mozambique and Nigeria also received significant FDI inflows in 2022, with $5.102 billion and $4.844 billion, respectively.", "citations": {"a5d99f5d-5340-4171-8450-24720fdfb69e_898064754": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ethiopia received $4.259 billion FDI inflows in 2022, with the country's FDI inflows expected to continue growing in the coming years.", "citations": {"a5d99f5d-5340-4171-8450-24720fdfb69e_898064754": 1.0}}, {"text": "The majority of FDI in Africa went to clean energy projects in 2021, with energy and gas supply projects increasing to $120 billion.", "citations": {"b40e3169-b0e3-4e79-9135-979f85ff557e_660205898": 1.0}}, {"text": "Construction and extractive industries projects also saw significant investment, with project values rising to $24 billion and $21 billion, respectively.", "citations": {"b40e3169-b0e3-4e79-9135-979f85ff557e_660205898": 1.0}}, {"text": "European investors own the largest FDI in Africa, with the UK holding $65 billion in total FDI stock in Africa as of 2020.", "citations": {"fca095bf-c4eb-4350-8684-81821e77f7d1_424720639": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UK's FDI in Africa is mainly in oil, gas, mining, and financial services, with $2.1 billion invested in oil and gas deals in 2022.", "citations": {"fca095bf-c4eb-4350-8684-81821e77f7d1_424720639": 1.0}}, {"text": "Fintech revenues in Africa are expected to reach $30 billion by 2025, with seven of the 10 newly minted African unicorns in 2021 being fintechs.", "citations": {"fca095bf-c4eb-4350-8684-81821e77f7d1_424720639": 1.0}}, {"text": "British International Investment made a $150m investment in Kelix bio in 2020, and has committed to investing $60 billion in Africa over five years.", "citations": {"e3d3bec1-19f0-4d60-a67f-c8cb4d639ade_764369635": 1.0}}, {"text": "The investment focus is on renewable power and digital infrastructure, with support for women-owned businesses and a focus on key markets like Ethiopia, Kenya, Nigeria, and Egypt.", "citations": {"e3d3bec1-19f0-4d60-a67f-c8cb4d639ade_764369635": 1.0}}, {"text": "MultiChoice Africa Accelerator Programme has expanded to eight countries, providing funding for emerging businesses in the technology sector.", "citations": {"52c54090-5421-4a41-859b-4b3996b13198_6077143": 1.0}}, {"text": "The programme focuses on healthtech, agritech, fintech, edutech, and creative industries, and aims to support small business development in Africa.", "citations": {"52c54090-5421-4a41-859b-4b3996b13198_6077143": 1.0}}, {"text": "The African Development Bank backs small-business development as an economic strategy, and the MultiChoice Africa Accelerator offers virtual", "citations": {}}], "references": ["fe9b8031-91b0-459e-8952-4766250ddd0c_618966819", "e3d3bec1-19f0-4d60-a67f-c8cb4d639ade_764369635", "fca095bf-c4eb-4350-8684-81821e77f7d1_424720639", "49df26a7-82a0-4dc1-bb11-c6e257cf429b_167847908", "8feb9eb1-7481-432d-a445-526ef149fd2e_365508457", "ae292450-64e9-4526-be1f-0c7555974775_845790495", "04066339-a2c7-4229-9fce-5f8ea28c547a_1033323970", "5bfeb426-e80d-45e0-9fc1-d9c7182c9abb_187276660", "acdcfd54-0846-4776-960b-5245dbdb0a77_140675468", "f1c02df9-944b-46b0-a272-00c962b5e792_788630913", "940b83f7-af87-4242-9615-8597f9087952_786010691", "144428a7-e284-44de-9df0-7d707b3a138d_463674264", "da89937a-32d7-40db-beb3-46050cdb3c6d_927341125", "a5d99f5d-5340-4171-8450-24720fdfb69e_898064754", "b40e3169-b0e3-4e79-9135-979f85ff557e_660205898", "597ce22a-3355-4a23-a097-e5d2cf203c83_621803186", "77626304-23cc-441b-b824-e3da7700ee4a_182209447", "4c5a2c67-ac50-4aa2-ba34-6e4dc570c606_851181790", "52c54090-5421-4a41-859b-4b3996b13198_6077143", "811ebf51-2133-41e0-bba2-3fdae8ae6a70_757674700", "ebe2c34c-5dcb-4421-a702-9bc0dd4f4ad9_741016251", "1766a2f6-4c2b-4b44-a664-7f421a3c154c_896677360", "4fab73d8-1228-4ec6-bb1c-034b79b4898d_1067303941", "84ceb796-4153-4342-8ec2-f1ccf962ca23_314148496"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1033", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "A 4-day workweek improves employee well-being, work-life balance, and overall health.", "citations": {"2afb54f5-6e6f-4cd6-9856-49054d7f7c21_155420427": 1.0}}, {"text": "The 4-day workweek reduces employee turnover, with 71% experiencing less burnout and 39% less stress.", "citations": {"be60c53b-d14a-421c-ad03-003b08185e9b_1025688978": 1.0}}, {"text": "80% of companies find it easier to recruit talent with a 4-day workweek.", "citations": {"e482bd93-fd7e-446b-ba03-e2926e0a5753_758874821": 1.0}}, {"text": "The 4-day workweek has a positive environmental impact through reduced commuting and energy consumption.", "citations": {"cf1102b4-5f90-45b4-9f65-661cd09ce910_1018928369": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UK is leading the 4-day workweek trend with a 6-month trial involving 3,300 employees at 70 companies.", "citations": {"29ee155a-83fc-45c5-a784-cadcc5f8b8cc_70773650": 1.0}}, {"text": "Implementing a 4-day workweek requires careful consideration of technical and logistical factors.", "citations": {"fab3c828-582b-4ae0-bf95-7773cf884e4d_871877708": 1.0}}, {"text": "Clear rules and communication are essential for a successful 4-day workweek.", "citations": {"c93b6c62-4b4e-4dc5-9756-5d7414b60b8b_540351926": 1.0}}, {"text": "A 4-day workweek may reduce earning power, but provides around 50 extra days of personal time annually.", "citations": {"e482bd93-fd7e-446b-ba03-e2926e0a5753_758874821": 1.0}}, {"text": "Larger companies may struggle with a 4-day workweek due to logistical challenges, while smaller companies can adopt it more easily.", "citations": {"b645a0a9-35e6-4332-87bd-9e5c9151dca1_775014741": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies can maintain customer service levels with reduced hours, often with no negative impact.", "citations": {"1d2aca84-d690-4e12-a07d-f87ff7a3b4ee_206156476": 1.0}}, {"text": "A 4-day workweek can boost employee happiness and productivity, with companies like Bolt and Accu reporting increased efficiency.", "citations": {"5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256": 1.0}}, {"text": "A 4-day workweek trial with 2900 employees at 61 companies saw sharp drops in staff turnover and absenteeism, with most maintaining or increasing productivity.", "citations": {"95484a6c-3484-4ebc-bcd9-0b7ef7fd3d89_98102531": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies can adopt a 4-day workweek with 80% hours and 100% pay, with 91% continuing after a trial.", "citations": {"cf48d8ac-0386-40b7-9253-77191b543af4_295608395": 1.0}}, {"text": "A UK-wide switch to a four-day working week could lower CO2 emissions by over 20 percent.", "citations": {"e9e88feb-fe4c-4b14-9a0e-e6455c754862_420211157": 1.0}}, {"text": "Some companies, like Unilever, have successfully introduced four-day weeks with minimal disruption.", "citations": {"e9e88feb-fe4c-4b14-9a0e-e6455c754862_420211157": 1.0}}, {"text": "Technology facilitates this transition, with 77% of employees believing automation can save time and increase productivity.", "citations": {"057e6c7a-5624-460c-b4c9-7ca823a9b76f_791418612": 1.0}}, {"text": "A 4-day workweek's success depends on company culture, employee buy-in, and effective use of technology.", "citations": {"e482bd93-fd7e-446b-ba03-e2926e0a5753_758874821": 1.0}}, {"text": "Companies can improve satisfaction, increase productivity, and stay competitive by leveraging technology and flexible work arrangements.", "citations": {"e0bb4330-60f2-409e-b75a-aef598fd8d7c_450545180": 1.0}}], "references": ["e0bb4330-60f2-409e-b75a-aef598fd8d7c_450545180", "b645a0a9-35e6-4332-87bd-9e5c9151dca1_775014741", "1d2aca84-d690-4e12-a07d-f87ff7a3b4ee_206156476", "e482bd93-fd7e-446b-ba03-e2926e0a5753_758874821", "c93b6c62-4b4e-4dc5-9756-5d7414b60b8b_540351926", "2afb54f5-6e6f-4cd6-9856-49054d7f7c21_155420427", "5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256", "29ee155a-83fc-45c5-a784-cadcc5f8b8cc_70773650", "e9e88feb-fe4c-4b14-9a0e-e6455c754862_420211157", "057e6c7a-5624-460c-b4c9-7ca823a9b76f_791418612", "be60c53b-d14a-421c-ad03-003b08185e9b_1025688978", "cf48d8ac-0386-40b7-9253-77191b543af4_295608395", "cf1102b4-5f90-45b4-9f65-661cd09ce910_1018928369", "95484a6c-3484-4ebc-bcd9-0b7ef7fd3d89_98102531", "fab3c828-582b-4ae0-bf95-7773cf884e4d_871877708"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1034", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The global trend towards a 4-day workweek is gaining momentum, with 92% of companies deciding to continue the practice after implementing it, and 56 companies choosing to maintain it.", "citations": {"092b9b4a-fc14-4205-98eb-1c1872d911e0_256602758": 1.0}}, {"text": "A significant number of companies worldwide have participated in 4-day workweek experiments, with 60 companies taking part in one such experiment.", "citations": {"35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423": 1.0}}, {"text": "The results of these experiments have shown that productivity remains unaffected, with a 1.4% revenue increase, and employment rates increasing while absenteeism decreases.", "citations": {"35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423": 1.0}}, {"text": "Moreover, stress, burnout, and fatigue rates have fallen during the trial periods, with sleep problems and resignations decreasing sharply, and physical and mental health improving significantly.", "citations": {"35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423": 1.0}}, {"text": "A notable example is Microsoft's Japan trial, which showed higher productivity with a four-day week.", "citations": {"4c2db427-4932-4b7c-977a-dfac0181fffd_255105730": 1.0}}, {"text": "In the UK, 21% of businesses adopted a four-day workweek in 2021, and 65% of UK businesses have a four-day workweek for some staff, with four-day workweek increasing productivity by 64%.", "citations": {"4c2db427-4932-4b7c-977a-dfac0181fffd_255105730": 1.0}}, {"text": "Additionally, 78% of businesses report less-stressed workers with a four-day week, and 68% of businesses see hiring and retention benefits with a four-day week.", "citations": {"4c2db427-4932-4b7c-977a-dfac0181fffd_255105730": 1.0}}, {"text": "Majority of Indian employers favor a 4-day workweek to reduce stress, with 60% of employers believing it boosts morale and job satisfaction, and 100% of employees favoring the 4-day workweek model.", "citations": {"4caa1e09-fab5-4186-9a73-0e526d939de5_611648540": 1.0}}, {"text": "The benefits of a 4-day workweek also include improved work-life balance, with employees managing their personal and work lives better, and most employers thinking it reduces stress and anxiety levels.", "citations": {"4caa1e09-fab5-4186-9a73-0e526d939de5_611648540": 1.0}}, {"text": "Over 3300 workers at 70 companies are working a 4-day week with no loss of pay, with companies like Atom Bank seeing a 500% surge in job applications after introducing a 4-day week.", "citations": {"5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256": 1.0}}, {"text": "The implementation of a 4-day workweek has also led to improved productivity levels, with employees at Atom Bank reporting a 13% increase in people engagement, and days lost to sickness declining by 28%.", "citations": {"5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256": 1.0}}, {"text": "Four-day workweek boosts employee satisfaction and productivity, with reduced work hours decreasing stress and sleep problems, and shorter workweeks resulting in a 9% reduction in fatigue and a 67% drop in burnout.", "citations": {"941bb6a1-0562-49cf-b65d-40a1edf10f98_903436754": 1.0}}, {"text": "Moreover, employees experience a 40% increase in productivity with a four-day workweek, and reduced work hours improve life satisfaction and energy levels.", "citations": {"941bb6a1-0562-49cf-b65d-40a1edf10f98_903436754": 1.0}}, {"text": "A four-day workweek trial involving nearly 3,000 employees in the UK showed that staff turnover and absenteeism rates fell sharply after 6 months, with 18 companies permanently implementing the 4-day workweek.", "citations": {"95484a6c-3484-4ebc-bcd9-0b7ef7fd3d89_98102531": 1.0}}, {"text": "The trial also found that productivity maintained or increased, with 39% of employees reporting less stress at work, and nearly half of employees reporting improved mental health.", "citations": {"95484a6c-3484-4ebc-bcd9-0b7ef7fd3d89_98102531": 1.0}}, {"text": "Furthermore, 81% of workers say a 4-day week would increase productivity, with the four-day week reducing burnout and benefiting health and finances, and the majority of bosses rating the experience well with high productivity.", "citations": {"9e1be21b-78bd-4a02-99be-30592613efad_77733316": 1.0}}, {"text": "Most companies will not return to a five-day workweek due to the benefits of a four-day workweek, which include reduced employee turnover and burnout, and improved work-life balance for employees.", "citations": {"be60c53b-d14a-421c-ad03-003b08185e9b_1025688978": 1.0}}, {"text": "The extra day off has also been shown to improve employee well-being, with 71% of employees experiencing reduced burnout rates, and 39% of employees experiencing reduced stress levels.", "citations": {"be60c53b-d14a-421c-ad03-003b08185e9b_1025688978": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the global adoption trend towards a 4-day workweek is driven by its benefits to employee well-being and productivity, with companies and employees alike experiencing positive results from its implementation.", "citations": {"c81c5dee-23ff-495f-ab91-7887d6ee6c8b_554937375": 1.0}}, {"text": "The largest 4-day workweek trial, involving 70 UK companies and 3,300 employees, aims to improve the quality of life and competitiveness of businesses, and assess the impact on productivity and employee well-being.", "citations": {"cf1102b4-5f90-45b4-9f65-661cd09ce910_1018928369": 1.0}}, {"text": "The trial has shown promising results, with 91% of companies continuing the 4-day workweek after the trial, and revenue increasing by 35% during the trial periods.", "citations": {"cf48d8ac-0386-40b7-9253-77191b543af4_295608395": 1.0}}, {"text": "Employee wellbeing and health have also improved significantly, with stress and burnout rates decreasing among employees, and commuting time falling by half an hour per week.", "citations": {"cf48d8ac-0386-40b7-9253-77191b543af4_295608395": 1.0}}, {"text": "The 4-day workweek has been shown to improve workers' health, reduce fatigue and disease, and improve mental health, with most companies planning to continue the four-day workweek.", "citations": {"cb4ac5bc-bc25-4f66-82eb-2fb95df543dd_683572091": 1.0}}, {"text": "The trial with 2,900 employees tested the four-day workweek, with results showing that it does not lower profits, and companies seeing a positive impact on work.", "citations": {"cb4ac5bc-bc25-4f66-82eb-2fb95df543dd_683572091": 1.0}}, {"text": "The world's largest four-day workweek attempt was conducted, with 70 UK companies starting a four-day workweek trial with 3,300 employees, and a trial period of six months with 100% salary and 80% work time.", "citations": {"cf1102b4-5f90-45b4-9f65-661cd09ce910_1018928369": 1.0}}, {"text": "The trial aims to measure stress, burnout, and job satisfaction, with participating companies aiming for 100% output with 80% work time, and researchers analyzing energy use, travel, and health impacts.", "citations": {"cf1102b4-5f90-45b4-9f65-661cd09ce910_1018928369": 1.0}}, {"text": "A study found that 71% of employees reported lower burnout levels, with 39% experiencing less stress, and sick days decreasing by 65%.", "citations": {"e1e67c07-ed6a-4575-bfb6-23f7f40091cd_16756718": 1.0}}, {"text": "Employee resignations decreased by 57%, with company revenue remaining unchanged, and employees' mental and physical health improving.", "citations": {"e1e67c07-ed6a-4575-bfb6-23f7f40091cd_16756718": 1.0}}, {"text": "Anxiety and fatigue levels decreased among employees, with work-life balance improving.", "citations": {"e1e67c07-ed6a-4575-bfb6-23f7f40091cd_16756718": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UK introduced a 4-day workweek pilot program, which involved 3,300 employees from 70 companies, who maintained 100% wages with maximum productivity.", "citations": {"29ee155a-83fc-45c5-a784-cadcc5f8b8cc_70773650": 1.0}}, {"text": "The trial, which lasted 6 months, aimed to measure productivity and well-being, and the results showed that productivity increased with a 4-day workweek schedule.", "citations": {"29ee155a-83fc-45c5-a784-cadcc5f8b8cc_70773650": 1.0}}, {"text": "A similar experiment was conducted by Microsoft Japan, which saw a 40% increase in worker productivity, and the company also saved 20% on electricity and 50% on paper.", "citations": {"29ee155a-83fc-45c5-a784-cadcc5f8b8cc_70773650": 1.0}}, {"text": "Other companies from the banking and hotel sectors also participated in the 4-day workweek trial, and the organizers aimed to change the approach to the workweek post-pandemic.", "citations": {"29ee155a-83fc-45c5-a784-cadcc5f8b8cc_70773650": 1.0}}, {"text": "The 4-day workweek experiment was also tested by 60 companies, which involved 3,000 employees working one day less per week with the same salary, and the results showed that productivity was not affected by the lighter work weeks.", "citations": {"35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423": 1.0}}, {"text": "The trial also found that revenue increased by an average of 1.4% over the trial period, and employment increased, while absenteeism decreased.", "citations": {"35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall health and staff well-being improved, and stress, fatigue, and sleep problems decreased, with 9 out of 10 companies deciding to continue with the 4-day workweek.", "citations": {"35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423": 1.0}}, {"text": "In the UK, 21% of businesses adopted a four-day workweek in 2021, and 65% of respondents had a four-day workweek for some workers, which included reduced or compressed work hours.", "citations": {"4c2db427-4932-4b7c-977a-dfac0181fffd_255105730": 1.0}}, {"text": "The four-day workweek definition includes reduced or compressed work hours, and 78% of survey respondents reported less-stressed workers, while 68% saw benefits in terms of hiring and retention.", "citations": {"4c2db427-4932-4b7c-977a-dfac0181fffd_255105730": 1.0}}, {"text": "IT-focused firms are more likely to switch to a four-day week, but companies with diverse workforces may find a short workweek complicated, and 66% of respondents reported cost savings from a four-day workweek.", "citations": {"4c2db427-4932-4b7c-977a-dfac0181fffd_255105730": 1.0}}, {"text": "Meeting customer demands is a major challenge for a four-day workweek, but 64% of respondents reported improved productivity and quality output.", "citations": {"4c2db427-4932-4b7c-977a-dfac0181fffd_255105730": 1.0}}, {"text": "In another trial, 3300 workers at 70 companies worked a four-day week with no loss of pay, and Atom Bank saw a 500% surge in job applications after introducing a four-day week.", "citations": {"5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256": 1.0}}, {"text": "Productivity levels at Atom Bank improved across all 165 departmental metrics tracked, and Merthyr Valleys Homes adopted a 30-hour week with no loss of pay.", "citations": {"5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256": 1.0}}, {"text": "Marketing Signals staff worked 32 hours with no loss of pay on a four-day week, and Tyler Grange reported promising results with the same amount of work produced in 80% of the time.", "citations": {"5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256": 1.0}}, {"text": "Accu saw a 25% increase in headcount and 400% increase in job applications, and the company's productivity improved by 46% and order numbers increased by 15%.", "citations": {"5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256": 1.0}}, {"text": "Chilwell Products reduced staff hours by five hours with no impact on lead times, and City to Sea implemented a four-day week with no reduction in pay and saw increased staff motivation and wellbeing.", "citations": {"5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256": 1.0}}, {"text": "A 4-day workweek trial was also started by 70 UK companies, which involved 3,300 workers from various industries, including healthcare, and the trial aimed to assess the impact on productivity and quality.", "citations": {"740d02c7-245a-4405-a579-818efb5231e7_333774911": 1.0}}, {"text": "The workers earned the same salary with reduced hours, and researchers from Cambridge, Oxford, and Boston College were involved in the trial, which was expected to produce results in 2023.", "citations": {"740d02c7-245a-4405-a579-818efb5231e7_333774911": 1.0}}, {"text": "Similar efforts have been made in Iceland and New Zealand, where companies tested the 4-day workweek with positive results, including increased productivity and revenue.", "citations": {"95484a6c-3484-4ebc-bcd9-0b7ef7fd3d89_98102531": 1.0}}, {"text": "61 companies tested the 4-day workweek with 2900 employees, and 18 companies decided to permanently implement the 4-day workweek, which resulted in staff turnover and absenteeism rates falling sharply.", "citations": {"95484a6c-3484-4ebc-bcd9-0b7ef7fd3d89_98102531": 1.0}}, {"text": "Most employees maintained or increased productivity, and employees reported reduced work stress and improved health, with nearly half of employees reporting improved mental health.", "citations": {"95484a6c-3484-4ebc-bcd9-0b7ef7fd3d89_98102531": 1.0}}, {"text": "Productivity was flat or slightly higher with the 4-day workweek, and revenue increased by 47% with the implementation of the 4-day workweek.", "citations": {"95484a6c-3484-4ebc-bcd9-0b7ef7fd3d89_98102531": 1.0}}, {"text": "81% of workers said that a 4-day week would increase productivity, and healthcare workers are likely to benefit from a 4-day schedule, which can reduce burnout and improve benefits.", "citations": {"9e1be21b-78bd-4a02-99be-30592613efad_77733316": 1.0}}, {"text": "Burnout and productivity are tightly linked, and research confirms that four-day workweek experiments led to reduced burnout and benefits, with the majority of bosses rating the experience well with high productivity [8", "citations": {}}], "references": ["4caa1e09-fab5-4186-9a73-0e526d939de5_611648540", "941bb6a1-0562-49cf-b65d-40a1edf10f98_903436754", "35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423", "9e1be21b-78bd-4a02-99be-30592613efad_77733316", "092b9b4a-fc14-4205-98eb-1c1872d911e0_256602758", "5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256", "be60c53b-d14a-421c-ad03-003b08185e9b_1025688978", "c81c5dee-23ff-495f-ab91-7887d6ee6c8b_554937375", "e1e67c07-ed6a-4575-bfb6-23f7f40091cd_16756718", "29ee155a-83fc-45c5-a784-cadcc5f8b8cc_70773650", "4c2db427-4932-4b7c-977a-dfac0181fffd_255105730", "cf1102b4-5f90-45b4-9f65-661cd09ce910_1018928369", "cf48d8ac-0386-40b7-9253-77191b543af4_295608395", "740d02c7-245a-4405-a579-818efb5231e7_333774911", "95484a6c-3484-4ebc-bcd9-0b7ef7fd3d89_98102531", "cb4ac5bc-bc25-4f66-82eb-2fb95df543dd_683572091"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1035", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Biohacking, which optimizes health and well-being through lifestyle tweaks, has gained significant attention with 951 million TikTok views and is part of the growing $8.5 trillion global wellness economy.", "citations": {"dacc0541-6652-4db0-a304-fe00f95e3622_646492919": 1.0}}, {"text": "Biohackers use methods like nutrition, physical activity, and supplements to improve their health, with popular approaches including intermittent fasting, keto diet, and high supplement intake.", "citations": {"fa9e1059-0043-4662-b4ce-35da904e721c_680282951": 1.0}}, {"text": "Combining multiple biohacking methods can lead to risks like infection, toxicity, and dependence.", "citations": {"0b939999-07ca-44ec-9b4e-60ad2f459051_897859293": 1.0}}, {"text": "Approach biohacking with caution and consult medical professionals, as some methods can cause liver damage, kidney damage, and increased disease risk.", "citations": {"39613d42-3cd1-49c2-b4be-85e6c5ccc0ba_684590547": 1.0}}, {"text": "Biohacking methods often lack reliable scientific support and require more research to understand their long-term health effects.", "citations": {"6915d0bf-08ef-453d-9f0f-024a9553f6a1_6142879": 1.0}}, {"text": "Biohacking methods like intermittent fasting and keto diet may have health benefits, but also potential negative effects, including increased risk of heart disease and stroke.", "citations": {"2427cb34-45b4-40d5-be0f-22bacda20dee_16920964": 1.0}}, {"text": "Carefully evaluate the scientific evidence and consult medical professionals before adopting biohacking methods.", "citations": {"936c65fa-80e6-47ba-8442-e5e77a4826a5_411498914": 1.0}}, {"text": "Healthcare professionals guide biohacking decisions to ensure safe and effective practices.", "citations": {"c42332c2-1492-4fbd-978b-4b108988d734_238176982": 1.0}}, {"text": "Biohacking requires a critical and informed approach, considering both potential risks and benefits.", "citations": {"0f2ceda1-1145-419b-adad-243aa48471c2_868441574": 1.0}}, {"text": "Individuals can make informed biohacking decisions and achieve health goals by consulting medical professionals and evaluating scientific evidence.", "citations": {"c42332c2-1492-4fbd-978b-4b108988d734_238176982": 1.0}}, {"text": "Biohacking methods, like microchips and gene editing, must be used responsibly with proper oversight to mitigate environmental risks.", "citations": {"ef681eef-bf83-4d4d-9865-3593fd4e59b8_1070587499": 1.0}}], "references": ["0b939999-07ca-44ec-9b4e-60ad2f459051_897859293", "936c65fa-80e6-47ba-8442-e5e77a4826a5_411498914", "dacc0541-6652-4db0-a304-fe00f95e3622_646492919", "6915d0bf-08ef-453d-9f0f-024a9553f6a1_6142879", "39613d42-3cd1-49c2-b4be-85e6c5ccc0ba_684590547", "2427cb34-45b4-40d5-be0f-22bacda20dee_16920964", "c42332c2-1492-4fbd-978b-4b108988d734_238176982", "0f2ceda1-1145-419b-adad-243aa48471c2_868441574", "fa9e1059-0043-4662-b4ce-35da904e721c_680282951", "ef681eef-bf83-4d4d-9865-3593fd4e59b8_1070587499"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1036", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Biohacking is a lifestyle approach that involves making changes to one's diet, nutrition, and lifestyle to optimize health and well-being, and it can be practiced in various ways, including through the use of supplements, cold-water therapy, and intermittent fasting.", "citations": {"0f2ceda1-1145-419b-adad-243aa48471c2_868441574": 1.0}}, {"text": "The methods used in biohacking vary from person to person and can include dietary changes, such as following a gluten-free, dairy-free, or keto diet, as well as the use of supplements, such as vitamins and minerals.", "citations": {"7330daf3-723a-424d-a476-023fed1467cf_546361925": 1.0}}, {"text": "Some popular biohacking methods include intermittent fasting, which has been shown to improve health and life expectancy, and exercise, such as physical strength training, which is nonnegotiable for women's health and longevity.", "citations": {"5bd8b7be-d64b-4d33-a44f-bb2bf500412c_903971285": 1.0, "0f2ceda1-1145-419b-adad-243aa48471c2_868441574": 0.5}}, {"text": "However, biohacking can also be dangerous if not done properly, and taking high doses of supplements can cause liver damage and interact with medications, highlighting the need for medical supervision.", "citations": {"0b519769-c0fc-4af4-b59f-28e4611fcaf2_833441994": 1.0}}, {"text": "It is essential to consult a healthcare professional before starting any biohacking regimen, including intermittent fasting, extreme exercise, and high supplement intake, to minimize side effects and ensure safety.", "citations": {"be3573dd-c6ec-408f-b33a-3b892d10d334_798761864": 1.0}}, {"text": "Medical supervision is necessary to validate biohacking efforts and ensure safety, as it helps to prevent potential harm and identify potential health risks.", "citations": {"936c65fa-80e6-47ba-8442-e5e77a4826a5_411498914": 1.0}}, {"text": "The combination of intermittent fasting, extreme exercise, and high supplement intake may have potential long-term effects on physical and mental health, including increased risk of cardiovascular disease, kidney problems, and mood disorders.", "citations": {"bb36b6c5-4ac2-47a0-ac52-27467078081a_598315669": 1.0}}, {"text": "To mitigate the risks associated with biohacking practices, individuals should be aware of the potential health risks and interactions, and take steps to monitor their health and consult with medical professionals.", "citations": {"0b519769-c0fc-4af4-b59f-28e4611fcaf2_833441994": 1.0, "0b939999-07ca-44ec-9b4e-60ad2f459051_897859293": 0.5, "3f8076e7-f98e-4344-a27e-5660a24b7d3e_113707781": 0.25, "6f2f22a0-86a7-462b-87d5-c5344be0812e_5083589": 0.125, "7330daf3-723a-424d-a476-023fed1467cf_546361925": 0.0625, "974ce5df-76d8-494f-88bd-19a564ef34ae_387131773": 0.03125, "cc014a49-591f-47ad-a2b9-4f2fa3d42018_350727545": 0.015625, "d8897448-e658-4b70-ae6a-6ae6517cb0e2_264109322": 0.0078125, "e177190a-ce88-4764-8ccf-bdc0a99d92b3_667223029": 0.00390625, "ef8828ff-2a00-4f86-a538-28497980cec7_442130510": 0.001953125, "f40f6268-960d-4656-9582-9e425c3fa20e_687801580": 0.0009765625, "fa9e1059-0043-4662-b4ce-35da904e721c_680282951": 0.00048828125}}, {"text": "Biohacking can have unpleasant consequences if not done correctly, and a healthcare professional should be consulted before starting any new biohacking regimen.", "citations": {"fa9e1059-0043-4662-b4ce-35da904e721c_680282951": 1.0}}, {"text": "The effectiveness and safety of biohacking methods are not always supported by reliable scientific data from clinical research, and individuals should approach biohacking with caution and consult medical professionals before starting any new regimen.", "citations": {"114e6335-8854-4b6a-9e8e-2cb9a5939cfc_694147838": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ultimately, a comprehensive and personalized approach to biohacking, taking into account individual health needs, lifestyle, and goals, is essential for maximizing benefits and minimizing risks.", "citations": {"89aca9a5-d558-4bb8-9299-e2b4a97be004_449191620": 1.0}}, {"text": "Healthcare professionals play a crucial role in helping individuals make informed decisions about their health, and their guidance is essential in the implementation and monitoring of a biohacking regimen.", "citations": {"6538b2d7-6d79-434b-b636-9e72ddcde903_1070002272": 1.0}}, {"text": "Biohacking involves changing nutrition and lifestyle for better health, and methods vary per person, including diet and supplements.", "citations": {"7330daf3-723a-424d-a476-023fed1467cf_546361925": 1.0}}, {"text": "Popular biohacking methods include cold-water therapy for mental health, removing inflammatory foods to improve overall health, and using saunas and supplements to aid in the regimen.", "citations": {"7330daf3-723a-424d-a476-023fed1467cf_546361925": 1.0}}, {"text": "Collagen and protein supplements are also used to support biohacking routines, and MCT oil is a healthy form of saturated fat used in biohacking.", "citations": {"7330daf3-723a-424d-a476-023fed1467cf_546361925": 1.0}}, {"text": "Biohacking can help manage mental health and cravings, and small changes can improve mental health through biohacking.", "citations": {"7330daf3-723a-424d-a476-023fed1467cf_546361925": 1.0}}, {"text": "Individualized approaches are key to successful biohacking, and nutrition and sleep quality are essential pillars of biohacking.", "citations": {"73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384": 1.0}}, {"text": "Intermittent fasting is a biohacking strategy that should be done under medical supervision, and physical training must be intermittent with recovery periods.", "citations": {"73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384": 1.0}}, {"text": "Cognitive stimulation is also essential to counteract cognitive degeneration, and medical supervision is necessary for intermittent fasting.", "citations": {"73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384": 1.0}}, {"text": "Biohacking aims to improve life quality by lowering morbidity rate, and diagnosing aging involves tests like oxidative stress measurement.", "citations": {"73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tailor-made programs are created after checking individual health status, and medical professionals are necessary for safe implantations and biohacking practices.", "citations": {"caa85e37-6f84-4cdd-91ed-88f88ac63b80_793273344": 1.0}}, {"text": "Biohacking can involve inserting chips and devices under the skin, and medical supervision is crucial for safe biohacking practices.", "citations": {"caa85e37-6f84-4cdd-91ed-88f88ac63b80_793273344": 1.0}}, {"text": "Healthcare professionals should advise individuals to consult a doctor before taking dietary supplements for safety, as thoughtless supplement intake can harm health.", "citations": {"31c0c4d0-bc9c-4e41-8bda-6a8b62696abe_366873676": 1.0}}, {"text": "Dietary supplements should be taken under medical supervision, as vitamins and minerals may cause health damage without supervision.", "citations": {"4bf9b276-3203-4362-b9aa-910e9b35d93b_626869712": 1.0}}, {"text": "Medical supervision is necessary for supplement use, and heart-healthy diet is recommended over supplements.", "citations": {"4bf9b276-3203-4362-b9aa-910e9b35d93b_626869712": 1.0}}, {"text": "Supplements can lead to kidney failure and other health issues, and hormones and steroids can be deadly and cause cardiac arrest.", "citations": {"4bf9b276-3203-4362-b9aa-910e9b35d93b_626869712": 1.0}}, {"text": "Energy drinks can destroy kidneys and raise blood pressure, and supplements can cause electrical dysfunction and cardiac arrest.", "citations": {"4bf9b276-3203-4362-b9aa-910e9b35d93b_626869712": 1.0}}, {"text": "Personalized nutritional supplements are tailored to individual needs, and professionals provide more accurate supplements than public selections.", "citations": {"cad68b28-9613-4010-bbdb-3c946c035b06_616924221": 1.0}}, {"text": "Guidance from professionals is necessary for supplement use, and pharmacists or doctors should be consulted before use.", "citations": {"cad68b28-9613-4010-bbdb-3c946c035b06_616924221": 1.0}}, {"text": "Individual health conditions and lifestyle habits are considered when recommending supplements, and nutritional supplements improve nutrient utilization efficiency.", "citations": {"cad68b28-9613-4010-bbdb-3c946c035b06_616924221": 1.0}}, {"text": "Over-absorption of unwanted supplements is avoided with professional recommendations, and supplements are more effective with professional recommendations.", "citations": {"cad68b28-9613-4010-bbdb-3c946c035b06_616924221": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Health Ministry warns against using dietary supplements without doctor supervision, and some supplements are harmful to health without medical necessity.", "citations": {"ef8828ff-2a00-4f86-a538-28497980cec7_442130510": 1.0}}, {"text": "Dietary supplements should not be taken without physician evaluation, and structural hormones should not be used without consultation and medical necessity.", "citations": {"ef8828ff-2a00-4f86-a538-28497980cec7_442130510": 1.0}}, {"text": "Anabolic steroids can cause physical and psychological damage in men and women, and using structural hormones can increase aggression and lead to depression.", "citations": {"ef8828ff-2a00-4f86-a538-28497980cec7_442130510": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sharing injections can transmit diseases like AIDS and viral hepatitis, and acquiring hormones without prescription may contain cheated contents.", "citations": {"ef8828ff-2a00-4f86-a538-28497980cec7_442130510": 1.0}}, {"text": "Using supplements without medical supervision may be harmful, and dietary supplements require medical understanding to be effective.", "citations": {"f669aa68-3b7d-4fd6-b227-b8deb8a258c1_703241710": 1.0}}, {"text": "Artificial hormone supplements affect natural body hormones, and protein-based supplements aid muscle formation and recovery.", "citations": {"f669aa68-3b