{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1038", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The conversion of the Hagia Sophia into a mosque in 2020 by Turkish President Erdogan has sparked controversy and criticism due to its historical significance as both a Byzantine cathedral and an Ottoman mosque.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UNESCO Foundation has criticized the conversion for being done without consultation, highlighting the site's symbolic importance to Orthodox Christians worldwide.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "As a tour guide in Istanbul, it is essential to be aware of the controversy surrounding the Hagia Sophia's conversion and to provide a balanced perspective on the site's complex history and cultural significance.", "citations": {"4e093f28-baf3-4799-8558-76d16d051ada_992581879": 1.0}}, {"text": "To achieve this, tour guides can use strategies such as individual tours with small groups, which allow for better dialogue and question-asking, and providing recommendations and answering questions about the city.", "citations": {"4e093f28-baf3-4799-8558-76d16d051ada_992581879": 1.0}}, {"text": "Guides should be knowledgeable about the site's history and cultural significance, and inform tourists about dress codes and entrance fees for mosques.", "citations": {"4e093f28-baf3-4799-8558-76d16d051ada_992581879": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government has implemented measures to manage tourist access to the Hagia Sophia, including separate entrances for tourists and worshippers, and the use of earphones for tourist guidance.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tour guides can provide balanced perspectives on controversial historical topics, such as the conversion of the Hagia Sophia into a mosque, by presenting multiple viewpoints and acknowledging the different interpretations of the site's history.", "citations": {"6520a8e4-2d97-4c78-8f05-4f048241b9f6_105665812": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion of the Hagia Sophia into a mosque in 2020 was met with international criticism and controversy, with some countries and organizations criticizing the move as a political gesture by President Erdogan.", "citations": {"6520a8e4-2d97-4c78-8f05-4f048241b9f6_105665812": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Greek PM criticized the conversion of the Chora Church into a mosque, another UNESCO World Heritage site, as offending history.", "citations": {"6520a8e4-2d97-4c78-8f05-4f048241b9f6_105665812": 1.0}}, {"text": "To address tourist concerns and questions about the Hagia Sophia conversion, tour guides can use diplomatic responses such as \"We respect all visitors\" and \"Prayer is our priority\" to explain the rules and regulations in place.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "Guides can also emphasize the importance of Hagia Sophia as a world heritage site and use earphones to provide information to tourists without disrupting prayer.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The new rules in place aim to improve coexistence between visitors and worshippers, and separate entrances are now used for worshippers and tourists.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The entrance fee for foreign tourists will help fund the preservation of cultural assets, including the excavation and restoration of monuments like Hagia Sophia.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tour guides can say \"We welcome all visitors\" to promote inclusivity and respect for all visitors, regardless of their faith or background.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The controversy surrounding the Hagia Sophia's conversion has sparked international concern, with UNESCO expressing concerns about the site's preservation and the impact of the conversion on its cultural heritage.", "citations": {"d766c719-43c0-4423-80e6-89c1f9dc9d52_954300905": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government has implemented visitor management policies to regulate visitor density and ensure safety and quality, and is working to implement UNESCO recommendations for preservation.", "citations": {"f81149b2-9efa-411c-b8fa-ed1ba6062f6f_619383984": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hagia Sophia's conversion has been criticized by the Greek Orthodox Church and other Christian groups, who see it as a loss of a significant Christian site.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "The site's history and significance are complex, with Hagia Sophia having been a Byzantine cathedral, an Ottoman mosque, and a museum, before being converted back into a mosque in 2020.", "citations": {"3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion has also sparked concerns about safety, with fragments falling from the dome of Hagia Sophia in 2022, and restoration work urgently needed to preserve the site.", "citations": {"9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018": 1.0}}, {"text": "To provide a nuanced and informative perspective on the Hagia Sophia's history and cultural significance, tour guides should be aware of the site's complex history and cultural significance, and be able to communicate this information effectively to tourists.", "citations": {"4ac4ea70-f757-47f2-9a69-a9247cbec976_661002239": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministries have set standards for tourist guides to ensure accurate information, and guides must pass exams and have university qualifications to provide high-quality guidance.", "citations": {"4ac4ea70-f757-47f2-9a69-a9247cbec976_661002239": 1.0}}, {"text": "Tourist guides must master multiple languages to effectively communicate with tourists from different countries and backgrounds.", "citations": {"4ac4ea70-f757-47f2-9a69-a9247cbec976_661002239": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conservation work done on the Hagia Sophia, including the restoration of marble and wooden railings, and the preservation of Byzantine Period mosaics, is an important aspect of the site's history and cultural significance.", "citations": {"3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Hagia Sophia's history spans nearly four and a half centuries, and its significance extends beyond religion to culture, making it a unique and complex site to manage and interpret.", "citations": {"aca9fced-3a95-40a8-82a7-3da41f775387_904412472": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish authorities have implemented measures to preserve the cultural assets of the Hagia Sophia, including the use of entrance fees to fund conservation work.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The visitor management policy implemented at the Hagia Sophia aims to improve the quality and safety of the tourist experience, while also preserving the site's cultural and historical significance.", "citations": {"9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018": 1.0}}, {"text": "The regulation of density and the distribution of visitors along different routes can help to prevent catastrophic structural failure and preserve the site's integrity.", "citations": {"9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018": 1.0}}, {"text": "By being aware of the controversy and criticism surrounding the conversion of the Hagia Sophia into a mosque, tour guides can address tourist concerns and questions in a sensitive and respectful manner.", "citations": {"6520a8e4-2d97-4c78-8f05-4f048241b9f6_105665812": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UNESCO World Heritage Site designation of the Hagia Sophia highlights the importance of preserving the site's cultural and historical significance, and tour guides can emphasize this in their interactions with tourists.", "citations": {"36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the most effective strategies for tour guides to address tourist concerns and questions about the Hagia Sophia conversion involve providing accurate and respectful information, being sensitive to the cultural and historical context, and emphasizing the importance of preserving the site's cultural heritage.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}], "references": ["4ac4ea70-f757-47f2-9a69-a9247cbec976_661002239", "f81149b2-9efa-411c-b8fa-ed1ba6062f6f_619383984", "aca9fced-3a95-40a8-82a7-3da41f775387_904412472", "36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408", "d766c719-43c0-4423-80e6-89c1f9dc9d52_954300905", "4e093f28-baf3-4799-8558-76d16d051ada_992581879", "9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018", "3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190", "6520a8e4-2d97-4c78-8f05-4f048241b9f6_105665812", "97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692", "76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1039", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The 2020 reconversion of Hagia Sophia into a mosque by Turkish President Erdogan has sparked international criticism.", "citations": {"36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408": 1.0}}, {"text": "The decision has been criticized for prioritizing Islamic past over other cultural heritage by the Greek Orthodox Church, UNESCO, and other countries.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "A 2020 Turkish court decision overturning a 1934 ruling led to Hagia Sophia's recent conversion.", "citations": {"36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion of Hagia Sophia into a mosque reflects Erdogan's efforts to promote Islamic heritage and consolidate power.", "citations": {"36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408": 1.0}}, {"text": "The international community has expressed concern that the conversion undermines secularism and cultural heritage preservation.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "UNESCO has criticized the conversion of Hagia Sophia, affecting its World Heritage Site status.", "citations": {"6520a8e4-2d97-4c78-8f05-4f048241b9f6_105665812": 1.0}}, {"text": "Erdogan's conversion of Hagia Sophia is seen as a move to strengthen his support among conservatives and distract from economic problems.", "citations": {"dc7d1e14-9026-4142-8352-b56898791c5a_838665307": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion of Hagia Sophia raises concerns about its preservation and structural integrity.", "citations": {"9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Hagia Sophia conversion may significantly impact Turkey's international relationships, potentially leading to increased tensions and conflict.", "citations": {"d0d4acd7-74b5-467f-9c78-985c6a08a9e5_893345947": 1.0}}, {"text": "Hagia Sophia was a church for 916 years, a mosque from 1453 to 1934, and a museum for 86 years before being reconverted.", "citations": {"36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government claims the conversion will preserve the site, but critics see it as part of a broader Islamization trend eroding Turkey's secularism.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "Imposing entrance fees on foreign tourists at Hagia Sophia is seen as a revenue generator, but critics argue it undermines the site's cultural significance.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "Turkey's tourism revenues jumped 23% in the second quarter and 53.4% in 2022 to $46.28 billion after Hagia Sophia's reconversion.", "citations": {"408158c8-72b3-42cc-aff8-df968745952b_708575783": 1.0}}, {"text": "The entrance fee for foreign tourists will fund improvements to the visitor experience and cultural preservation.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}], "references": ["97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692", "d0d4acd7-74b5-467f-9c78-985c6a08a9e5_893345947", "6520a8e4-2d97-4c78-8f05-4f048241b9f6_105665812", "76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229", "a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274", "dc7d1e14-9026-4142-8352-b56898791c5a_838665307", "9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018", "36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408", "408158c8-72b3-42cc-aff8-df968745952b_708575783"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1040", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The controversy surrounding the reconversion of Hagia Sophia into a mosque in 2020 has sparked international criticism, with many viewing it as a politically motivated move by Turkish President Erdogan.", "citations": {"3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190": 1.0}}, {"text": "The decision to reconvert Hagia Sophia into a mosque has been seen as a step towards greater Turkey and a promotion of democracy, although this has been met with criticism from various quarters.", "citations": {"5f313598-c9ac-40a3-8bae-106d6564ae87_210914181": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Greek Orthodox Church has decried the conversion decision, citing the historical and cultural significance of the buildings as Byzantine constructions.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "The reconversion of Hagia Sophia has also led to the covering of mosaics of Jesus and Mary, as artwork of human figures is forbidden in Islamic places of prayer.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "UNESCO has criticized Turkey's decision to convert Hagia Sophia into a mosque, citing its status as a UNESCO World Heritage site.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government has claimed that the status of Hagia Sophia is an internal affair, despite international criticism.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "Pope Francis expressed grief over the conversion of Hagia Sophia, while the Patriarch warned of a negative reaction in the Orthodox world.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "The first prayer at Hagia Sophia after its reconversion was attended by 1000-1500 people, with frescoes and mosaics covered during the prayer.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "Erdogan's image has been moving away from Western partners, and his decision to reconvert Hagia Sophia has been seen as a move to strengthen his conservative support base.", "citations": {"d0d4acd7-74b5-467f-9c78-985c6a08a9e5_893345947": 1.0}}, {"text": "The American Council has demanded Christian worship in Hagia Sophia, highlighting the religious implications of the reconversion.", "citations": {"d0d4acd7-74b5-467f-9c78-985c6a08a9e5_893345947": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion of Hagia Sophia has also sparked controversy over its potential impact on relations between Turkey and other countries, including Greece.", "citations": {"d766c719-43c0-4423-80e6-89c1f9dc9d52_954300905": 1.0}}, {"text": "Greece has criticized Turkey's decision to convert the Khora church into a mosque, citing it as a personal insult.", "citations": {"d766c719-43c0-4423-80e6-89c1f9dc9d52_954300905": 1.0}}, {"text": "The UN has listed both Hagia Sophia and the Khora church as World Heritage Sites, highlighting their cultural and historical significance.", "citations": {"d766c719-43c0-4423-80e6-89c1f9dc9d52_954300905": 1.0}}, {"text": "Turkish authorities have introduced separate entrances for worshippers and tourists at Hagia Sophia, with earphones to be used for tourist guidance instead of tour guides.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The entrance fee for foreign tourists at Hagia Sophia has been reintroduced, with proceeds to be spent on cultural assets.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish court ruled that the 1934 decision to convert Hagia Sophia into a museum was illegal, paving the way for its reconversion into a mosque.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "The reconversion of Hagia Sophia into a mosque is seen as a way for Erdogan to consolidate his Islamist support base.", "citations": {"6520a8e4-2d97-4c78-8f05-4f048241b9f6_105665812": 1.0}}, {"text": "Erdogan's decision to convert Hagia Sophia into a mosque was possibly due to geopolitical power politics.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion of Hagia Sophia may have been used by Erdogan to revive his electoral popularity.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "Erdogan's government has been accused of using the conversion of churches to mosques to gain support amid economic downturn.", "citations": {"d766c719-43c0-4423-80e6-89c1f9dc9d52_954300905": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion of Hagia Sophia to a mosque has been criticized by Greece and the US, among others, for offending Istanbul's rich history as a crossroads of cultures.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "Erdogan's decision to convert Hagia Sophia into a mosque was praised by Muslims in Turkey, who see it as a way to reclaim the country's Ottoman heritage.", "citations": {"d766c719-43c0-4423-80e6-89c1f9dc9d52_954300905": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion of Hagia Sophia has been compared to the fall of Constantinople, with Erdogan seeking to emulate Sultan Mehmed II.", "citations": {"dc7d1e14-9026-4142-8352-b56898791c5a_838665307": 1.0}}, {"text": "Erdogan's goal is the Islamization of Turkey, and the conversion of Hagia Sophia is seen as a key part of this effort.", "citations": {"dc7d1e14-9026-4142-8352-b56898791c5a_838665307": 1.0}}, {"text": "The decision to convert Hagia Sophia into a mosque has been criticized for prioritizing Islamic past over other layers of the site's history.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "Erdogan's move has sparked concern from Russia, among other countries, and has been criticized by UNESCO for potentially damaging the site's cultural heritage.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Greek Orthodox Church has decried the conversion of Hagia Sophia as an ill-advised decision that undermines the site's status as a cultural and historical landmark.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "Erdogan has defended the conversion of Hagia Sophia, stating that it is a matter of internal affairs and that the site will remain open to all people.", "citations": {"9dd219f6-2d94-4cd6-a905-bbd3c87a161b_427727559": 1.0}}, {"text": "The conversion of Hagia Sophia has been seen as a way for Erdogan to distract from economic problems and consolidate his power.", "citations": {"dc7d1e14-9026-4142-8352-b56898791c5a_838665307": 1.0}}, {"text": "Erdogan's decision to convert Hagia Sophia into a mosque has been criticized for implying a hierarchy in religious tolerance.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government has taken several measures to manage and preserve Hagia Sophia since its reconversion to a mosque in 2020, including the introduction of an entrance fee for foreign tourists.", "citations": {"6f38cb1a-e23d-4640-b32d-e60c213671a8_857153029": 1.0}}, {"text": "The entrance fee, which was introduced on January 15, 2024, is set at \u20ac25 for foreign tourists, while Turkish citizens can enter for free.", "citations": {"3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government has also implemented a visitor management system to regulate the density of visitors and improve the quality and safety of visits.", "citations": {"edf15035-b2e4-4724-a579-fe44de7e5e79_558380586": 1.0}}, {"text": "Additionally, the government has installed security cameras and fire detection systems to ensure the safety of visitors and the preservation of the monument.", "citations": {"3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190": 1.0}}, {"text": "Conservation work has also been done on the marble coverings and railings, and headset guides with QR codes are available in 23 languages to provide visitors with information about the history and iconography of Hagia Sophia.", "citations": {"3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government has also restricted free admission to foreigners, with only Turkish citizens allowed to enter for free for worship purposes.", "citations": {"7c91a665-2672-4d9b-8eae-3ec3168be312_904357446": 1.0}}, {"text": "The introduction of the entrance fee is expected to generate revenue for the preservation of the monument, with the proceeds from the fees to be spent on cultural assets preservation.", "citations": {"97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government has also followed UNESCO's recommendations for the visitor management plan, which aims to balance tourism and preservation of the monument.", "citations": {"9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018": 1.0}}, {"text": "The restoration of Hagia Sophia is urgently needed to prevent collapse, with extensive restoration work underway in various sections of the monument.", "citations": {"9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government has also reopened the Ayasofya Fatih Madrassa as a religious school, which will serve as an education center for scholars and researchers.", "citations": {"aca9fced-3a95-40a8-82a7-3da41f775387_904412472": 1.0}}, {"text": "The madrassa is operated by Fatih Sultan Mehmet University and aims to preserve Turkey's rich history through reopenings.", "citations": {"aca9fced-3a95-40a8-82a7-3da41f775387_904412472": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government's decision to reconvert Hagia Sophia to a mosque has been criticized by international organizations, including UNESCO and the Pope, who have expressed concern over the conversion.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "The decision has also been criticized by countries such as Greece, the US, and Russia, who have argued that the conversion is a political move by Erdogan.", "citations": {"a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274": 1.0}}, {"text": "Despite the criticism, the Turkish government has maintained that the status of Hagia Sophia is an internal affair, and that the decision to reconvert it to a mosque is a step towards greater Turkey.", "citations": {"5f313598-c9ac-40a3-8bae-106d6564ae87_210914181": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Turkish government has also promised to preserve the historical and cultural significance of Hagia Sophia, with Erdogan stating that the monument will remain accessible to visitors.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, the covering of the mosaics of Jesus and Mary in Hagia Sophia has been seen as a prioritization of Islamic past over other layers of the monument's history.", "citations": {"76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the Turkish government's measures to manage and preserve Hagia Sophia since its reconversion to a mosque have been aimed at balancing tourism and preservation, while also addressing the concerns of local communities and international organizations.", "citations": {"f81149b2-9efa-411c-b8fa-ed1ba6062f6f_619383984": 1.0}}], "references": ["7c91a665-2672-4d9b-8eae-3ec3168be312_904357446", "aca9fced-3a95-40a8-82a7-3da41f775387_904412472", "a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274", "9dd219f6-2d94-4cd6-a905-bbd3c87a161b_427727559", "6f38cb1a-e23d-4640-b32d-e60c213671a8_857153029", "d766c719-43c0-4423-80e6-89c1f9dc9d52_954300905", "5f313598-c9ac-40a3-8bae-106d6564ae87_210914181", "d0d4acd7-74b5-467f-9c78-985c6a08a9e5_893345947", "6520a8e4-2d97-4c78-8f05-4f048241b9f6_105665812", "76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229", "edf15035-b2e4-4724-a579-fe44de7e5e79_558380586", "f81149b2-9efa-411c-b8fa-ed1ba6062f6f_619383984", "9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018", "97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692", "3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190", "dc7d1e14-9026-4142-8352-b56898791c5a_838665307"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1041", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The Indian herbal medicine market is projected to reach USD 371.45 billion by 2030, driven by increasing demand during the COVID-19 pandemic.", "citations": {"21cad66b-e3e9-4d51-bf12-0c7b485aee69_976945430": 1.0}}, {"text": "Indian herbal medicine has been found effective in treating diseases like COVID-19, diabetes, and cancer.", "citations": {"362c2c86-f85e-4fb2-a284-cd4f44e4aee0_498281295": 1.0}}, {"text": "Yoga and Ayurveda have been found to relieve anxiety and aid in recovery in COVID-19 patients, with personalized Ayurvedic treatment improving outcomes.", "citations": {"362c2c86-f85e-4fb2-a284-cd4f44e4aee0_498281295": 1.0}}, {"text": "Neem tree extract has anti-parasitic and antiviral properties, and has been shown to decrease COVID-19 virus replication and spread in animal models.", "citations": {"290cabe3-2353-4112-bf92-b9a0914e327b_142802437": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ayurveda, which often uses turmeric, can help maintain blood sugar levels in Type 2 diabetes patients.", "citations": {"57a4cab9-1b23-4ded-946b-11646bce1b5f_855891334": 1.0}}, {"text": "Cardamom has anti-inflammatory properties and is being researched for treating various health issues, including cancer and respiratory problems.", "citations": {"57ef30c9-1e84-4bf5-8e27-b1dab39904f6_389634030": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Indian government established the Ministry of Ayush to regulate and integrate Ayurveda, Siddha, and Unani into modern healthcare.", "citations": {"0a2d1ec2-1ee6-4f95-9d00-3b75d29dc6d0_100317677": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Ayush is developing healthcare services, aiming for 12,500 Ayush health centers by 2023-24.", "citations": {"2a71159d-8419-47be-a5f6-27e2d320f5da_156354955": 1.0}}, {"text": "The WHO has established a Global Centre for Traditional Medicine in India with a $250 million contribution from India.", "citations": {"cb9ef0c6-8b7e-40ec-a20a-a356d3083fe7_261399576": 1.0}}, {"text": "The centre will use AI and big data to study traditional medicine, aiming to promote global wellness.", "citations": {"cb9ef0c6-8b7e-40ec-a20a-a356d3083fe7_261399576": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ashwagandha has anti-inflammatory and anti-stress properties, but may interact with certain medications, requiring caution and medical supervision.", "citations": {"0f55ce69-818a-4827-b9db-4c9b0f8ed6fe_962129761": 1.0}}, {"text": "The use of Indian herbal medicine, such as Giloy, can pose risks including liver toxicity, with 43 reported cases of liver injury across 13 Indian hospitals.", "citations": {"0e728151-f68d-4e8a-ae91-60975a7dbe76_1044959366": 1.0}}, {"text": "Patients should consult their doctor before taking Indian herbal medicines, as they can interact with conventional medications and are not subject to the same FDA controls as drugs.", "citations": {"9fb80c3c-f222-4ccc-8733-92b73334f617_898008542": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Indian government has set new manufacturing standards for pharmaceutical companies to ensure product quality and safety.", "citations": {"b99309e2-51a7-4ee5-b674-179ebee00e82_123669396": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Ayush supports Ayurveda development, mandates good manufacturing practices, and requires annual product quality reviews.", "citations": {"f4dd4c26-7e8b-4710-8d63-63928820f4ee_818860206": 1.0}}, {"text": "Indian herbal medicine can be beneficial but may cause side effects, allergic reactions, and interact with other medications, requiring caution and medical supervision.", "citations": {"e482bd93-fd7e-446b-ba03-e2926e0a5753_419383171": 1.0}}], "references": ["cb9ef0c6-8b7e-40ec-a20a-a356d3083fe7_261399576", "0e728151-f68d-4e8a-ae91-60975a7dbe76_1044959366", "f4dd4c26-7e8b-4710-8d63-63928820f4ee_818860206", "362c2c86-f85e-4fb2-a284-cd4f44e4aee0_498281295", "e482bd93-fd7e-446b-ba03-e2926e0a5753_419383171", "57a4cab9-1b23-4ded-946b-11646bce1b5f_855891334", "21cad66b-e3e9-4d51-bf12-0c7b485aee69_976945430", "0a2d1ec2-1ee6-4f95-9d00-3b75d29dc6d0_100317677", "57ef30c9-1e84-4bf5-8e27-b1dab39904f6_389634030", "290cabe3-2353-4112-bf92-b9a0914e327b_142802437", "2a71159d-8419-47be-a5f6-27e2d320f5da_156354955", "0f55ce69-818a-4827-b9db-4c9b0f8ed6fe_962129761", "b99309e2-51a7-4ee5-b674-179ebee00e82_123669396", "9fb80c3c-f222-4ccc-8733-92b73334f617_898008542"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1042", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Ayurveda has been found effective in maintaining blood sugar levels in Type 2 diabetes patients with limited side effects.", "citations": {"57a4cab9-1b23-4ded-946b-11646bce1b5f_855891334": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ayurvedic remedies like turmeric are in demand for their potential to control blood sugar levels and limit drug harm.", "citations": {"57a4cab9-1b23-4ded-946b-11646bce1b5f_855891334": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Indian government has established the National Ayush Institutes to promote Ayurveda, Homoeopathy, and Unani.", "citations": {"7c35d59b-3417-4232-97ca-d685314ade3f_354844377": 1.0}}, {"text": "The World Health Organization has recognized India as a global leader in Ayurveda and established a centre there.", "citations": {"cb9ef0c6-8b7e-40ec-a20a-a356d3083fe7_261399576": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ashwagandha and other medicinal plants may reduce anxiety and stress.", "citations": {"ce13ec75-5d14-4993-a8f7-c31c1539b04b_1051680076": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ashwagandha is being studied for its potential to combat long Covid symptoms in a 2,000-person trial.", "citations": {"ce13ec75-5d14-4993-a8f7-c31c1539b04b_1051680076": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Ayush has supported research on Indian herbal medicines, including a study on 400 plants with potential anti-diabetic properties.", "citations": {"c7759200-92d0-49c0-b063-d504fc07f1ae_307926663": 1.0}}, {"text": "The study found 21 herbal plants with anti-hyperglycemic action and a formulation called BGR-34 that can manage diabetes.", "citations": {"c7759200-92d0-49c0-b063-d504fc07f1ae_307926663": 1.0}}, {"text": "The National Medicinal Plant Board has found that three medicinal plants in Uttarakhand can cure malaria when combined.", "citations": {"af4623f9-11e4-4872-acf1-82ab58601269_425789638": 1.0}}, {"text": "The WHO emphasizes the need for research on traditional medicine to ensure its safe and effective use.", "citations": {"8ab3ddad-35b5-48f8-a58e-56a49840ca41_799531423": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Indian government emphasizes outcome-based measurement and data-based evidence for traditional Indian medicine.", "citations": {"2a71159d-8419-47be-a5f6-27e2d320f5da_156354955": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Central Research Institute of Yoga & Naturopathy in Dibrugarh is working to standardize traditional knowledge with modern technology.", "citations": {"42883104-0bc6-428c-961b-f8057ba3a9ef_84142596": 1.0}}, {"text": "The WHO centre in India will provide a reliable evidence base and connect traditional medicine practitioners globally.", "citations": {"cb9ef0c6-8b7e-40ec-a20a-a356d3083fe7_261399576": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Indian government has allocated funds to develop Ayush health centers and hospitals offering traditional Indian medicine services.", "citations": {"2a71159d-8419-47be-a5f6-27e2d320f5da_156354955": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ayush system has a turnover of $18.1 billion and is recognized in 30 countries globally.", "citations": {"6256be34-ee15-4ca1-9168-912f0e0407db_364912179": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Ayush has signed an MoU with the Ministry of Tribal Affairs to preserve tribal cultural heritage.", "citations": {"6256be34-ee15-4ca1-9168-912f0e0407db_364912179": 1.0}}, {"text": "The WHO has established a World Centre for Traditional Medicine in India for research and development.", "citations": {"8ab3ddad-35b5-48f8-a58e-56a49840ca41_799531423": 1.0}}, {"text": "The centre will use AI and big data to standardize traditional medicine.", "citations": {"cb9ef0c6-8b7e-40ec-a20a-a356d3083fe7_261399576": 1.0}}, {"text": "Traditional Indian medicine shows promise in treating diseases like diabetes, anxiety, and arthritis, but more research is needed.", "citations": {"0f55ce69-818a-4827-b9db-4c9b0f8ed6fe_962129761": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Ayush has organized sensitization programs to mainstream Ayush treatments in health insurance schemes.", "citations": {"ce81a3b1-962d-402d-b926-4b9cbe19a4b2_260359267": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Ayush supports developing Module-2 to standardize Ayurvedic practices.", "citations": {"e2101fe3-e219-47c1-8300-449bef7dfe12_68754735": 1.0}}, {"text": "Regulatory agencies, healthcare professionals, and patients must ensure the safe use of Indian herbal medicines through greater regulation and standardization.", "citations": {"e740d601-b53e-4635-9992-3e8936b06287_572584438": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ayurvedic practice lacks standardization, leading to adverse events and a need for better regulation.", "citations": {"e740d601-b53e-4635-9992-3e8936b06287_572584438": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ayush sector can provide global leadership in holistic health through institutions like the Rashtriya Ayurveda Vidyapeeth and the National Institute of Homoeopathy.", "citations": {"893d3061-12ee-4931-8790-1e8534d669ff_34879333": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Ayush is promoting Ayurveda, with the Prime Minister inaugurating three National Ayush institutes.", "citations": {"7c35d59b-3417-4232-97ca-d685314ade3f_354844377": 1.0}}, {"text": "The 9th World Ayurveda Congress featured the Arogya Expo, showcasing Ayush institutes and research councils.", "citations": {"7c35d59b-3417-4232-97ca-d685314ade3f_354844377": 1.0}}, {"text": "The National Ayush Morbidity portal aids Ayurveda standards implementation, supported by the Ministry of Ayush.", "citations": {"e2101fe3-e219-47c1-8300-449bef7dfe12_68754735": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Indian government has integrated traditional medicine with modern medicine through the National Ayush Mission, operationalizing 12,500 health centers by 2023-24.", "citations": {"2a71159d-8419-47be-a5f6-27e2d320f5da_156354955": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Ayush has collaborated with the Ministry of Tribal Affairs to promote Ayurveda, recognized in 30 countries.", "citations": {"6256be34-ee15-4ca1-9168-912f0e0407db_364912179": 1.0}}, {"text": "Prajna Ayurveda herbs combine traditional Ayurvedic practice with modern science and are responsibly sourced and triple-tested in India.", "citations": {"2b3d1f11-a45e-4ea7-ae82-52bef644a2c4_103444846": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Central Research Institute of Yoga & Naturopathy in Dibrugarh aims to develop evidence-based protocols for non-communicable disease management by combining traditional knowledge and modern technology.", "citations": {"42883104-0bc6-428c-961b-f8057ba3a9ef_84142596": 1.0}}, {"text": "The institution provides inpatient services using Yoga, naturopathy, and therapies to manage diseases like obesity and diabetes.", "citations": {"42883104-0bc6-428c-961b-f8057ba3a9ef_84142596": 1.0}}, {"text": "The World Health Organization has a centre in India for traditional medicine to set research standards and connect global practitioners.", "citations": {"cb9ef0c6-8b7e-40ec-a20a-a356d3083fe7_261399576": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ashwagandha, an Indian herb, reduces anxiety and stress, and is being studied for alleviating long Covid fatigue.", "citations": {"ce13ec75-5d14-4993-a8f7-c31c1539b04b_1051680076": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Ayush has funded a study on Ashwagandha involving 2000 UK participants to monitor self-reported quality of life.", "citations": {"ce13ec75-5d14-4993-a8f7-c31c1539b04b_1051680076": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ayurveda, which includes herbs like turmeric, is used to treat diabetes with limited side effects by controlling blood sugar.", "citations": {"57a4cab9-1b23-4ded-946b-11646bce1b5f_855891334": 1.0}}, {"text": "A pilot project on Ayurveda treatment for diabetes, including lifestyle modification and detoxifying therapies, has been suggested.", "citations": {"57a4cab9-1b23-4ded-946b-11646bce1b5f_855891334": 1.0}}, {"text": "IIT Delhi's research found that Yoga and Ayurveda relieved anxiety in high-risk COVID-19 patients.", "citations": {"362c2c86-f85e-4fb2-a284-cd4f44e4aee0_498281295": 1.0}}, {"text": "Thirty high-risk COVID-19 patients were successfully treated with personalized Yoga and Ayurveda programs.", "citations": {"362c2c86-f85e-4fb2-a284-cd4f44e4aee0_498281295": 1.0}}, {"text": "Daily yoga sessions and lifestyle modifications accelerated recovery by reducing anxiety, with over half of symptomatic patients improving within 5 days.", "citations": {"362c2c86-f85e-4fb2-a284-cd4f44e4aee0_498281295": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Ayush has organized a sensitization programme and set standard treatment guidelines to promote Ayush insurance coverage.", "citations": {"ce81a3b1-962d-402d-b926-4b9cbe19a4b2_260359267": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ayurveda system seeks WHO's ICD-11 inclusion with Ministry of Ayush support.", "citations": {"e2101fe3-e219-47c1-8300-449bef7dfe12_68754735": 1.0}}, {"text": "The inclusion of Ayurveda in ICD-11 will aid in regulating and researching traditional medicine and reporting adverse events.", "citations": {"e2101fe3-e219-47c1-8300-449bef7dfe12_68754735": 1.0}}, {"text": "The WHO has recognized a platform to register traditional medicine clinical trials.", "citations": {"a4bf79fa-f5fc-4f0b-a1a6-e4d980d2a91e_764153263": 1.0}}, {"text": "The platform enhances transparency in clinical trial design and aims to set a registration standard.", "citations": {"a4bf79fa-f5fc-4f0b-a1a6-e4d980d2a91e_764153263": 1.0}}, {"text": "High-quality evidence is needed for traditional medicine development, which the platform helps improve.", "citations": {"a4bf79fa-f5fc-4f0b-a1a6-e4d980d2a91e_764153263": 1.0}}, {"text": "The FDA has approved clinical trials for Chinese herbal-based drugs that follow US FDA requirements.", "citations": {"a7e604e9-ad9e-44a1-b1f7-8b39b20551d2_1043175994": 1.0}}, {"text": "Clinical trials for Indian herbal medicines can use randomized double-blind placebo controls to provide robust evidence.", "citations": {"a7e604e9-ad9e-44a1-b1f7-8b39b20551d2_1043175994": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Centre has documented over 1,400 medicinal plants in a pilot project across Uttarakhand's tribal communities.", "citations": {"af4623f9-11e4-4872-acf1-82ab58601269_425789638": 1.0}}, {"text": "The National Medicinal Plant Board reports over 1,500 plants in Uttarakhand, with 900 found in just three districts.", "citations": {"af4623f9-11e4-4872-acf1-82ab58601269_425789638": 1.0}}, {"text": "Chemical analysis of plants is being carried out using HPLC machines with necessary permissions from the biodiversity board.", "citations": {"af4623f9-11e4-4872-acf1-82ab58601269_425789638": 1.0}}, {"text": "The AYUSH ministry has been urged to document and put plant details online.", "citations": {"af4623f9-11e4-4872-acf1-82ab58601269_425789638": 1.0}}, {"text": "Research has found that 400 medicinal plants and 21 herbal plants have anti-diabetic properties.", "citations": {"c7759200-92d0-49c0-b063-d504fc07f1ae_307926663": 1.0}}, {"text": "BGR-34 is a herbal formulation that manages diabetes using compounds from four medicinal herbs.", "citations": {"c7759200-92d0-49c0-b063-d504fc07f1ae_307926663": 1.0}}, {"text": "Studies have been done on 21 herbs for diabetes, but further trials are needed.", "citations": {"c7759200-92d0-49c0-b063-d504fc07f1ae_307926663": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ashwagandha reduces anxiety, stress, and fatigue, and improves muscle strength.", "citations": {"ce13ec75-5d14-4993-a8f7-c31c1539b04b_1051680076": 1.0}}, {"text": "A double-blind clinical trial for Ashwagandha involved 2000 participants.", "citations": {"ce13ec75-5d14-4993-a8f7-c31c1539b04b_1051680076": 1.0}}, {"text": "The study included monthly follow-ups and is expected to last over a year.", "citations": {"ce13ec75-5d14-4993-a8f7-c31c1539b04b_1051680076": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Ministry of Ayush and WHO supported the research project.", "citations": {"ce13ec75-5d14-4993-a8f7-c31c1539b04b_1051680076": 1.0}}, {"text": "The WHO has a $250 million center in India to explore traditional medicine.", "citations": {"cb9ef0c6-8b7e-40ec-a20a-a356d3083fe7_261399576": 1.0}}, {"text": "The center aims to set standards for traditional medicine and integrate it into health systems.", "citations": {"cb9ef0c6-8b7e-40ec-a20a-a356d3083fe7_261399576": 1.0}}, {"text": "The WHO will use AI, big data, and evidence-based traditional medicine for research.", "citations": {"cb9ef0c6-8b7e-40ec-a20a-a356d3083fe7_261399576": 1.0}}, {"text": "India seeks Ayurveda's inclusion in the WHO's ICD-11 list.", "citations": {"e2101fe3-e219-47c1-8300-449bef7dfe12_68754735": 1.0}}, {"text": "ICD.", "citations": {}}], "references": ["e2101fe3-e219-47c1-8300-449bef7dfe12_68754735", "cb9ef0c6-8b7e-40ec-a20a-a356d3083fe7_261399576", "af4623f9-11e4-4872-acf1-82ab58601269_425789638", "2b3d1f11-a45e-4ea7-ae82-52bef644a2c4_103444846", "8ab3ddad-35b5-48f8-a58e-56a49840ca41_799531423", "6256be34-ee15-4ca1-9168-912f0e0407db_364912179", "e740d601-b53e-4635-9992-3e8936b06287_572584438", "a4bf79fa-f5fc-4f0b-a1a6-e4d980d2a91e_764153263", "ce81a3b1-962d-402d-b926-4b9cbe19a4b2_260359267", "7c35d59b-3417-4232-97ca-d685314ade3f_354844377", "893d3061-12ee-4931-8790-1e8534d669ff_34879333", "a7e604e9-ad9e-44a1-b1f7-8b39b20551d2_1043175994", "57a4cab9-1b23-4ded-946b-11646bce1b5f_855891334", "ce13ec75-5d14-4993-a8f7-c31c1539b04b_1051680076", "42883104-0bc6-428c-961b-f8057ba3a9ef_84142596", "2a71159d-8419-47be-a5f6-27e2d320f5da_156354955", "c7759200-92d0-49c0-b063-d504fc07f1ae_307926663", "0f55ce69-818a-4827-b9db-4c9b0f8ed6fe_962129761", "362c2c86-f85e-4fb2-a284-cd4f44e4aee0_498281295"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1047", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Ocean acidification harms marine life, including cephalopods like cuttlefish, by decreasing water pH levels, making it harder for them to build and maintain their shells and skeletons.", "citations": {"54053584-4dc9-40d0-bbea-8b47295e1d6f_116363246": 1.0}}, {"text": "The decrease in pH levels is caused by excess carbon dioxide reacting with water to form carbonic acid, reducing calcium carbonate availability.", "citations": {"0f12f37d-8df3-4e5d-90c5-d3860ba8d4a2_872534487": 1.0}}, {"text": "Cephalopods, including cuttlefish, are vulnerable to ocean acidification due to their calcium carbonate shells and skeletons.", "citations": {"54053584-4dc9-40d0-bbea-8b47295e1d6f_116363246": 1.0}}, {"text": "Pteropods are showing signs of stress due to ocean acidification, with reduced shell growth and increased mortality.", "citations": {"54053584-4dc9-40d0-bbea-8b47295e1d6f_116363246": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ocean acidification can have cascading effects on the food web, as pteropods are a key food source for many marine species.", "citations": {"54053584-4dc9-40d0-bbea-8b47295e1d6f_116363246": 1.0}}, {"text": "Some fish can rapidly evolve to cope with ocean acidification, but it's unclear if cuttlefish can adapt similarly.", "citations": {"5eaf29bc-9eb3-4678-b6d5-6b31ef609367_520746131": 1.0}}, {"text": "Seagrass meadows and kelp cultivation may help mitigate ocean acidification's effects on some marine species, including possibly cuttlefish.", "citations": {"72c97bcc-1d0e-4811-af80-28bb8339387c_827939974": 1.0, "af4623f9-11e4-4872-acf1-82ab58601269_463596060": 0.5}}, {"text": "Ocean warming can significantly impact marine life, affecting distribution, behavior, and physiology.", "citations": {"38bc0ca9-7189-4e60-9649-6082d34b1be5_19527343": 1.0}}, {"text": "Cuttlefish, as sentient cephalopods, are likely affected by ocean acidification, though the effects are not well-documented.", "citations": {"83f366c3-ad07-470e-87d6-8aafe6a9483a_671588004": 1.0}}, {"text": "More research is needed to understand ocean acidification's impact on cuttlefish and develop effective monitoring strategies.", "citations": {"574849e9-6f52-48ce-9c63-44f3d756ba1c_158383503": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ocean acidification can have long-term consequences for marine ecosystems, affecting cuttlefish populations, food webs, and biodiversity.", "citations": {"e35a74c7-1c1d-4f5d-b2ec-ccc9befc043b_968649048": 1.0}}, {"text": "Reducing greenhouse gas emissions is crucial for preserving marine biodiversity and protecting cuttlefish populations.", "citations": {"b0993337-fb9a-43cb-a8fe-1ded47b0a813_76101291": 1.0}}, {"text": "International cooperation and research are necessary to address ocean acidification's impacts on marine life, including cuttlefish.", "citations": {"574849e9-6f52-48ce-9c63-44f3d756ba1c_158383503": 1.0}}, {"text": "Place-based and integrated SDG actions can help protect cuttlefish and mitigate ocean acidification.", "citations": {"05d3d6bf-6d65-4dbe-b48e-f5a4bbf5218b_773785891": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ocean acidification is a complex issue affecting marine life, including cuttlefish.", "citations": {"543522d0-710a-4343-9604-7d30ec68fc40_108583209": 1.0}}], "references": ["574849e9-6f52-48ce-9c63-44f3d756ba1c_158383503", "83f366c3-ad07-470e-87d6-8aafe6a9483a_671588004", "543522d0-710a-4343-9604-7d30ec68fc40_108583209", "af4623f9-11e4-4872-acf1-82ab58601269_463596060", "b0993337-fb9a-43cb-a8fe-1ded47b0a813_76101291", "05d3d6bf-6d65-4dbe-b48e-f5a4bbf5218b_773785891", "e35a74c7-1c1d-4f5d-b2ec-ccc9befc043b_968649048", "0f12f37d-8df3-4e5d-90c5-d3860ba8d4a2_872534487", "72c97bcc-1d0e-4811-af80-28bb8339387c_827939974", "5eaf29bc-9eb3-4678-b6d5-6b31ef609367_520746131", "38bc0ca9-7189-4e60-9649-6082d34b1be5_19527343", "54053584-4dc9-40d0-bbea-8b47295e1d6f_116363246"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1048", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Ocean acidification is a pressing issue that affects marine life, particularly those with calcium carbonate shells and skeletons, such as clams, bivalves, and potentially cephalopods.", "citations": {"0f12f37d-8df3-4e5d-90c5-d3860ba8d4a2_872534487": 1.0}}, {"text": "The increase in atmospheric carbon dioxide leads to a decrease in pH levels, making it difficult for these organisms to build and maintain their shells.", "citations": {"0f12f37d-8df3-4e5d-90c5-d3860ba8d4a2_872534487": 1.0}}, {"text": "While there is limited information available on the specific effects of ocean acidification on cephalopods, it is likely that they will be impacted by changes in the food web and ecosystem processes.", "citations": {"0f12f37d-8df3-4e5d-90c5-d3860ba8d4a2_872534487": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ocean acidification can affect fish at an energetic cost, and fish are more sensitive to warming than acidification, which can have indirect effects on cephalopod populations.", "citations": {"38bc0ca9-7189-4e60-9649-6082d34b1be5_19527343": 1.0}}, {"text": "Temperature affects fish growth and behavior, and young fish are most sensitive to warming and acidification, which can impact the overall resilience of the ecosystem.", "citations": {"38bc0ca9-7189-4e60-9649-6082d34b1be5_19527343": 1.0}}, {"text": "Pteropods, which are an important food source for many marine species, including cephalopods, are vulnerable to ocean acidification, which can impact their shell building and survival.", "citations": {"54053584-4dc9-40d0-bbea-8b47295e1d6f_116363246": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ocean acidification can also affect the development and growth of sea urchin larvae, which can have cascading effects on the entire ecosystem.", "citations": {"72c97bcc-1d0e-4811-af80-28bb8339387c_827939974": 1.0}}, {"text": "Seagrass meadows can mitigate the negative effects of ocean acidification on calcifying species, including cephalopods, by increasing the pH and reducing the acidity of the seawater.", "citations": {"72c97bcc-1d0e-4811-af80-28bb8339387c_827939974": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, ocean acidification is predicted to worsen under the RCP8.5 scenario, which can have significant consequences for marine ecosystems and biodiversity.", "citations": {"72c97bcc-1d0e-4811-af80-28bb8339387c_827939974": 1.0}}, {"text": "Cephalopods, such as octopuses, are affected by ocean warming, which can cause blurred vision, reduced protein production, and accelerated metabolism.", "citations": {"f681d169-2708-462a-ba28-f689fa1fae4f_169019957": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ocean warming can also change octopus distribution areas, reduce reproduction, and decrease egg spawn numbers.", "citations": {"f681d169-2708-462a-ba28-f689fa1fae4f_169019957": 1.0}}, {"text": "The combined effects of ocean acidification and warming can increase the breathing rates of larvae and make them more sensitive to environmental stressors, which can have significant consequences for the resilience of the ecosystem.", "citations": {"e35a74c7-1c1d-4f5d-b2ec-ccc9befc043b_968649048": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, ocean acidification has the potential to impact cephalopod-dominated ecosystems in a variety of ways, including changes to the food web dynamics, species interactions, and ecosystem processes.", "citations": {"e35a74c7-1c1d-4f5d-b2ec-ccc9befc043b_968649048": 1.0}}, {"text": "It is essential to continue monitoring and studying the effects of ocean acidification on marine ecosystems, including those dominated by cephalopods, to better understand the potential consequences and develop effective mitigation strategies.", "citations": {"e35a74c7-1c1d-4f5d-b2ec-ccc9befc043b_968649048": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Arctic Ocean acidifies three to four times faster than other oceans, which can have severe consequences for cephalopod-dominated ecosystems in these regions.", "citations": {"0bea86b1-eadb-4c2a-8d48-e3bb5ef5780a_203442634": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ocean acidification may make some metals more toxic, which can further harm cephalopods and other marine life.", "citations": {"0bea86b1-eadb-4c2a-8d48-e3bb5ef5780a_203442634": 1.0}}, {"text": "Cephalopod-dominated ecosystems are vulnerable to changes in food web dynamics, as ocean acidification can disrupt zooplankton populations and affect the entire food chain.", "citations": {"e35a74c7-1c1d-4f5d-b2ec-ccc9befc043b_968649048": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ocean acidification can also impact ecosystem resilience, making it more challenging for cephalopod populations to recover from disturbances.", "citations": {"e35a74c7-1c1d-4f5d-b2ec-ccc9befc043b_968649048": 1.0}}, {"text": "Some species, such as pteropods, which are an essential food source for many cephalopods, are particularly vulnerable to ocean acidification, which can harm their shell-building abilities.", "citations": {"54053584-4dc9-40d0-bbea-8b47295e1d6f_116363246": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ocean acidification can also affect the growth and survival of shrimp larvae, which are an essential food source for many cephalopod species.", "citations": {"eabaa8bc-af88-4b73-a1b2-dec0f49336fd_390178312": 1.0}}, {"text": "Kelp deployment on oyster farms can protect bivalves from acidification, but more research is needed to understand how to mitigate the effects of ocean acidification on cephalopod-dominated ecosystems.", "citations": {"af4623f9-11e4-4872-acf1-82ab58601269_463596060": 1.0}}, {"text": "Ocean warming and acidification can have combined effects on marine ecosystems, including changes in species distribution, reproductive cycles, and food chain dynamics.", "citations": {"e35a74c7-1c1d-4f5d-b2ec-ccc9befc043b_968649048": 1.0}}, {"text": "Cephalopods, such as octopuses, may become smaller in warmer water temperatures, which can further exacerbate the impacts of ocean acidification.", "citations": {"f681d169-2708-462a-ba28-f689fa1fae4f_169019957": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, ocean acidification has far-reaching consequences for cephalopod-dominated ecosystems, including changes in food web dynamics and ecosystem resilience, which can have significant impacts on the entire marine ecosystem.", "citations": {"e35a74c7-1c1d-4f5d-b2ec-ccc9befc043b_968649048": 1.0}}], "references": ["54053584-4dc9-40d0-bbea-8b47295e1d6f_116363246", "eabaa8bc-af88-4b73-a1b2-dec0f49336fd_390178312", "f681d169-2708-462a-ba28-f689fa1fae4f_169019957", "0bea86b1-eadb-4c2a-8d48-e3bb5ef5780a_203442634", "72c97bcc-1d0e-4811-af80-28bb8339387c_827939974", "e35a74c7-1c1d-4f5d-b2ec-ccc9befc043b_968649048", "af4623f9-11e4-4872-acf1-82ab58601269_463596060", "38bc0ca9-7189-4e60-9649-6082d34b1be5_19527343", "0f12f37d-8df3-4e5d-90c5-d3860ba8d4a2_872534487"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1053", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The US has become the world's leader in avocado consumption between 2015 and 2024, driving significant global market growth.", "citations": {"8ca9c8e9-43b5-47a1-b8c7-47fcb66e4530_31759721": 1.0}}, {"text": "US avocado consumption rose from 3.2 pounds per capita in 2015 to 8.5 pounds in 2019, before declining in 2020 due to the coronavirus epidemic.", "citations": {"53ec3f8b-1f33-4db7-b460-fc0533d8e9db_308359623": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US avocado market more than doubled between 2015 and 2024, with most coming from Mexico.", "citations": {"8ca9c8e9-43b5-47a1-b8c7-47fcb66e4530_31759721": 1.0}}, {"text": "Mexico, the world's largest avocado producer, supplies 80% of US avocados, with $2.8 billion in exports in 2020.", "citations": {"3f2668d2-a695-4d4c-a2be-36032d9a07f4_87857532": 1.0}}, {"text": "The avocado industry faces environmental concerns including deforestation, water depletion, and climate change.", "citations": {"65e3998a-3ab7-4bb2-b022-ca181d90e86f_222072541": 1.0}}, {"text": "Avocado farming consumes around 1,000 liters of water per kilogram, causing water scarcity in countries like Mexico and Peru.", "citations": {"9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657": 1.0}}, {"text": "Avocado farming has a substantial environmental impact, consuming around 1,000 liters of water per kilogram and generating 5.4 kg of carbon dioxide emissions through transportation.", "citations": {"65e3998a-3ab7-4bb2-b022-ca181d90e86f_222072541": 1.0, "9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657": 0.5}}, {"text": "Sustainable avocado farming practices and government incentives can reduce water and chemical use.", "citations": {"9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657": 1.0}}, {"text": "Certifications like Fairtrade and Organic promote sustainable farming, improve farmers' lives, and provide better prices.", "citations": {"0e536ba6-0e5e-42c5-8b5c-cdd823f654ef_3282698": 1.0}}, {"text": "Regenerative Organic Certification promotes environmental protection, animal welfare, and fair trade, and can improve the sustainability of avocado farming.", "citations": {"2e6fcce7-0fbe-4f6b-8df5-b166f040da51_715289060": 1.0}}, {"text": "Supporting small-scale farmers promotes environmental sustainability and self-sufficient communities.", "citations": {"d81bd102-edab-45d8-9e07-7eabfd506ff6_213163074": 1.0}}, {"text": "Sustainable practices like drip irrigation and agroforestry can reduce environmental impact while improving crop yields and farmer incomes.", "citations": {"0184e3cb-6e36-4152-8a1f-80423b62d1f5_377748049": 1.0, "5f988bab-ef63-4c89-b675-2e70748aed01_216901935": 0.5, "2b456d4e-3743-41f2-b0db-2d72e9b13355_224901378": 0.25}}, {"text": "Digital tools can empower smallholder farmers to adopt sustainable practices, which is crucial for water-intensive crops like avocados.", "citations": {"b412ad1e-5559-4922-aeb4-efbc6f63bf67_812658867": 1.0, "e723799f-1810-462b-b84e-a0b5e5a4749d_1052218110": 0.5}}, {"text": "Avocado farming can negatively impact local communities by exploiting workers and limiting access to healthy food, making responsible supply chains essential.", "citations": {"9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657": 1.0, "e723799f-1810-462b-b84e-a0b5e5a4749d_1052218110": 0.5, "a22bbc80-d28a-493c-82f4-5b443da86c81_628665012": 0.25, "b412ad1e-5559-4922-aeb4-efbc6f63bf67_812658867": 0.125}}, {"text": "Partnerships like Al Dahra and Agrena show that sustainable farming practices can be implemented at scale, improving local livelihoods and reducing environmental impacts.", "citations": {"f23c779e-017f-4628-9a50-d04f7ac0add2_370094659": 1.0}}, {"text": "Preserving water catchment areas and using composting and mulching techniques are crucial for sustainable avocado farming.", "citations": {"08243776-6209-4f58-bf9b-6eba959ce05f_94533784": 1.0}}], "references": ["3f2668d2-a695-4d4c-a2be-36032d9a07f4_87857532", "53ec3f8b-1f33-4db7-b460-fc0533d8e9db_308359623", "9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657", "d81bd102-edab-45d8-9e07-7eabfd506ff6_213163074", "e723799f-1810-462b-b84e-a0b5e5a4749d_1052218110", "08243776-6209-4f58-bf9b-6eba959ce05f_94533784", "2e6fcce7-0fbe-4f6b-8df5-b166f040da51_715289060", "2b456d4e-3743-41f2-b0db-2d72e9b13355_224901378", "0e536ba6-0e5e-42c5-8b5c-cdd823f654ef_3282698", "5f988bab-ef63-4c89-b675-2e70748aed01_216901935", "8ca9c8e9-43b5-47a1-b8c7-47fcb66e4530_31759721", "b412ad1e-5559-4922-aeb4-efbc6f63bf67_812658867", "0184e3cb-6e36-4152-8a1f-80423b62d1f5_377748049", "f23c779e-017f-4628-9a50-d04f7ac0add2_370094659", "a22bbc80-d28a-493c-82f4-5b443da86c81_628665012", "65e3998a-3ab7-4bb2-b022-ca181d90e86f_222072541"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1054", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The global demand for avocados has increased significantly in recent years, with the US being the largest consumer of avocados, accounting for half of the global demand.", "citations": {"0647188f-9964-4a4f-ae8e-63483708d38d_55923929": 1.0}}, {"text": "The rising demand for avocados has led to an increase in avocado production, with Mexico being the largest producer of avocados, accounting for 80% of the avocados consumed in the US.", "citations": {"114d1622-c9c5-4614-b132-9c9189790987_442554566": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, the increasing demand for avocados has also raised concerns about the environmental and social impacts of avocado production, including deforestation, water depletion, and labor exploitation.", "citations": {"9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657": 1.0}}, {"text": "Avocado farming requires a significant amount of water, with approximately 1,000 liters of water needed to produce one kilogram of avocados, making it a water-intensive crop.", "citations": {"18665f57-7b47-4cae-9c9d-5fc30625182f_930516690": 1.0}}, {"text": "The water usage for avocado farming has led to a water crisis in countries such as Morocco, where avocado farming drains 10 billion liters of water annually.", "citations": {"2409aa08-ac99-4af7-9b03-00162ac09568_658036910": 1.0}}, {"text": "In addition to water depletion, avocado farming has also been linked to deforestation, with one tree being cut down every 75 seconds in Jalisco, Mexico, to make way for avocado gardens.", "citations": {"c4df1771-8297-4414-adac-d7cd6bb376e0_639626865": 1.0}}, {"text": "The high demand for avocados has also led to labor exploitation and food insecurity in Mexico, where the avocado mafia controls production and export.", "citations": {"9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657": 1.0}}, {"text": "To address these concerns, companies such as GLC Cerritos LLC are prioritizing sustainability efforts, including reforestation programs and responsible recruiting initiatives.", "citations": {"695b759e-d787-4a16-9bc5-9f006dc56478_763886478": 1.0}}, {"text": "Technologies such as AI and agri-technologies are also being used to reduce environmental impacts, including optimizing water and fertilizer use, and promoting sustainable agriculture practices.", "citations": {"4c89c353-c777-491d-86a9-a5a401e65167_543001314": 1.0, "90c773b4-1b6c-4e31-ad9c-ce6436027af7_615449353": 0.5}}, {"text": "Overall, the rising demand for avocados has significant environmental and social impacts, and it is essential for companies and governments to balance the trade-offs between economic benefits and environmental and social concerns.", "citations": {"2409aa08-ac99-4af7-9b03-00162ac09568_658036910": 1.0, "65e3998a-3ab7-4bb2-b022-ca181d90e86f_222072541": 0.5, "9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657": 0.25}}, {"text": "The economic benefits of avocado production are significant, with the avocado industry being a billion-dollar industry in Mexico.", "citations": {"3f2668d2-a695-4d4c-a2be-36032d9a07f4_87857532": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, the economic benefits of avocado production come at a cost, with the industry being linked to deforestation, water depletion, and labor exploitation.", "citations": {"9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657": 1.0}}, {"text": "To mitigate these impacts, sustainable avocado farming practices are being promoted, including the use of precision irrigation and agtech.", "citations": {"45fc74d4-b53d-435b-b877-06faa45e599d_42134423": 1.0}}, {"text": "Precision irrigation can help reduce water consumption, while agtech can help optimize fertilizer use and promote sustainable agriculture practices.", "citations": {"45fc74d4-b53d-435b-b877-06faa45e599d_42134423": 1.0}}, {"text": "In addition to sustainable farming practices, certifications such as Fair Trade and Organic are being used to promote social and environmental responsibility in the avocado industry.", "citations": {"695b759e-d787-4a16-9bc5-9f006dc56478_763886478": 1.0}}, {"text": "These certifications ensure that avocado farmers are paid a fair price for their produce and that their rights are protected.", "citations": {"695b759e-d787-4a16-9bc5-9f006dc56478_763886478": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the economic benefits of avocado production can be significant, but it is essential to prioritize sustainability and social responsibility to mitigate the environmental and social impacts of the industry.", "citations": {"2409aa08-ac99-4af7-9b03-00162ac09568_658036910": 1.0, "65e3998a-3ab7-4bb2-b022-ca181d90e86f_222072541": 0.5, "9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657": 0.25}}, {"text": "The social impacts of avocado production are significant, with the industry being linked to labor exploitation and food insecurity in Mexico.", "citations": {"9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657": 1.0}}, {"text": "The avocado mafia controls production and export in Mexico, leading to labor exploitation and food insecurity.", "citations": {"9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657": 1.0}}, {"text": "In addition to labor exploitation, avocado production has also been linked to deforestation and water depletion, which can have significant social impacts on local communities.", "citations": {"c4df1771-8297-4414-adac-d7cd6bb376e0_639626865": 1.0}}, {"text": "To address these concerns, companies such as GLC Cerritos LLC are prioritizing sustainability efforts, including reforestation programs and responsible recruiting initiatives.", "citations": {"695b759e-d787-4a16-9bc5-9f006dc56478_763886478": 1.0}}, {"text": "Technologies such as AI and agri-technologies are also being used to reduce environmental impacts, including optimizing water and fertilizer use, and promoting sustainable agriculture practices.", "citations": {"4c89c353-c777-491d-86a9-a5a401e65167_543001314": 1.0, "90c773b4-1b6c-4e31-ad9c-ce6436027af7_615449353": 0.5}}, {"text": "Overall, the social impacts of avocado production are significant, and it is essential for companies and governments to prioritize sustainability and social responsibility to mitigate these impacts.", "citations": {"2409aa08-ac99-4af7-9b03-00162ac09568_658036910": 1.0, "65e3998a-3ab7-4bb2-b022-ca181d90e86f_222072541": 0.5, "9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657": 0.25}}, {"text": "In conclusion, the rising demand for avocados has significant environmental and social impacts, and it is essential for companies and governments to balance the trade-offs between economic benefits and environmental and social concerns.", "citations": {"2409aa08-ac99-4af7-9b03-00162ac09568_658036910": 1.0, "65e3998a-3ab7-4bb2-b022-ca181d90e86f_222072541": 0.5, "9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657": 0.25}}, {"text": "Sustainable avocado farming practices, including the use of precision irrigation and agtech, can help mitigate these impacts.", "citations": {"45fc74d4-b53d-435b-b877-06faa45e599d_42134423": 1.0}}, {"text": "Certifications such as Fair Trade and Organic can also promote social and environmental responsibility in the avocado industry.", "citations": {"695b759e-d787-4a16-9bc5-9f006dc56478_763886478": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the avocado industry has the potential to be a significant contributor to the economy, but it is essential to prioritize sustainability and social responsibility to mitigate the environmental and social impacts of the industry [17,4,13].", "citations": {"8ca9c8e9-43b5-47a1-b8c7-47fcb66e4530_31759721": 1.0}}, {"text": "The US avocado market has more than doubled between 2015 and 2024, with eight out of 10 avocados in the US coming from Mexico.", "citations": {"8ca9c8e9-43b5-47a1-b8c7-47fcb66e4530_31759721": 1.0}}, {"text": "The economic output of imported avocados in the US increased by 500% between 2015 and 2024, with the US GDP from avocado imports reaching $6.1 billion annually.", "citations": {"8ca9c8e9-43b5-47a1-b8c7-47fcb66e4530_31759721": 1.0}}, {"text": "Avocado household penetration in the US grew by six million between 2015 and 2024, with purchase frequency increasing by 19%.", "citations": {"8ca9c8e9-43b5-47a1-b8c7-47fcb66e4530_31759721": 1.0}}, {"text": "The foodservice market share of avocados in the US grew by 20% between 2015 and 2024, with menu penetration also increasing by 20%.", "citations": {"8ca9c8e9-43b5-47a1-b8c7-47fcb66e4530_31759721": 1.0}}, {"text": "However, the rising demand for avocados has also raised environmental concerns, with climate change affecting avocado productivity and requiring a lot of water to grow.", "citations": {"65e3998a-3ab7-4bb2-b022-ca181d90e86f_222072541": 1.0}}, {"text": "Avocado farming is vulnerable to hotter and drier climate conditions, with Mexico potentially losing 59% of its land suitable for avocado growth by 2050.", "citations": {"c0a6998e-f6dc-4da7-9421-f8e7e575bd75_992753141": 1.0}}, {"text": "The avocado crop may be reduced by 40% by 2050 due to climate change, with some regions potentially experiencing a 41% reduction in avocado growth.", "citations": {"c0a6998e-f6dc-4da7-9421-f8e7e575bd75_992753141": 1.0}}, {"text": "In terms of social effects, 300,000 workers in Michoac\u00e1n depend on the avocado industry, with the US lift of a temporary ban on Mexican avocado imports ensuring economic certainty for farmers and laborers.", "citations": {"3f2668d2-a695-4d4c-a2be-36032d9a07f4_87857532": 1.0}}, {"text": "The average US avocado price is $1.43, up 11% from 2021, with annual avocado exports to the US nearing $3 billion.", "citations": {"a7f4f074-8551-4e2d-b84b-2fa1588ea418_168101927": 1.0}}, {"text": "Kenya has also emerged as a significant player in the global avocado market, ranking first in Africa for avocado export and eighth globally in 2020.", "citations": {"5265a592-e564-46e3-90dc-7b6f403e67e2_421983327": 1.0}}, {"text": "European avocado imports rose 23% in 2023, with Mexican supplies accounting for 40% of the US market.", "citations": {"fd214626-2761-443a-aee5-3562ee536d85_342391363": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the rising demand for avocados has had significant economic, environmental, and social impacts on the countries that produce them, with the US being a major driver of this demand.", "citations": {"8ca9c8e9-43b5-47a1-b8c7-47fcb66e4530_31759721": 1.0}}], "references": ["90c773b4-1b6c-4e31-ad9c-ce6436027af7_615449353", "65e3998a-3ab7-4bb2-b022-ca181d90e86f_222072541", "c4df1771-8297-4414-adac-d7cd6bb376e0_639626865", "c0a6998e-f6dc-4da7-9421-f8e7e575bd75_992753141", "2409aa08-ac99-4af7-9b03-00162ac09568_658036910", "695b759e-d787-4a16-9bc5-9f006dc56478_763886478", "45fc74d4-b53d-435b-b877-06faa45e599d_42134423", "fd214626-2761-443a-aee5-3562ee536d85_342391363", "0647188f-9964-4a4f-ae8e-63483708d38d_55923929", "114d1622-c9c5-4614-b132-9c9189790987_442554566", "a7f4f074-8551-4e2d-b84b-2fa1588ea418_168101927", "3f2668d2-a695-4d4c-a2be-36032d9a07f4_87857532", "9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657", "5265a592-e564-46e3-90dc-7b6f403e67e2_421983327", "8ca9c8e9-43b5-47a1-b8c7-47fcb66e4530_31759721", "18665f57-7b47-4cae-9c9d-5fc30625182f_930516690", "4c89c353-c777-491d-86a9-a5a401e65167_543001314"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1055", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Additives are commonly used in salmon farming to promote growth, prevent disease, and enhance nutritional value.", "citations": {"de9f2e6e-6769-4635-a399-58552e6eb27d_165935816": 1.0}}, {"text": "Vitamins, minerals, and amino acids are added to salmon feed to promote growth and health.", "citations": {"88cc5dfc-2dad-431c-b65d-8bee5c76cbf6_162638453": 1.0}}, {"text": "Additives like antibiotics and parasiticides are used to prevent disease and parasites, but their use is regulated.", "citations": {"92606b79-8d15-4945-b120-f2fc5ebb8261_958532855": 1.0}}, {"text": "The use of GMOs and nanomaterials is a debated topic with varying regulations across countries.", "citations": {"a56c34d0-d4fe-4519-85d1-821647039e57_22869885": 1.0}}, {"text": "Farmed salmon may contain added pigments and have more fat due to feed additives.", "citations": {"de9f2e6e-6769-4635-a399-58552e6eb27d_165935816": 1.0}}, {"text": "Farmed salmon's Omega 3 content can be affected by feed additives like fish oil and vegetable oil.", "citations": {"e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371": 1.0}}, {"text": "Farmed salmon has higher concentrations of PCBs, a potential cancer risk, than wild salmon.", "citations": {"ebc22f9a-9095-4f3b-a1e4-f2345c46bd76_389913171": 1.0}}, {"text": "Regulations in Norway, Chile, and Scotland ensure salmon feed additives are used safely, sustainably, and responsibly to minimize environmental and human health impacts.", "citations": {"e9c6105a-2ae1-41f6-b5c7-b46b192d7334_209861858": 1.0}}, {"text": "The use of some additives has raised health concerns, including the potential impact of ethoxyquin and antibiotic resistance.", "citations": {"14262a48-23c6-4805-a3f8-3bac32956acc_61620599": 1.0}}, {"text": "Development of sustainable salmon feed alternatives is ongoing to reduce environmental impact and promote salmon health.", "citations": {"16eca011-d5d9-4690-bf44-5ab7e52514e3_276664462": 1.0}}, {"text": "Researchers are investigating microalgae as a sustainable salmon feed due to its high omega-3 content and fish-like taste.", "citations": {"22fbd601-0f08-4671-a02a-f456f4c38c93_830260818": 1.0}}, {"text": "Insect-based feed is being explored as a sustainable option with 42%-63% higher protein content than traditional resources.", "citations": {"b2337ac7-4a05-48cc-a9a2-fcb21369a826_912080398": 1.0}}, {"text": "The European Union has implemented regulations on aquaculture feed additives, including environmental impact assessments and monitoring.", "citations": {"a025b1c1-ccbb-47af-9251-cf0ec52396c3_982238416": 1.0}}, {"text": "The FDA regulates aquaculture feed additives in the US, requiring manufacturers to prove safety and efficacy.", "citations": {"a025b1c1-ccbb-47af-9251-cf0ec52396c3_982238416": 1.0}}, {"text": "Countries like Russia, China, and Norway are investing in research to develop sustainable feed alternatives for the salmon farming industry.", "citations": {"23d7fe7e-4589-40b8-b911-e83020b3b80b_318736858": 1.0, "ced34f0a-144c-4eec-afab-98de204f3bfe_726039735": 0.5}}, {"text": "Standards for salmon farming additives vary by country, but many are implementing stricter regulations for sustainability and safety.", "citations": {"a025b1c1-ccbb-47af-9251-cf0ec52396c3_982238416": 1.0}}], "references": ["e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371", "88cc5dfc-2dad-431c-b65d-8bee5c76cbf6_162638453", "22fbd601-0f08-4671-a02a-f456f4c38c93_830260818", "ebc22f9a-9095-4f3b-a1e4-f2345c46bd76_389913171", "23d7fe7e-4589-40b8-b911-e83020b3b80b_318736858", "de9f2e6e-6769-4635-a399-58552e6eb27d_165935816", "16eca011-d5d9-4690-bf44-5ab7e52514e3_276664462", "14262a48-23c6-4805-a3f8-3bac32956acc_61620599", "a025b1c1-ccbb-47af-9251-cf0ec52396c3_982238416", "b2337ac7-4a05-48cc-a9a2-fcb21369a826_912080398", "ced34f0a-144c-4eec-afab-98de204f3bfe_726039735", "e9c6105a-2ae1-41f6-b5c7-b46b192d7334_209861858", "92606b79-8d15-4945-b120-f2fc5ebb8261_958532855", "a56c34d0-d4fe-4519-85d1-821647039e57_22869885"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1056", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The use of additives in salmon farming is a common practice to improve the growth and health of the fish, with common additives including probiotics, prebiotics, and immune stimulants.", "citations": {"206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288": 1.0}}, {"text": "Probiotics, such as Lactic Acid Bacillus B4, are used to improve fish growth and resistance to pathogens, and can also be used to reduce breeding time and risk in salmon farming.", "citations": {"206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288": 1.0}}, {"text": "Prebiotics, such as glucans, can be used to increase the production of probiotics in the body and improve fish and shrimp growth and immunity.", "citations": {"206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288": 1.0}}, {"text": "Other common additives used in salmon farming include essential oils, acidifiers, antioxidants, vitamins, amino acids, and enzymes, which can improve physiological processes and support immune system performance.", "citations": {"6ca8d065-49f9-4071-afff-f7fa2791705a_881197116": 1.0}}, {"text": "Uncommon additives used in salmon farming include Coix seeds and algae, which have antimicrobial properties and can be used to reduce the dependence on antibiotics.", "citations": {"88e1620b-05e4-4676-b96c-ba056e1a081f_297756784": 1.0}}, {"text": "The use of additives in salmon farming can have health concerns, such as the use of copper sulfate, which is toxic to humans and aquatic life, causing cell damage and death, as well as eye irritation and nausea.", "citations": {"9165fc8a-4222-4727-9d4e-ca1af6b2c914_402277020": 1.0}}, {"text": "Farmed salmon has been found to have higher levels of contaminants, including PCBs and methylmercury, which can pose health risks to humans, particularly pregnant women and children.", "citations": {"ebc22f9a-9095-4f3b-a1e4-f2345c46bd76_389913171": 1.0}}, {"text": "The consumption of farmed salmon more than once a month may increase the risk of cancer due to high levels of PCBs.", "citations": {"ebc22f9a-9095-4f3b-a1e4-f2345c46bd76_389913171": 1.0}}, {"text": "The standards and regulations governing the use of additives in salmon farming vary by country, with some countries having stricter regulations than others.", "citations": {"0475164f-f97d-480d-b3fb-28b5be941c89_711244548": 1.0}}, {"text": "In China, the Ministry of Agriculture monitors veterinary drug residues in aquaculture, and the pass rate of veterinary drug residue monitoring is 99.9% in 2021.", "citations": {"d2f70c93-61ca-4e93-bfb5-e48bb1f59d27_579728869": 1.0}}, {"text": "The use of additives in salmon farming is also regulated in other countries, such as Canada, where the Minister of Agriculture met with BC Salmon Farmers to discuss regulations and co-develop a transition plan.", "citations": {"adb6b376-1981-4027-92c3-fa738c1690ce_356480643": 1.0}}, {"text": "The plan aims to meet environmental objectives and protect wild salmon, and the sector is concerned about the rushed timeline for the transition plan.", "citations": {"adb6b376-1981-4027-92c3-fa738c1690ce_356480643": 1.0}}, {"text": "Overall, the use of additives in salmon farming is a complex issue that requires careful regulation and monitoring to ensure the safe and sustainable production of salmon.", "citations": {"b2dcfd3e-fd69-43ae-8ff2-3d30994a5e37_732859026": 1.0}}, {"text": "The health effects of consuming farmed salmon with additives can be detrimental, with potential health risks including increased cancer risk and developmental problems.", "citations": {"ebc22f9a-9095-4f3b-a1e4-f2345c46bd76_792342338": 1.0}}, {"text": "Consumers should be aware of the potential risks and choose wild-caught salmon as a healthier alternative.", "citations": {"ebc22f9a-9095-4f3b-a1e4-f2345c46bd76_389913171": 1.0}}, {"text": "The established safety limit for methylmercury in food is 0.5 parts per million, and the weekly intake limit for methylmercury is 96 micrograms for women.", "citations": {"05cbef67-7d80-4e76-b8cd-9e9768273f22_124342719": 1.0}}, {"text": "The Joint FAO/WHO sets food additive limits, including limits for methylmercury, which is 1.6 mg per kilogram per week.", "citations": {"05cbef67-7d80-4e76-b8cd-9e9768273f22_124342719": 1.0}}, {"text": "The use of additives in salmon farming is regulated by various agencies, including the Centre for Food Safety and the US EPA, which aim to protect human health and the environment.", "citations": {"00580580-2d22-4655-a113-539c80fc105d_955448469": 1.0, "5d99bcf8-caa9-455c-bba2-fe1e7c35ab76_46300290": 0.5, "c20ec645-6842-4082-bbf4-00bf4cdf99f6_498906330": 0.25}}, {"text": "However, more research is needed to fully understand the health effects of consuming farmed salmon with additives and to develop effective regulations to ensure the safety of farmed salmon for human consumption.", "citations": {"ebc22f9a-9095-4f3b-a1e4-f2345c46bd76_792342338": 1.0}}], "references": ["88e1620b-05e4-4676-b96c-ba056e1a081f_297756784", "6ca8d065-49f9-4071-afff-f7fa2791705a_881197116", "ebc22f9a-9095-4f3b-a1e4-f2345c46bd76_792342338", "c20ec645-6842-4082-bbf4-00bf4cdf99f6_498906330", "00580580-2d22-4655-a113-539c80fc105d_955448469", "0475164f-f97d-480d-b3fb-28b5be941c89_711244548", "d2f70c93-61ca-4e93-bfb5-e48bb1f59d27_579728869", "adb6b376-1981-4027-92c3-fa738c1690ce_356480643", "ebc22f9a-9095-4f3b-a1e4-f2345c46bd76_389913171", "9165fc8a-4222-4727-9d4e-ca1af6b2c914_402277020", "206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288", "05cbef67-7d80-4e76-b8cd-9e9768273f22_124342719", "5d99bcf8-caa9-455c-bba2-fe1e7c35ab76_46300290", "b2dcfd3e-fd69-43ae-8ff2-3d30994a5e37_732859026"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1065", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "The Labubu phenomenon has gained worldwide popularity, especially among younger generations, on social media platforms like TikTok.", "citations": {"16db704a-cc79-4157-884b-4e668dc4f687_198145340": 1.0}}, {"text": "The brand's unique design and character have driven its success and virality on TikTok through authenticity and creativity.", "citations": {"16db704a-cc79-4157-884b-4e668dc4f687_198145340": 1.0}}, {"text": "Labubu's partnerships with influencers like Rihanna have likely boosted its credibility and popularity.", "citations": {"20d8a15d-878a-4d0b-bc36-4615c82a868c_937625849": 1.0}}, {"text": "The brand's limited-edition products and exclusive experiences drive sales and increase popularity.", "citations": {"e28eb68f-8751-4971-92ce-84a78c57f3d3_641584784": 1.0}}, {"text": "Labubu targets younger generations and art toy fans, partnering with POP MART for immersive experiences.", "citations": {"a966128e-46f2-4173-b179-220745714004_912690380": 1.0}}, {"text": "The collection toy market, including Labubu, is expected to exceed 150 billion yuan by 2025, driven by a 35% growth rate and the blind box trend.", "citations": {"4970f67d-3140-4205-9f05-bdb1690fa93e_47737513": 1.0}}, {"text": "The brand's popularity has boosted Pop Mart's global revenue, significantly increasing its founder's wealth.", "citations": {"41c6b81d-926c-472d-9228-b56767997a63_720139167": 1.0}}, {"text": "Labubu's success is due to its unique design, effective marketing, and strategic partnerships with influencers and celebrities.", "citations": {"ae82719e-3b45-4ca5-a14a-9514a5889632_487728695": 1.0}}, {"text": "The brand's use of social media, particularly TikTok, has created a viral sensation with fans sharing unboxing experiences and showcasing their Labubu collections.", "citations": {"8ace1afd-bf71-4d4c-afe2-e37438397952_514663010": 1.0}}, {"text": "TikTok, with over 1 billion users, offers high engagement rates, making it ideal for brands like Labubu to boost their online presence.", "citations": {"8ace1afd-bf71-4d4c-afe2-e37438397952_514663010": 1.0}}, {"text": "The target audience likely appreciates cultural collaborations, limited-edition products, and exclusive experiences.", "citations": {"a966128e-46f2-4173-b179-220745714004_912690380": 1.0}}, {"text": "Labubu's success is partly due to its ability to create a sense of community among fans, particularly in Thailand.", "citations": {"d7ca8fc0-d7dc-4230-95fb-232096ab8873_656831105": 1.0}}, {"text": "The brand has a strong fan base and its products often sell out in under half an hour.", "citations": {"e28eb68f-8751-4971-92ce-84a78c57f3d3_641584784": 1.0}}, {"text": "Pop Mart's revenue growth is driven by Labubu sales, with the company's overall income rising 35%-40% year-on-year.", "citations": {"41c6b81d-926c-472d-9228-b56767997a63_720139167": 1.0}}, {"text": "Influencer endorsements positively impact Labubu's brand awareness and sales, with celebrity endorsements contributing to its popularity.", "citations": {"20d8a15d-878a-4d0b-bc36-4615c82a868c_937625849": 1.0}}], "references": ["e28eb68f-8751-4971-92ce-84a78c57f3d3_641584784", "41c6b81d-926c-472d-9228-b56767997a63_720139167", "ae82719e-3b45-4ca5-a14a-9514a5889632_487728695", "8ace1afd-bf71-4d4c-afe2-e37438397952_514663010", "16db704a-cc79-4157-884b-4e668dc4f687_198145340", "a966128e-46f2-4173-b179-220745714004_912690380", "4970f67d-3140-4205-9f05-bdb1690fa93e_47737513", "d7ca8fc0-d7dc-4230-95fb-232096ab8873_656831105", "20d8a15d-878a-4d0b-bc36-4615c82a868c_937625849"]}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "still", "task": "multilingual", "topic_id": "1066", "run_id": "still-proposed"}, "responses": [{"text": "Labubu, a brand of collectible plush toy monster elves created by Kasing Lung, has gained worldwide popularity, boosting Pop Mart's global revenue.", "citations": {"4439e590-c34a-43da-8231-bac806e2921a_797916345": 1.0}}, {"text": "The brand's popularity stems from its unique character design, marketing, and partnerships, such as with The Peninsula Shanghai for a LABUBU-themed afternoon tea.", "citations": {"a966128e-46f2-4173-b179-220745714004_912690380": 1.0}}, {"text": "Labubu's target audience is younger generations who value unique products and are active on social media.", "citations": {"a966128e-46f2-4173-b179-220745714004_912690380": 1.0}}, {"text": "The brand's audience is influenced by social media marketing, including influencer marketing and referral programs.", "citations": {"dc8bff1f-d43c-42de-870c-11c0f2fc3457_7095251": 1.0}}, {"text": "Labubu's popularity has driven a significant increase in Pop Mart's stock price, with revenue and profit growth of at least 55% and 90% year-on-year, respectively.", "citations": {"6e8266d8-b5ac-4c3a-a99c-09a11714a059_519628549": 1.0}}, {"text": "The company's market value is $25.6 billion, with self-owned products contributing nearly half of its revenue.", "citations": {"ae2ee7e7-87bd-45aa-9f99-e39c295bd660_1019660895": 1.0}}, {"text": "Labubu's success is due to its viral sensation on TikTok, where it uses trend content, popular hashtags, and a unique video style.", "citations": {"0326be4b-7d21-4e14-8ce6-991e56e398c7_506133113": 1.0}}, {"text": "The brand's unique storytelling, music, and interactive content have helped it go viral on TikTok.", "citations": {"16db704a-cc79-4157-884b-4e668dc4f687_198145340": 1.0}}, {"text": "Labubu's target audience is diverse, united by their love for the brand and its products.", "citations": {"a571d8f8-819b-4d5b-8ee0-1feacaa7b19f_497366267": 1.0}}, {"tex